\h Farasegi Gumgi
\toc1 Zisas Farasegi 12 Th…®gi Ňäaara Gumgi MuuŇčgi Ňäaari
\toc2 Farasegi Gumgi
\toc3 FG
\mt1 FARASEGI GUMGI
\mt2 Zisas Farasegi 12 Th…®gi Ňäaara Gumgi MuuŇčgi Ňäaari
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Kha gavar ki buni, nta Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi muuŇčgi Ňčaari bun nzuai buni ki gap ma. Kha buni nta Ruk vh…®ra nduara nta khergi. Nza kha gavan gan…®nga, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar, ana nduara tuavar mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi kh…®vigim, mbe Zisas muuŇčgi bigir vhuuiŇč, ‚Äúmbe Zerusareman nta bun nzuav, Zudian nta bun nzuav, Samarian nta bun nzuav, vh…®ra za kha nuianan vov, nta bun suaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Ndu sapta 1.18 gan…®ri.
\ip Kha gap, ana Zisas Krais fhara guarara ZudaiŇč r…®gar sios khavgim, ana k…®vgiap, zumgum ana za kha nuianan vugi ne neŇčgi gap ma. Ruk vh…®ra khuen nza kh…®vi, ana Zisas Krais muuŇčgi Ňčaari gum ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir k…®r…® t…®vi gum bigi, nta guigira mba Fhe Bak…®me fhum mba Isrerar ki gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčgi bunira z…®n vugi.
\ip Kha gap, ana nzuai big…®na bak…®me ne khare, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňäinan Ňäaar Ňčgari Ňčaara nzuai. Fhe Bak…®me fharav Pentikos raar ana won Ňäina Ňäaara sarigim, ana mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgir han zergi. Ana mben han zergap, zumgum, ana nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin mbe nd…®…®v, ŇčkasŇčkan mbe n…®…®Ňčgi.
\ip Nza vh…®ra kha gavan gan…®nga, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mba Zisas muuŇčgi buni vhuuiŇč bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav suaŇčgi buni mpeeiŇč nta ki. Nza mba buni garim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč z…®n vuim, sios th…®ga havhargi.
\ip Kha gap, ana Zisas farasegi gumgi vh…®rve bun suaŇčgi. Mba gumgi r…®gar kha guma phunini, Pita gu Por, mani muuŇčgi bigi neŇčgegi buni, nta guigira vh…®rk…®vgi. Pita, ana mba Zisas phorga ruigi guma mbe ma. Por, ana fharav Zisas z…®n vugi guma fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Por, ana fharav Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben farfav, mbe Zisas z…®n vui ne nzuav mbe th…®vav, mben farfagi. Ana maaŇč mbuav kim, Zisas ana kamgim, ana Zisas z…®n vuim, ana ana ndi fagim, ana ana z…®n vov, ana Ňčaara mbui guman vhuuŇč guarara ki.
\ip Nza kha gavar gan…®nga Ňčana mueŇč, Ruk Porar h…®gi bigi mbari, ana nta neŇčgegi. Ana nza Por ga muuŇčgi bigi mbari, ana nta neŇčgegim, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Ruk, ana nduara tugi mbarir Por phorga ruigi, ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap kaŇčgiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza kha fhaiŇč nt…®…®rira.‚ÄĚ
\c 1
\ms1 Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Zerusareman Zisas muuŇčgi bigir vhuuiŇč, mbe nta bun nzuai.
\s1 Zisas khaŇč suaŇčgi, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara sararim ana zir…®rga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mk 16.19; Ru 1.1-4; 24.49-51\x*O, Tiofirus, gu mba fharav khergi gap, gu ana kherav, gu mba Zisas fhara guarara won Ňčaara bak…®me khavgiap, mba gumgi gu mbigi ana Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav mbe suaŇčgi bigi gu za nta neŇčgegi. \f a \fr 1:1 \ft Ruk kha gava khergi. Mba gava z…® khare. Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi muuŇčgi Ňčaari. Ruk khaŇč nzuai, ana fhara guarara, ana kha gava khergi. Mba gava z…® khare, Ruk khergi kaman vhuuŇč. \f*
\v 2 Gu nta neŇčga vov, mba Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana ndiga Hevenan ndagi nera th…®gi. Fhe Bak…®me zumgum ana ndiga Hevenan ndagi, ana fharav rimgiap, khavgiap, ana vov wo farasegi 11 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgir h…®gap, ana Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaara ŇčkasŇčkar panan, ana mbe muunga Ňčaari bun mbe suaŇčgi. Ana Ňčaari bun mbe suaŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me ana ndigap Hevenan ndagi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Mt 28.17; Mk 16.12; Ru 24.36-49; FG 10.41; 1 Ko 15.5-7\x*Zisas fharav won Ňčaara bak…®me mbuav kav, zaa bak…®me ndigap, rimgiap, taagia khavgiap, mbaram vov wo farasegi Ňčaara gumgir h…®gi. Ana mben h…®gap, won mbe kh…®vav ana bigi vh…®rvera muuŇčgi. Ana mba bigir muuŇčrim, mbe ana gangip, ana khoth…®g…®p khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúAna guigira rimgiap taagia khavgi.‚ÄĚ Ana mba t…®var mbe mbuav 40 rarir ana mbe phorga kav Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga bunin mbe suaŇčgi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Ru 24.49; Zo 14.16-17; FG 2.33\x*Ana mba tugir mbe phorgara kav, ana kama havharan khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Zerusaremra k…®ri. Nde k…®v mba Fhe Bak…®me nden n…®…®n za suaŇčgi big…®n, nde ana rarg…® k…®ri. Gu fhum mba big…®na bun nde suaŇčgi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Mt 3.11; Mk 1.8; Ru 3.16; Zo 1.33; FG 11.16\x*Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma, ana fhum mb…®n gumgi gu mbigi ruagi. Nde ntigem rari vh…®rve fhuvara, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar nde ruarga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ais 1.26; Dan 7.17; Amo 9.11; Mt 24.3; Ru 24.21\x*Zisas mba kamen mbe nzuaim, mba ana farasegi 11 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe wari fugap kha nzambaren ana muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ndu ntigem taagip kha IsreriŇč gan…®nga guman pana ndim farim, ana mbe gan…®rim, mbe taagip thivgip havhargip zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rie? Ee, fhuve?‚ÄĚ \f b \fr 1:6 \ft Fhum guarara, mbe IsreriŇč, mbe nduarira Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan kav, mbe nduarira wari gari. Mbe zumgum Zisas h…®gi tugen mbe, Rom gari guman pan mbe ndigim, mbe ana piin kim, ana mbe gari. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, Rom guman pana piin kav kim, Zisas h…®gim, mbe IsreriŇč gumgi vh…®rve, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Zisas ntige z…®v, kha RomiŇč guman pana vh…®rarim, ana sarga, ana taagip nza ndim, Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani ndi feg…®rim, mbe nza IsreriŇč, mbe nza gan…®rim, nza wom Rom guman pana piin k…®rim, ana nza gan…®nga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nza nduarira wari gan…®nga. \f*
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mt 24.36; Mk 13.32; 1 Te 5.1\x*Mbe mba nzambaren Zisas ga muuŇčgim, ana mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúKhe nde bigeŇč, ee? Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip mba bigeŇč h…®rga tuk gum ra nzuav nzaire? Fhuvara! Khe Fhe Bak…®me big…®n ma. Ana nduara ana mba bigi gari, ana nduara mba bigeŇč tugas…®rga.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Mt 28.19; Mk 16.15; Ru 24.47-48; Zo 15.27; FG 2.32; 3.15; 5.32\x*Nde fhura k…®v gan…®ri, ana zumgum won Ňäina Ňäaara sararim, ana nde han zirg…®p, ŇčkasŇčkan nden n…®…®Ňčgirim, nde Zerusareman nan buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčv, za mba Zudia fhain nta bun suaŇčv, vh…®ra Samaria fhain nta bun suaŇčv, Ňčg…®p vh…®ra kha nuianan za nta bun suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me Zisas ndiga Hevenan ndai.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Mk 16.19; Ru 24.50-51; Zo 6.62; 20.17\x*Zisas kha bunin mbe suaŇčgia thugim, mbe ana garavra kim, ana mbe thav fhura sigap Hevenan ndai. Ana ndaim, buiva hura mbige za ana vharigim, mbe wom ana gari fhu.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Mt 28.3; Mk 16.5; Ru 24.4; Zo 20.12; FG 10.3; 10.30\x*Zisas ndagim, mbe ana nzuav khozr…®gia buiva garav kim, guma phunini, mani shagi huri shargi, mani fhura hav mbe gaar mbar th…®gi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mt 24.30; 26.64; Ru 21.27; Zo 14.3; 1 Te 1.10; 4.16; VB 1.7\x*Mani th…®gap khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha Gariri gumgi, nde thaŇč nzuav thivgiap, fhura khoga kha buiva garav ki? Kha guma Zisas, Fhe Bak…®me ntigem ana ndigim, ana nde thav Hevenan ndagi. Ana zumgum, nde ana gan…®nga, ana ntigem Hevenan ndagi t…®vara muuŇčgip, ana taagi Hevenan keg…®p zir…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mbe harigi guma mbe ndi fagim, ana Zudas Ňčana ndigip, ana muunga Ňčaarar muunga.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Ru 24.50\x*Mba gumani maaŇč mbe suaŇčgim, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mba Oriv mb…®ksh…®ma thav, wari taagiap Zerusareman vergi. Mba Oriv Mb…®ksh…®m, ana Zerusarem hara ki. Anan veri r…®ks…®gage kiromita bavira th…®gi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Mt 10.2-4; Mk 3.16-19; Ru 6.14-16\x*Mbe Zerusareman vergap, mbe vov, mba zazera ki phenan mba vun ki vundavar ndav anan ki. Mbe mba ki nt…®…®ri, mbe z…®ri khare, Pita gu Zems, Andru, Firip, Tomas, Bartoromiu, Matiu, Arfisun kam Zems, mba Serotan wari ga r…®gi guma mbe Saimon, Zemsan kam Zudas.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mt 13.55; Ru 23.49; 23.55; 24.10; Zo 6.42; 7.5\x*Mbe kha gumgi, mbe wari t…®gap ndava bavira kav, mbe wari t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav wari ki. Mbe mbigi mbari, mbe vh…®ra mbe phorga ki. Mba mbigi Zisasan niamuuŇč Maria gum, ana Ňčgugi, mbe vh…®ra zav, maam mbe phorgav mbe wari t…®gap, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 15 Mba tugen, guigira Zisasan buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mben vh…®rve khaŇč muuŇčgi, 120. Mba gumgi gu mbigir vh…®rve kim, Pita khavgiap mben r…®ga th…®gap khaŇč nzuai,
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Sng 41.9\x*‚ÄúNde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, nde mbarara. Fhum, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar Devit ga rugim, ana kha kameŇč suaŇčgim, ne Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėZudas ana mba tuavar mba gumgi kh…®vigim, mbe zav Zisasan suirigi.‚Äô Ntigem, mba Devit suaŇčgi kameŇč ne mbara muuŇčgiap khar h…®gi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 10.4; Ru 6.16; FG 1.25\x*Zudas, ana fhum nza phorga kav, ana nza kha mbui Ňčaarara muuŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mt 26.15; 2 Pi 2.15\x*\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mt 27.3-8\x*Kha guma Zudas, ana mba t…®va mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgiap, ne vheza ndigap, mbaram wo nzuav nuiana s…®ga mueŇč ga vhezgi. Ana mba nuiana s…®geŇč ga vhezgiap, zumgum ana rav, mba nuiana s…®geŇč ga r…®gav, ndav furagar…®gap, mbu gum bigi za faŇčgia n…®…®aŇč ndarigi.
\v 19 Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, zumgum mba Zerusareman ki gumgi, mbe za ana muuŇčgi bigeŇč kaŇčgi. Mbe mba bigeŇč kaŇčgiap, mbe mba nuiana s…®geŇč mbe won kaman kha z…®n nen kaai, ‚ÄúAkerdama.‚ÄĚ Kha z…® Akerdama, ne n…®…®eŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúV…®z…®n regi nuianeŇč.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Sng 69.25; 109.8\x*Pita mba bunin mbe nzua vov khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha kameŇč mbe Ňägavi Ki Gavar ne khergi, mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėAna mba r…®gi ŇčaneŇč, ne fhura k…®ri, nde guma the gan…®ri, ana mba Ňčanen k…® thari.‚Äô
\p ‚ÄúMba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar Ňčana mueŇč mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėHarigi guma the, ana Ňčana ndigip, ana mbui Ňčaarar muunga.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Mt 3.16; Mk 1.9; 16.19; Ru 3.21; 24.51; Zo 15.27; FG 4.33\x*‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza nduarira warira r…®gar mba fhum Guma Bak…®me Zisas nzan kov, kha bigi ga ruim, mba zazera nza phorga ruigi guma the, nza ana ndim farga.
\v 22 Mba guma Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma mba gumgi gu mbigi ruai tugen kegap, zav Zisas won Ňčaara bak…®me khavgiap, ana mbua rui tugen h…®gap, zav, ntigem kha raar Fhe Bak…®me Zisas ndigim, ana nza thav taagia Hevenan ndagi raa th…®gi. Mba nza phorga ruav, za mba Zisas muuŇčgi bigi gangi, guma the ndi farim, ana nza phorg…®p kha Ňčaarar muuŇčv, mba Zisas rimgiap, taagia khavgi ne bun suanga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Pita maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram mbe guma phunini ndi fagi. Mbe fagi guma mbe, Zosep, ana z…® mbe khare, Barsabas. Mbe vh…®ra kha z…® phorga ana kaai Zastus. Harigi ne, Matias.
\v 24-25 \x - \xo 1:24-25 \xt 1 Sml 16.7; Jer 11.20; Zo 2.25; VB 2.23\x*Mbe mani ndi fav, mani ga nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúO, Guma Bak…®me, ndu za kha gumgi ndavir vheri gum nd…®knd…®gi kaŇčgi. Ndu nduara nza kh…®vari. Ndu kha gumani r…®gar maaŇčgi ne farasarigi, ana Zudas Ňčana ndigip, nza Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, ana nza phorg…®p kha Ňčaarar muunga. Zudas mba Ňčaara thav, ana mba k…®rga Ňčgu ana vov anan ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 26 Mbe ne Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap mbaram, mani heen zav, k…®ma phuni ndigap, mani z…®nin mba k…®m…®ni khergiap, ni ndi thuuŇč kh…®ngiap ni tuaŇčtuagi. Mbe ni tuaŇčtuav kim, mbevi n…®…®eŇč r…®gim, mbe mbaram ana ndigap ana z…® garim, ana Matias z…® ana ki. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap Matias heigim, ana mba Zisas farasegi 11 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi phorg…®v Ňčgar…®rga. \f c \fr 1:26 \ft Mbe khueŇč vuzvugi, Fhe Bak…®me nduara Zudas Ňčana ndirga guma farsararim, ana Zudas Ňčana ndirga. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, k…®ma phuni ndigap, Barsabas gum, Matias z…®nin mba k…®mani khergiap, nin big…®na mbe kh…®ngiap ni tuaŇčtuagi. Mbe mani z…®ni kh…®gap, mba k…®mani tuaŇčtuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza mani z…®ni ki k…®mani tuaŇčtuav gan…®nga, mani the z…® ki k…®m, mba big…®na thav n…®…®eŇč r…®g…®rga, nza gangip, kaŇčgirga, Fhe Bak…®me ana farasarigi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\c 2
\s1 Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar zeri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Lo 16.9-11; FG 1.14\x*Mba Pentikos tuga bak…®me h…®gim, mba raar mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe wari fugap, phena mbevi vhen ki. \f a \fr 2:1 \ft Mba ‚ÄúPentikos Tuga Bak…®me‚ÄĚ Ana z…® mbe khare, ana mba mbe IsreriŇč mbe fharav wari won m…®ni hiaŇč suav ndikndigi tuga bak…®me ma. Ndu vh…®ra kha gava gan…®ri, mba gava z…® khare. Fhe Bak…®me Rotu Gari Gumgir Ňägargi Ňäaari. O Wokpris. Sapta 23.15 keg…®p gan…®v Ňčg…®p, 22 th…®g…®ri. Mba tuga bak…®me, ana mba Fhe Bak…®me Idz…®van mba IsreriŇč tari bari Ňčk…®…®av, Idz…®viŇč tari bari shogim, mbe vh…®zgi. Mbe IsreriŇč nd…®knd…®gi tuga bak…®me h…®gap vh…®zgim, 50 rari vov vh…®zgim, mbe IsreriŇč won m…®ni hiaŇč suav ndikndigi tuga bak…®me hi. \f*
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt FG 4.31\x*Mbe mba phena vhen wari fugap kim, kh…®kh…®ma mbe fhura Hevenan h…®gi, mba kh…®kh…®m b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…®me fara muuŇčgiap zerav, mbe mba ki phena vhee mba kh…®kh…®m za mba phena vhee ruigi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Mt 3.11\x*Mbe garav, vhava zari fara muuŇčgi bigi gari. Mbe nta garim, nta vov za mbe pani sh…®ri tug…®rat…®gap nta thivgi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mk 16.17; FG 1.5; 4.31; 10.44-46; 1 Ko 12.10; 13.1\x*Mba bigi mbe pani sh…®ri thivgim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäinan Ňäaar za mbe ndavi vherir vergap, mbe rugim, mbe harigi Ňčguir kaa ga vhov buni nzuai. Mbe fhura mba t…®va mbui fhuvara, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäinan Ňäaar nduara mbe rugim, mbe mba kaa ga vhui.
\p 
\v 5 Mba tugen, ZudaiŇč mbari, mbe vh…®ra zegap, Zerusareman ki, mbe vh…®ra guigira Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ana t…®va z…®n vui nt…®…®ri ma. Mbe za kha nuianan ki Ňčguian kega zegi.
\v 6 Mba tugen mba kh…®kh…®m him, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera, mbe mba kh…®kh…®m mbararagiap, zav wari fugap, mba Zisas farasegi 12 t…®gi Ňčaara gumgi nzuai buni, mbe za khuara mbe t…®gi. Mbe khuaran mbe t…®gap, mbe mbararav khueŇč nzuav guigira Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi. Mba zegi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbe mbararagim, mbe mben kaara vhov mba buni nzuaim, mbe mba buni mbararagi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt FG 1.11\x*Mba zegi ZudaiŇč, mbe mbararagiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúEe, kheiŇč GaririŇč gumgira khare.
\v 8 Nza ram muuŇčgiap mbe nzuai buni nza won kaara nta mbararagi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2 T 1.15\x*Nza khaŇč muuŇčgi Ňčgui, nza zega khar ki. Nza mbari Partia fhain kega zegi, nza mbari Midia fhain kega zegi, mbari Eram fhain kega zegi, nza mba Mesopotemia fhain ki gumgi gum Zudia fhain ki gumgi, Kapadosian fhain ki gumgi, Pontus fhain ki gumgi, Esia fhain ki gumgi gum, nza mbari.
\v 10 Frigia gum Pamfiria fhain kega zegi, nza mbari Idz…®p fhain kega zegi, nza mbari Ribia nder muen, Sairini Ňčgu bak…®men han kega zegi. Nza mbari Roman zegap wari zav khaŇč ndagi.
\v 11 Nza ZudaiŇč gum nza phorgap nza rotu mbui t…®va z…®n vui gumgi, gum Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen kega zegi gumgi, gum Arebian kega zegi gumgi, nza khar zegi gumgi, nza mbe mbararagi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi baik…®vi, mbe nzan kamara nta neŇčgim, nza nta mbararagi.‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Mba zegi gumgi, mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbararagiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Mbe nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbuav nduarira khaŇč wari ga nzuai, ‚ÄúKha ntige hi bigeŇč, ne ram mbui khesharigi big…®na goreŇčra?‚ÄĚ
\v 13 Mbe maaŇč wari ga nzuav, mbe mbari mbe nz…®…®v khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúMbe waina kama mbegav ŇčanŇčana nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pita buni nzuai.
\p 
\v 14 Mbe maaŇč wari ga nzuaim, Pita mbaram mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi r…®gar khavgia th…®gap, kama havharan kaav khaŇč mba gumgi gum mbigi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha ZudaiŇč gum nde mbe zegap kha Zerusareman ki gumgi gu mbigi, nde khuarar na bunin t…®g…®ri. Nde khuaran na bunin t…®g…®p, nde ntige khar hi bigeŇč n…®…®eŇč kaŇčgirga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Te 5.7\x*Nde nd…®knd…®gi, kha gumgi waina kama mbegav ŇčanŇčanire? Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ntigera m…®n thugim, ra ndav sh…®rav nzai, 9 kirok ma.\f b \fr 2:15 \ft Pita khaŇč muuŇčgiap mba kameŇč nzuai, mbe ZudaiŇč mben t…®v ma. Mbe manera mba pav mb…® pi fhu. \f*
\v 16-17 \x - \xo 2:16-17 \xt Jol 2.28-32; Sek 12.10; Zo 7.38; FG 10.45; 21.9\x*Nde ntige khar h…®gi bigeŇč, nde ne gari ne fhum Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma Zoer ne suaŇčgi. Ana fhum khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėFhe Bak…®me khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba mpuur rarivige han maanga, gu won Ňäina Ňäaara siv za kha gumgi gu mbigi ga suarga. Nden Ňčkaa gum nde Ňčkarmbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi na buni bun nzuai t…®var muuŇčgip, na buni bun suanga. Nden gumgir Ňčkaa, mbe r…®…®a kui t…®var muuŇčgip, bigi gan…®nga, nde gumgi vuri mbe r…®…®r kurga. \f c \fr 2:16-17 \ft Mba mpuur rarivige, ne mbe ZudaiŇč khaŇč nzuai ne ma. Mbe mba Zisas Krais z…®rza mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me ana bun mbe nzuav suaŇčgi buni h…®rga tugivige ma, mbe ne nzuai. Mba tugivigen Fhe Bak…®me mbe Ňčgi kameŇč mba teg…®rga. Nza ntigem, Zisas z…®n vov, ruagi gumgi vh…®rve mbe pham kaa kameŇč ga nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas kha nuianan zergap, rimgiap, taagia Hevenan ndav, taagi zir…® zav mbui tugivigen. Mba mpuur rarivige ne nzuai fhuvara.‚ÄĚ \f*
\v 18 Gu mba tugen gu won Ňäina Ňäaara sararim, ana na Ňčaara gumgi gum nan Ňčaara mbigi han Ňčgir…®rga, mbe Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi na buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai t…®var muuŇčgip na buni bun suanga.
\v 19 Gu kha buivar gu harigi khesharigi bigir muuŇčrim, nta h…®rga, gu mba nuianan mirikorir muunga, mba mirikori, nta mba tugen mba raar hi bigir nde kh…®vi mirikori ma. Mba tugen v…®z…®n gum vhav, vhava thuura bak…®me nta h…®rga.
\v 20 Mba tugen, ran Ňčaar vh…®zgirga, maaŇč g…®ngirga, k…®ni h…®vgip v…®z…®na geg…®rga. Mba bigi heg…®rga, zumgum Guma Bak…®me h…®rga tuk h…®g…®rga, ana mba raar ana won ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me gum won vhava Ňčaara ndim kh…®v…®rga.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Ro 10.13\x*Mba tugen, warir kurkura saŇčv Guma Bak…®men kam…®nga, mba gumgi gu mbigi Guma Bak…®me taagip mbe ndigirim, mbe nzerara k…®rga.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô Khe Zoer suaŇčgi buni khare.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Zo 3.2; 14.10-11; Hi 2.4\x*‚ÄúNde IsreriŇč gumgi, nde khuaran na bunin t…®g…®ri. Gu Nasaret guma Zisas bun nde suan za mbui. Fhe Bak…®me ndera nzuav Zisas ga sarigim, ana zergi. Nde nduarira wari wo r…®mgi thugira ana garim, ana nde r…®gar kav, Fhe Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčkan panan, won farvenira ana Ňčaari bak…®vi ga mbuav, mirikori ga muuŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me ana panan maaŇč muuŇčrim, nde gangip kaŇčgirga, Fhe Bak…®me nduara ana farasarigi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Mt 27.35; Mk 15.24; Ru 23.33; Zo 19.18; FG 4.28; 1 Pi 1.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra fhum kha guman nde farve ga sur zav suaŇčgiap, ne nd…®knd…®gap kav, ana ntigem anan nde farve kh…®ngi. Ana anan nde farve kh…®ngim, nde mba gumgi mbat…®gir kov hegap, ana ndim khanarareŇč ga t…®gap fugim, ana rimgi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Mt 28.5-6; Mk 16.6; Ru 24.5; FG 3.15; 4.10; 10.40; 13.30-31; 17.31; 1 Ko 15.15\x*Ana rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgi. Ana fhura ana garim, ana rimgiap khurigi fhuvara, ana khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana za rimgip mba mbogar k…®v khur…®v shargirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana rimgi, r…®mr…®m ana suirarga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Sng 16.8-11\x*Nzan nz…®ga Devit fhum ana nd…®knd…®gap khaŇč suaŇčgi,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄėGu Guma Bak…®me garim, ana guigira zazera na n…®mara ki.
\q1 Ana nan guva haren kav, ŇčkasŇčkar na nd…®…®im, big…®n the nan muuŇčgirim, gu rivgip, nin…®ga muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\q1 
\v 26 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap na ndava vhee guigira ndikndigim, na th…®…®nin gu ndikndigi bunira nzuai.
\q1 Gu ndikndigi bunira nzuav, gu kaŇčgi, gu rimgirga. Gu Fhe Bak…®me muunga bigir vhuuiŇč, gu ntan rarga ki.
\q1 
\v 27 \x - \xo 2:27 \xt FG 13.35\x*Ndu fhura na gan…®rim, na tum za vh…®zgi gumgi ki Ňčgun keg…®rga fhuvara.
\q1 Ndu vh…®ra, ndu guigira wo z…®n vui Ňčaara guman Ňčaar, ndu ana farasarigi. Ndu fhura ana gan…®rim, ana mbogar k…®v, khurgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\q1 
\v 28 Ndu zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndirga tuap, ndu anan na kh…®vigi.
\q1 Ndu fhura na gan…®rim, gu ndu phorg…®v k…®rim, ndu nan kurkurarim, gu guigira ndikndig…®rga.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 2:29 \xt 1 Kin 2.10; Ru 1.32; 1.69; FG 13.36; 2 T 2.8\x*‚ÄúNzan nz…®ga Devit the nd…®knd…®gap kha buni suaŇčgi? Nde nan fegi gum Ňčgugi, gu ntigem guigira nza won nz…®ga Devit bun nde suan za mbui. Nzan nz…®k Devit, ana rimgim, mbe fhum ana ndim mboga t…®gim, ana tum fhum vurvurigi. Anan tum vurvurigim, ana mbok fhum nzan r…®gar ka zav ntigem khar ki.
\v 30 \x - \xo 2:30 \xt 2 Sml 7.12-13; Sng 89.3-4; 132.11\x*Nzan nz…®ga Devit, ana Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma ma. Ana kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me guigi guarara taagia wora zitav khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėGu zumgum ndu sh…®gar guma the ndiv farim, ana ndu Ňčgui gari guman pan kegi farar muuŇčgip, Ňčgui gari guman pan k…®rga.‚Äô
\v 31 \x - \xo 2:31 \xt Sng 16.10; FG 13.35\x*Devit maaŇč muuŇčgiap kaŇčgiap, ana mba kameŇč suaŇčgi. Ana Fhe Bak…®me taagiap kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarigi guma, ana ana bun nzuai.\f d \fr 2:31 \ft ‚ÄúMba Fhe Bak…®me taagip won gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarav sarigi guma,‚ÄĚ mbe Grikin kaman khaŇč z…®n ana kaai, ‚ÄúKrais.‚ÄĚ \f* Ana rimgip, taagip khavgirga. Ana rimgip za mba vh…®zi gumgi ki Ňčgun keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra rimgip khurgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 32 \x - \xo 2:32 \xt FG 1.8; 2.24\x*Ana ne suaŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me ntigem Zisas rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgi. Ana rimgiap, taagia khavgim, nza za ana gangi. Nza ana gangiap, nza mba bigi, nza nta bun nzuai.
\v 33 \x - \xo 2:33 \xt Zo 14.26; FG 1.4; 5.31; 7.55-56; 10.45; Ef 4.8; Hi 10.12\x*Zisas khavgiap, ana ntigem taagia Fhe Bak…®me han Hevenan ndagi. Ana ndav, Fhe Bak…®men guva hareŇč ga perav mbur ki. Ana ntigem Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar ana n…®…®Ňčgi, ana fhum mba Ňäina Ňäaarar ana n…®…®n za suaŇčgiap, ana ntigem anan ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Fhe Bak…®me mba Ňäina Ňäaarar ana n…®…®Ňčgim, ana ntigem mba Ňäina Ňäaara siav nza suagim, nza ana panan Ňčgarim, nde ntigem ana mbui bigi garav ana buni mbararagi.
\v 34-35 \x - \xo 2:34-35 \xt Sng 110.1\x*Nzan nz…®k Devit, ana Zisas fara muuŇčgiap Hevenan ndagi fhuvara. Khe Devit suaŇčgi kameŇč khare. Ana khaŇč nzuai,
\q1 ‚ÄėFhe Bak…®me khaŇč na Guma Bak…®me nzuai,
\q1 ‚ÄúNdu nan guva haren perav k…®rim, gu ndun pana gumgir muuŇčrim, mbe ndun piin k…®rga.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 2:36 \xt FG 5.30-31\x*‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde za IsreriŇč, nde tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgiri. Nde mba khanarareŇč ga t…®ga fugi guma Zisas, Fhe Bak…®me ana ndiv Guma Bak…®men fagim, ana taagip won gumgi gu mbigi ndirga guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve ndavi domdorgiap ruagi.
\p 
\v 37 \x - \xo 2:37 \xt Sek 12.10; Ru 3.10-12; FG 9.6; 16.30\x*Pita mba buni nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe mba buni mbararagim, mba buni guigira mbe th…®gi. Mba buni guigira mbe thivgim, mbe mbaram Pita gum mba ana phorga Ňčgari Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mben nzarigi. Mbe kha nzambarer mbe muuŇčgi. ‚ÄúNde nzan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nde khar nza suaŇč, nza ntige ram muuŇčrie?‚ÄĚ
\v 38 \x - \xo 2:38 \xt Ru 24.47; FG 3.19\x*Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Pita khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde za bevbevira ndavi domdorgip, Zisas Krais z…®n panan ruagirim, Fhe Bak…®me nde fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgip, nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangirga. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgirga, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar nden n…®…®Ňčgirga.
\v 39 \x - \xo 2:39 \xt Ais 57.19; Jol 2.28; FG 10.45; 14.27; Ef 2.13; 2.17\x*Fhe Bak…®me fhum mba Ňäina Ňäaarar nden n…®…®n za suaŇčgi, ana mba Ňäina Ňäaarar nden n…®…®Ňčv, ana vh…®ra mba Ňäina Ňäaarar nden tarir n…®…®nga. Ana vh…®ra mba saman harigi Ňčguir ki gumgi gu mbigi gum zumgum h…®rga gumgi gu mbigi, ana vh…®ra anan mben n…®…®nga. Nzan Fhe Bak…®me, ana mba kamgi gumgi gu mbigi, ana za won Ňäina Ňäaarar mben n…®…®n za suaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 40 \x - \xo 2:40 \xt Lo 32.5; Fi 2.15\x*Pita mba bunin mbe nzua vov, ana vh…®ra harigi buni vh…®rve phorga mbe suaŇčgi. Ana kama havharar mbe nzuav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde warir r…®v…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®v mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi phorg…®v mbat…®girga.‚ÄĚ
\v 41 \x - \xo 2:41 \xt FG 2.47; 4.4; 5.14\x*Pita mba bunin mbe nzuaim, ana buni guigira gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve thivgim, mbe ndavi domdorav Zisas z…®n panan wari ruai. Mba raan ndavi domdorgiav, Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mben vh…®rve khaŇč muuŇčgi 3,000. Mbe zav Zisas khothivav, ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi vhen vergi.
\s1 Mba Zisas khoth…®gav ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe wari t…®gav ndava bavira ki.
\p 
\v 42 \x - \xo 2:42 \xt FG 20.7\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira khaŇč t…®gav mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi nzuai buni mbararagi.
\p Mbe mbe buni mbararav, mbe wari t…®gap ndava bavira kav mben kurkurav mbe wari phorga mba pav, wari t…®gap viktum gum mb…® pav, mbe wari t…®gap phogi ga vhuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.\f e \fr 2:42 \ft Fhe Bak…®men bunin vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi vh…®rve, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Mba fhara guarara Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe kha t…®va mbui. Mba fharav wari t…®gap phoga vhuigap, fharav mba mbegap, mbe zumgum Zisas fhava s…®k gum v…®z…®na panpana vhui viktum gum mb…® ndi. \f*
\v 43 \x - \xo 2:43 \xt Mk 16.17; FG 4.33; 5.11-12\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčkar panan mirikori vh…®rve ga mbuim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe nta garav za Ňčgava mbat…®ga mbuav, wari r…®vi.
\v 44 \x - \xo 2:44 \xt FG 4.32-35; 5.12; 6.8\x*Mbe r…®vim, mba Zisas khoth…®gav ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira za ndava bavira wari t…®gap ki. Mbe wari wo bigi gari, mbe bigi, nta za mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mba bigi, nta za mbe bigi ma.
\v 45 Mbe mba t…®va mbuav, mbe vh…®ra wari won nuiani s…®giveŇč gu bigi ndi mbaim, harigi gumgi nta vhezim, mbe mba Ňčk…®…®ar, mba mba gum bigi sosuagi gumgi gu mbigir kurkurigi.
\v 46 \x - \xo 2:46 \xt Ru 24.53; FG 1.14; 20.7\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe zazera rari tug…®ra t…®gap wari t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me Phenan phogi ga vhui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe vh…®ra wari ga nzuav, warir kaav, wari won phenin vov, ndava bavira kav, ndikndigap wari phorga pi.
\v 47 \x - \xo 2:47 \xt FG 2.41; 4.33; 5.14; 6.7; 11.21; 11.24; Ro 14.18\x*Mbe mba t…®va mbuav, mbe zazera Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndiv vun kuamkuagim, mba gumgi gu mbigi nd…®knd…®gar vhuun mbe mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Guma Bak…®me rari tug…®ra t…®gap gumgi gu mbigi ndi. Ana maaŇč mbuim, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mben vh…®rve khaŇč t…®gap v…®rk…®vgi.
\c 3
\s1 Suani mbat…®gi guma mbe suani taagia nzerigi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Sng 55.17; Zo 9.1; FG 2.46; 10.3; 10.9; 10.30; 14.8\x*Raa mben, ra vera vov Ňčkotuguraagen phuni khegene ndim, ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suanga tuk ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Pita gum Zon Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suan zav Fhe Bak…®me Phenan vui.
\v 2 Mani vov garim, gumgi mbari, mbe suani mbat…®gi guma mbe ndiga zi. Mba guma, ana won niamuuŇč ndava vhera kim, ana suani mbat…®gim, ana niamuuŇč ana ruagi. Mbe zazera rari tug…®rat…®gap mba guma ndia zav, Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen mbe kha z…®n r…®gi th…®mkamani han fim, ana maaŇč pigi. Mba th…®mkamani z…® khare, Th…®mkaman Vhuuni. Mbe ana ndim maaŇč fim, ana maaŇč kav garim, gumgi gu mbigi mbe Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen verav zim, ana Ňčk…®…®a mben nzai.
\v 3 Mba guma, ana perav kav Pita gum Zon garim, mani Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen Ňčgir…® za mbuim, ana mbaram Ňčk…®…®a manin nzai.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt FG 14.9\x*Ana manin nzaim, Pita gu Zon kh…®ra ana garav, Pita khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Ňčka gan…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Pita maaŇč ana nzuaim, mba suani mbat…®gi guma, ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®gap kh…®rav mani gari, mani Ňčk…®…®ar anan n…®…®nga thi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt FG 3.16; 4.10; 16.18\x*Ana ne nd…®knd…®gap kh…®ra mani garim, Pita thav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Ňčk…®…®a ki fhuvara. Gu ki big…®n, gu ana ndun n…®…®n za mbui. Gu Nasaret guma Zisas z…®n pananan ndu nzuai, ndu khavgiv thiv…®v ruu.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Pita nen ana suaŇčgiap, mbaram vov anan guva hareŇč suirav, ana nzuaim, ana khavgia th…®gi. Ana ana nzuaim, ana khava thivara thav, ana g…®zani gum ana suani havhargim, ana nzerara th…®gi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Ais 35.6; Zo 5.14; FG 14.10\x*Ana vhemkora khavgia th…®gap rui. Ana th…®ga, ruav mani phorga vov Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen vergap, th…®va ruav, ndikndigap, fomba ga ruav, Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndiv vun kuamkuagi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt FG 4.16; 4.21\x*Ana Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndim vun kuamkua ga ruim, mba gumgi gu mbigi ana gari.
\v 10 Mbe ana gangiap ana kaŇčgi, ana mba zazera mba Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen mbe kha z…®n r…®gi th…®mkamani ga pigav, Ňčk…®…®a ga nzuav nzai guma ma. Mba th…®mkamani z…® khare, Th…®mkama Vhuuni. Mbe ana garim, ana suani nzerarga ruim, mbe ana gangiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbuav, mben nd…®knd…®gi tivgi.
\s1 Pita Fhe Bak…®me Phena vhen Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 11 Mba gumgi gu mbigi mba guman h…®gi bigeŇč mbararagiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, khuafa zav mba guma gari. Mbe zav mba guma garim, ana Pita gum Zon suirav, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen kha z…®n r…®gi vunkameŇč th…®gap ki. Mba vunkameŇč z…® khare, Soromon VunkameŇč.
\v 12 Mba gumgi gu mbigi Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap khuafua zav ana garim, Pita mba t…®va gangiap, khaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha IsreriŇč gumgi gu mbigi, nde thaŇč nzuav kha h…®gi bigeŇč gangiap, ne ga nzuav, Ňčgava mbat…®ga mbui? Nde thaŇč nzuav kh…®ra Ňčka gari? Ee, nde kha nd…®knd…®gar Ňčka mbui thi, Ňčka nuanira ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me kav o, Ňčka vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzerara kav, Ňčka kha guma ga muuŇčgim, ana suani nzerav rui thi? Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Kis 3.6; 3.15; Mt 22.32; Ru 23.13-25; FG 2.23; 7.32\x*Abraham gum Aisak, Zekop, nzan nz…®gir, Fhe Bak…®me, ana guigira z…® bak…®men won Ňčaara guma Zisas ga n…®…®Ňčgi. Mba gumara, nde anan ana pana gumgi farve kh…®ngi. Mba tugen Pairat ana fh…®rgirim, ana Ňčg…®r za mbuim, nde ana shashagiap, k…®r ana segap, khaŇč Pairat ga nzuai, ‚ÄėPairat ndu ana fh…®rgirim ana Ňčg…® thari.‚Äô
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Mt 27.15-23; Mk 15.6-14; Ru 23.13-23; Zo 19.12-15\x*Mba guma, ana guigira Fhe Bak…®men piin ki guma ma. Ana guigira guman Ňčaar ma, ana vh…®ra t…®vir vhuuiŇčra mbui guma ma. Nde ana thav, ana shashagiap, k…®r ana segap, Pairat ga nzuaim, ana harigi guma fh…®rgim, ana nde han vugi. Mba Pairat fh…®rgim, nde han vugi guma, ana guma shogi ana rimgi guma ma.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt FG 1.8; 2.24; 2.32; 2.36; 4.10\x*Nde mba shogi rimgi guma, ana guigira fharigi guma ma. Ana nza ndigip, mba zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga tuavar vui guma ma. Nde ana shogim, ana rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgim, Ňčka won r…®manira ana gangiap, Ňčka mba bigi bun nde nzuai.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Mt 9.22; FG 4.10; 14.9\x*Ňäka Zisas khoth…®gi, kha guma nde ana gari, ana vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gap, ana Zisas z…®n panan ana suani gum g…®zani ŇčkasŇčkagim, ana khavgia th…®ga rui. Zisas, ana nduara Ňčka ana khoth…®gim, ana Ňčka ana khoth…®gi t…®va muuŇčgim, ana havhargi. Ňäka ana khoth…®gi t…®vara ana kha guma ga muuŇčgim, ana ntigem nzerav thiva ruim, nde ntigem ana gari.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Ru 23.34; Zo 16.3; 1 Ko 2.8; 1 T 1.13\x*‚ÄúNde Ňčkan fegutari khueŇč guigira, gu kaŇčgi, nde wari wo gumgir panin kov, nde tuituigia khueŇč kaŇčgi fhuvara, ndera kha t…®var Zisas ga muuŇčgi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ais 50.6; 53.5; Ru 24.27; 24.44; FG 26.22; 1 Pi 1.10-11\x*Mba t…®v fhum Fhe Bak…®me won kamthooŇč gumgi ga suaŇčgim, mbe mba kameŇč suaŇčgi. Kha guma, ana ana farasarigi, ana taagip wo gumgi gu mbigi ndirga, ana fharav zaa ndigirga. Nde ntigem khar muuŇčgi bigeŇč ne Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi kamera z…®n vugav mba tegi.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt FG 2.38\x*‚ÄúNde maaŇč muuŇčgip gangip, wari nd…®knd…®g…®p ndavi domdorgirim, Fhe Bak…®me nde fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgip, nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangirga.
\v 20 Nde maaŇč muuŇčgirga, Guma Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčkar kaman nden n…®…®Ňčgirga. Ana ŇčkasŇčkar kaman nden n…®…®Ňčgirga, ana mba taagia kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarigi guma, ana ana sararim, ana nde han zir…®rga. Mba guma Fhe Bak…®me nden kurkura zav farasarigi guma ma, mba gumara khare, Zisas.
\v 21 Ana ntigem Hevenan kav, mba Fhe Bak…®me sarigi tugar rarga ki. Mba tugar Fhe Bak…®me taagip kha bigir muuŇčgirim, nta fhum ana fhara guarara nta muuŇčgi farar muuŇčgirga. Ana fhum ntan muun zav, mba kamen wo kamthooŇč gumgir Ňčaari ga suaŇčgi. Mbe ana Ňčaara mbuav ne bun suaŇčgi.
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Lo 18.15-19; FG 7.37\x*Fhum ana Ňčaara guma Moses kha suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėNden Fhe Bak…®me, ana nde phorge r…®gi guma thera ndi farim, ana na farar muuŇčgip, ana kamthooŇč guma k…®rga. Nde ana nzuai buni, nde za nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Wkp 23.29\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma nzuai buni mbararagi fhuv gumgi, mbe mba IsreriŇč gumgi gu mbigi phorg…® keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara, mbe vh…®zgirga.‚Äô \f a \fr 3:23 \ft Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma suaŇčgi buni, Fhe Bak…®me nta sararim, nta z…®rga. Mba buni kha gavar ki, mba gava z…® khare, Lo. Ndu Lo sapta 18.19 gan…®. Pita khaŇč nzuai, Zisasra mba Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma ma. \f*
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúMba fhum Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčgi kaathoori gumgi, mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma mbe Samuer, gum zumgum ana z…®n hegi Fhe Bak…®men kaathoori gumgi, mbe mba suaŇčgi bigi h…®rga tuk, ana ntigem h…®gi.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Stt 12.3; 18.18; 22.18; Ro 9.4; 9.8; Ga 3.8; 3.26\x*‚ÄúNde Fhe Bak…®men kathoori gumgi tegi tari ma. Nde mba Fhe Bak…®me n…®…®n za suaŇčgi bigi ndirga gumgi ma. Fhe Bak…®me fhum nden nz…®gi phorga nzuav mba kamen mbe suaŇčgi. Ana khaŇč nden nz…®ga Abraham ga suaŇčgi. ‚ÄėGu ndun nz…®ga the panan, gu t…®var vhuun kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigir muunga!‚Äô
\v 26 \x - \xo 3:26 \xt Mt 10.5; Ru 24.47; FG 13.32-33; 13.46\x*Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, ana mbaram fharav won Ňčaara guma ga sarigim, ana zergap fhara nde han z…®gap, t…®var vhuueŇč mbuim, nde bevbevira wari wo mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde nta thamthagi.‚ÄĚ
\c 4
\s1 Mbe Pita guma Zon ndim b…®na kh…®ngi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Mt 22.23; Ru 22.4; 22.52; FG 23.8\x*Pita gum Zon mba bunin mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuavra kim, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgi gum, mba Fhe Bak…®me Phena gari g…®…®t…®vir guman pan gum, mba SadusiŇč gumgi, mbe hegi. \f a \fr 4:1 \ft Fhe Bak…®men phena guara gari g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®var pan, ana Fhe Bak…®me phena gari guman pan kav, ana mba Fhe Bak…®men phena b…®na vhen Ňčgari g…®…®t…®vi ki. Rivai, ana mbe gari g…®mat…®va pan ki. \f*
\p 
\v 2 Mbe khueŇč kaŇčgi, mani Zisas rimgiap, taagia khavgi ne bun mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Mani vh…®ra khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas taagia khavgim, mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra taagip khav…®rga.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap ne nzuav mani ga vhegi.
\v 3 Mbe ne nzuav mani suirav, mani ga suaŇčv suan za mbui. Mbe mani ga suaŇčv suan za mbuim, ra verav vh…®zgim, mbe thav mani ndim b…®na kh…®ngi. Mbe gurmaŇčgip mani ga suanga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt FG 2.41\x*Mani mba Zisas rimgia taagia khavgim, mani ne bun mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe Zisas khoth…®gi. Mba Zisas khoth…®gi gumgira, mben vh…®rve khaŇč muuŇčgi, 5,000.
\s1 Mbe Pita gum Zon ga nzuav, mbe won buaadegi gumgi phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 5 Mba m…®timanera mba Zudain gumgir ruu gum, mben gumgir pani gum, mba ZudaiŇč t…®vir vhuuiŇč kaŇčgi gumgi, mbe zav, Zerusareman wari fugi. \f b \fr 4:5 \ft Mba wari t…®gap, phogi ga vhuav, buni nzuai gumgi, mbe Zudain buaadegi gumgi ma. Mbe Zudain k…®r…® t…®v gum bigi gari gumgi ma. \f*
\p 
\v 6 Mbe wari fugim, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman panani, Anas gum Kaiafas, Zon gum, Areksander gum, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pana nt…®…®ri, mbe zav mbe phorgap wari fugi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 21.23; FG 7.27\x*Mbe wari fugim, mbe Pita gum Zon ndigap, mben n…®man fav khaŇč nzambarer mani ga mbui, ‚ÄúŇäko ram mbui khesharigi ŇčkasŇčka ndigap, kha khesharigi bigi ga mbui? Ňäko the z…®n panan mbui?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8-9 \x - \xo 4:8-9 \xt Mt 10.19-20\x*Mbe mba nzambarer mani ga muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira Pita phorga kav ana rugim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha IsreriŇč gumgir ruu gum mben gumgir pani, nde ntigem, Ňčka kha suani mbat…®gi guma Ňčka ana kurigim, nde ne nzuav Ňčkan nzaire? Ee, nde khueŇč kaŇčgi zav nzai ti, kha guma ana ram muuŇčgiap nzerigi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt FG 2.24; 3.6; 3.13-16\x*Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip ne kaŇčgir saŇčv, nde zam khueŇč kaŇčgiri, nde IsreriŇč, nde vh…®ra za khueŇč kaŇčgiri, kha suani mbat…®gi guma, ana Nasaret guma Zisas Krais z…®n panan, ana suani guigira nzerigim, ana ntigem nde n…®man khar th…®gi. Kha guma Zisas, ndera ana shogiap, ana ndim khanarareŇč ga t…®ga fugim, ana rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgi.\f c \fr 4:10 \ft Mba buaadegi gumgira, mbe Ňčgu gari guman pana vhari Pairat ga suaŇčgim, ana Zisas shogim, ana rimgi. Ndu Ruk sapta 22.66 gan…®v, vh…®ra sapta 23.5 gan…®ri. Mbe Zisas shogim, ana rimgim, mbe khueŇč vuzvugi, mba gumgi gu mbigi, ana khoth…®g…® thari. \f*
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Sng 118.22; Ais 28.16; Mt 21.42\x*Zisas ana mba pheni ga mbui k…®m ma. Mba pheni ga mbui gumgi ana gangiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAna k…®ma mbat…®k ma.‚Äô Mbe maaŇč ana suaŇčgiap, ana thav ana ndi mbur ndarigi. Ana ntigem ana fharav mba phena b…®na suirigim, ana havhargi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Mt 1.21; FG 10.43\x*Nde khueŇč kaŇčgiri, taagip nza ndigirga guma the ki fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Kha guma Zisasra, Fhe Bak…®me ana farasarigi, nza ana z…®n panan, nza kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, ana taagip nza ndigirga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Mba gumgi ruu, mbe Pita gu Zon kaŇčgi, mani sure muuŇčgi gumani fhuvara. Mani guma kh…®nani ma. Mbe mani garim, mani r…®vi fhu, mani khaŇč t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuaim, mbe mani gangiap, nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Mbe mba nd…®knd…®gar mani ga mbuav, mbe vh…®ra kaŇčgi, mani fhum Zisas phorga kegi.
\v 14 Mbe ne kaŇčgiap, mbe mba guma garim, ana ntige nzerav mani phorga kim, mbe mani nzuai buna thueŇč Ňčgarkarga kama thueŇč ki fhu.
\p 
\v 15 Mbe thav mani ga sarigim, mani mba buaadegi gumgir pani phena thav k…®rar h…®gi. Mani k…®rar h…®gap vugim, mba gumgi mbe kama shogap khaŇč nzuai.
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Zo 11.47; FG 3.9-10\x*‚ÄúNza ram kha gumanin muuŇčrie? Mani mirikor mbe muuŇčgim, kha Zerusareman ki gumgi, mbe za mani muuŇčgi mirikor kaŇčgi. Nza ne vhagirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 17 Nza ntige ram muuŇčrie, nza muuŇčv k…®rim, kha kameŇč za kha gumgi gu mbigir Ňčg…®g…®rivgi. Nza ntigera kama havharar kha gumani ga suaŇčrim, mani wom kha guma z…® bun harigi gumgi ga suangeŇč tharga.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt FG 5.28; 5.40\x*Mbe ne wari ga suaŇčgiap, mbaram taagia manin kamgim, mani zim, mbe khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko wom Zisas z…® bun suaŇčv buna thueŇč suaŇč thari.‚ÄĚ Ňäko vh…®ra kha z…®n harigi gumgi gu mbigi kh…®v…®v mbe suaŇč thari.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt FG 5.29\x*Mbe maaŇč mani ga nzuaim, Pita gum Zon mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nd…®knd…®gi, maaŇčgi t…®v, ana Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzerigi? Ňäka Fhe Bak…®me nzuai buni z…®n Ňčg…®rga o, Ňčka nde nzuai buni z…®n Ňčg…®rga? Nde nduarira khueŇč mbararagip, ne ga nd…®knd…®g…®ri.
\v 20 \x - \xo 4:20 \xt FG 1.8; 22.15; 1 Zo 1.1-3\x*Ňäka wo th…®…®ni mp…®rarga tukt…®gi fhu. Ňäka mba gangiap, mbararagi buni gum bigi, Ňčka nta bun suanga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Mani mba kamen mbe suaŇčgim, mben buaadegi gumgir pani kama havharar buni mbarir mani ga suaŇčgiap, mani ga sarigim, mani vui. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe manin muunga big…®n thueŇč kaŇčgi fhu. Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zam mba Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigeŇč ga nd…®knd…®gap, ana z…® ndi vun kuamkuagi. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgi ruu, mbe khaŇč t…®g…®p manin muunga tuavi ndi garav ragi.
\v 22 Pita gum Zon, mani mba mirikor ga muuŇčgim, taagia nzerigi guma, anan mpari 40 kambarigi.
\s1 Mbe Zisas buni bun suanga ŇčkasŇčka ndir zav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 23 Mba buaadegi gumgir pani Pita gum Zon fh…®rgim, mani taagiap, mbe mba Zisas buni khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui nt…®…®ri han vugap, mbaram mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani gum mben gumgir pani suaŇčgi buni bun mbe nzuai.
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Kis 20.11; Neh 9.6; Sng 146.6\x*Mani mba bunin mbe suaŇčgim, mbe mba buni mbararagiap, mbe za wari fugap, ndava bavira kav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ndu kha buiva mbuav, kha nuiana mbuav mbas…®ga muuŇčgiap, ana ki bigi, ndu za nta muuŇčgi.
\v 25 \x - \xo 4:25 \xt Sng 2.1-2\x*Fhum, ndun Ňäina Ňäaar kha kamen nzan nz…®k Devit ga n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana ndun Ňčaara guma ma, ana kha kamen ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana mba kamen Devit ga n…®…®Ňčgim, ana khaŇč suaŇčgi,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄėKha gumgi gu mbigi, mbe thaŇč nzuav pim ndavi shi? Kha harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe thaŇč nzuav fhura kaa shogap t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui?
\q1 
\v 26 Mba Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani, mbe za kha nuianan, mbe za ntarir muun zav ntari bigi bevah…®rga. Mba Ňčguir gumgir pani, mbe wari fug…®p, Guma Bak…®me mbev…®v, ana ndi n…®…®aŇč p…®nga. Ana mba taagi za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav farasarigi guma, mbe vh…®ra ana mbev…®v ana ndim n…®…®aŇč p…®nga.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Mt 27.1-2; Mk 15.1; Ru 23.1; 23.7-11; Zo 18.28-29; FG 3.13\x*‚ÄúKha kameŇč guigi guarara, Herot gum Pontius Pairat, mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gum IsreriŇč, mbe kha Ňčgu bak…®mera wari fugap, ndun Ňčaara guman Ňčaar Zisas, ndu fhum ana farasarigim, mbe ana mbevav ana ndim, n…®…®aŇč mp…®…®av ana muuŇčgi.
\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt FG 2.23; 3.18\x*Mbe mba t…®var ana mbuav, mbe wari won vuzvuga z…®n vui fhuvara, mbe ndun nd…®knd…®k gum vuzvugara z…®n vov mba t…®var ana muuŇčgi. Ndu won ŇčkasŇčka bak…®men panan, ndu fhum suaŇčgi, mba t…®v guigira h…®g…®rga.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt FG 9.27; 13.46; 19.8; Ef 6.19\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Guma Bak…®me, ndu ntigem mbe kha r…®r…®var nza nd…®…®v nza nzuai buni, ndu za nta nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Nza ndun Ňčaara gumgi ma, ndu nzan kurari. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip nzan kurarim, nza khaŇč t…®g…®p th…®g…® havhargip, ndu buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčv r…®v…®rga fhu.
\v 30 Ndu vh…®ra won farven r…®…®i gumgi ga surim, mben r…®mr…®…® vh…®z…®rim, ndu vh…®ra won Ňčaara guman Ňčaar Zisas z…®n panan mbark…®rga mirikorir muuŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt FG 2.4; 4.29; 16.26\x*Mbe Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav mba khesharigi suambarar ana muuŇčgim, mbe mba wari fugap ki phen, ana mbe kh…®gap n…®…®Ňčkui. Mba phen mbe kh…®gap n…®…®Ňčkuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar zav, mbe givav, mbe rugim, mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Mbe khaŇč t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me buni bun vhuuiŇč bun nzuav, mbe r…®vi fhu.
\s1 Mba Zisas buni vhuuiŇč khothivav ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za warir kurkurigi.
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 4:32 \xt FG 2.44-45; 2 Ko 13.11; 1 Pi 3.8\x*Mba Zisas buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za ndava bavira kav, wari t…®gav nd…®knd…®ga bavira mbui. Mbe the wo big…®n the gangiap khaŇč nzuai fhu, ‚ÄúKhe na big…®nara,‚ÄĚ Fhuvara. Mbe bigi za mbe bigira.
\v 33 \x - \xo 4:33 \xt FG 1.8; 1.22; 2.45-47\x*Mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Zisas rimgiav taagia khavgi buni vhuuiŇč, mbe nta bun nzuai. Mbe buni ŇčkasŇčka kim, Fhe Bak…®me guigira mba gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarga vuzvuk bak…®me kav, ana guigira t…®var vhuuŇčra mbe mbui.
\v 34-35 \x - \xo 4:34-35 \xt FG 2.45\x*Ana maaŇč mbe mbuim, mba gumgi gu mbigi r…®gar guma the mba gum bigi tivgi fhu. Mba gumgi, mbe za nuian gum pheni kav, mbe nta ndim mbaim, harigi gumgi nta vhezim, mbe ntan Ňčk…®…®a ndi. Mbe mba Ňčk…®…®a ndiav, mbe nta ndia zav, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi ga nd…®…®i. Mbe mba Ňčk…®…®ar mbe nd…®…®im, mbe mba Ňčk…®…®ar, mba bigi sosuagi gumgi gum, bigi tivgi gumgi, mbe mba bigir, mba tivgi bigi tug…®ra t…®gap mbe nd…®…®i.
\v 36 \x - \xo 4:36 \xt FG 11.22-26; 13.2-3\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, guma mbe, ana maaŇč ki, ana z…® Zosep.
\p Mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe vh…®ra kha z…®n ana t…®gi, mba z…® khare, Barnabas. Mba z…® n…®…®Ňčge khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGumgir ndavi havhari guma ma.‚ÄĚ Barnabas, ana mbe kha z…®n r…®gi guma mbe ma, ana Rivai guma ma. Ana vh…®ra Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rigen ki guma ma.
\v 37 Ana won nuiana s…®ga mueŇč ndi mbaim, harigi guma mbe ne ga vhezgim, ana mba Ňčk…®…®a ndiga zav mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi ga n…®…®Ňčgi.
\c 5
\s1 Ananaias gum Safaira Fhe Bak…®me guiguig…®r za mbui.
\p 
\v 1 Mbe mba t…®va mbuim, guma mbevi, ana z…® Ananaias, ana muuŇč z…® khare, Safaira. Mani kav, ana man Ananaias, ana won nuiana s…®ga mueŇč ndim mbaim, harigi guma mbe ne ga vhezgi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt FG 4.34-37\x*Mba guma mba nuianeŇč ga vhezgim, ana mba Ňčk…®…®a ndigap, ana mba Ňčk…®…®a mbari, ana wandi nta ndigap, nta ndi mbur t…®gi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, ana muuŇč vh…®ra ne kaŇčgi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi guigap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu won nuiana s…®ga mueŇč ndim mbaim, mbe ne ga vhezgim, gu za mba Ňčk…®…®a ndiga zav nde nd…®…®i.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Lo 23.21; Ru 22.3; Zo 13.2\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Pita mbaram khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAnanaias, ndu ram muuŇčgiap fhura Satan garim, ana zav ndu ndava vhen vergap, ndu nzuaim, ndu Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara guiguigi. Ndu mbarara! Ndu mba nuianeŇč ndi mbaim, mbe ne ga vhezgi Ňčk…®…®a, ndu nta sh…®rav wo ndi mbari ndiga zorgi.
\v 4 Mbe ndu nzuaim, ndu mba nuiana s…®geŇč ndi mbaim, harigi guma ne ga vhezgi fhuvara, ndu vuzvuk ma. Ndu ne ndi mbarav Ňčk…®…®a ndigi, nta vh…®ra ndun Ňčk…®…®a ma, ndu ram mba Ňčk…®…®ar muun saŇčv, ndu vuzvuk ma. Ndu ram muuŇčgiap kha nd…®knd…®ga mbat…®ga ndigi? Ndu khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…® thari. ‚ÄėGu kha gumgira guiguigi.‚Äô Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ndu Fhe Bak…®mera guiguigi.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Pita nen Ananaias ga nzuaim, Ananaias ne mbararara thav, k…®gira ndarav, za rimgi. Ananaias rimgim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba ana h…®gi bigeŇč mbararagiap, mbe guigira rivgi.
\v 6 Ananaias rimgim, mba gumgir Ňčkaa, mbe zav shagir ana khuma ndogiap, ana ndigap, mbogar r…®g…®r zav vui.
\p 
\v 7 Mba gumgir Ňčkaa, mbe Ananaias ndiga vugim, aua phuni khegene vh…®zgim, ana muuŇč zav, mba phena vhen veri. Ana wo manan h…®gi bigeŇč, ana ne kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 8 Ana zav mba phena vhen vergim, Pita khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khar na suaŇč, Ňčko mba won nuianeŇč ndi mbaim, mbe ne ga vhezgi Ňčk…®…®a, ntara kharere?‚ÄĚ Pita ne nzuaim, Ananaiasan muuŇč ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAhaŇč, ntara mbare.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Pita mbaram khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko thaŇč nzuav wani t…®gap kama shogiap, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaarar mpari? Ndu gan…®! Ndu mana ndiga vov ana mp…®rigi gumgira mbu th…®mkamanin mbu thivgi. Mbe ntige vh…®ra ndu ndigi Ňčg…®g…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Pita maaŇč ana nzuavra thagim, ana k…®gira Pita Ňčkarveni n…®mara ndarav, za rimgi. Ana rimgim, mba gumgir Ňčkaa, mbe zerav ana khuma gangiap, ana khuma ndiga vov, ana mana mboga han ana ndim mbok ga t…®gi.
\v 11 Mba bigeŇč mani man gum, manin h…®gim, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana buni vhuuiŇč z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, gum mba harigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba bigen kameŇč mbararagiap, mbe za guigira r…®r…®va mbat…®ga muuŇčgi.
\s1 Mbark…®rga mbark…®rga mirikori nta hi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt FG 2.43; 4.32; 14.3; Ro 15.19; 2 Ko 12.12\x*Mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mbark…®rga mbark…®rga mirikori, mbe mba gumgi gu mbigi r…®gar nta mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe za wari t…®gap ndava bavira kav wari t…®gap Fhe Bak…®men phena b…®na vhen verav, mbe wari t…®gap Soromon vunkamen ki.
\v 13 Mbe kim, mba mbe phorga ki fhuv nt…®…®ri, mbe mbe ndiv vun kuamkuagi. Mbe mbe ndiv vun kuamkuav, mbe vh…®ra mben rivav, maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe mbe phorga ki fhu.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt FG 2.41; 21.20\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera, mbe Zisas khothivav zav, ana khothivi nt…®…®ri vhen veri.
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Mt 9.21; 14.36; FG 19.12\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi mbui mirikori kaŇčgi. Mbe nta kaŇčgiap, mbaram mba r…®…®i gumgi gu mbigi, mbe kaagir mbe ndia zav mba Pita rui tuav gaanin mbaim, mbe ki. Mbe khueŇč nzuav Pita mba tuavar mbur Ňčg…®p khar z…®rim, ra ana sh…®g…®rim, ana tum Ňčg…®p mba r…®…®i gumgi vharim, mbe r…®mr…®…® vh…®z…®rga.\f a \fr 5:15 \ft Mba gumgi gu mbigi khueŇč khoth…®gi. Ra Pita ga sh…®rarga ana tum, Ňčg…®p mba r…®…®i gumgi gu mbigi vharga, mba r…®…®i gumgi gu mbigi mben r…®mr…®…® vh…®zgirga. \f*
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Mk 6.56; FG 19.11-12\x*Mba Zerusareman han ana gaar ki Ňčgui bak…®vir ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra zav, mbe Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi mbui bigi gari. Mbe vh…®ra r…®…®i gumgi gu ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi vhen dav farfagi gumgi, mbe vh…®ra mben kov zi. Mbe mben kov zim, mbe vh…®ra r…®mr…®…® vh…®zav, mba ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi ki gumgi, mba ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi mbe thamtha vuim, mbe taagia nzezerigi.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me enseri, mbe mba Zisas farasegi gumgir kurigim, mbe b…®na thav k…®rar hegi.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt FG 4.1-2; 4.6\x*Mbe taagia nzezerigim, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan won khurkhuu SadusiŇč gumgi mbarir kov, mbe mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi mbui bigi gangiap, mbe guigira ndavi mbat…®gi.
\v 18 Mbe ndavi mbat…®giap, mbaram khavgiap, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi suigiap, mbe ndim mba gumgi mbat…®gi phorgap b…®na suegi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt FG 12.7-10; 16.26\x*Mbe mbe ndim b…®na suegim, mba maan Fhe Bak…®men enser mbe zav, mbe nzuav mba phena t…®vaneŇč th…®ma fh…®rgiap, mben kov k…®rar hegi.
\v 20 Ana mbe ndim k…®rar mbarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Ňčg…®p, mba Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen Ňčgir…® thivgip, za mba Zisas z…®n vui t…®vir Ňčkaa bun mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Mba Fhe Bak…®me enser maaŇč mbe suaŇčgim, m…®n thugim, mbe mba ana suaŇčgi kameŇč z…®n vov, mbe vov mba Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen vergap, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vi.
\p Mbe mbe kh…®vim, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan gum anan khurkhuu, mbe zav hegap, mbaram mbe won buaadegi gumgi gum mba Zudain gumgir ruu, mbe za mben kamgim, mbe zav wari fugi. Mbe wari fugap, mbaram, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi ga nzuav, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari gumgi ga nzuav kama ndi mbarigi. Mbe mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir kov mben han z…®rga.
\v 22 Mbe kama ndim mbarigim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®…®t…®vi vov mba phena t…®vanen vugap garim, mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi ki fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap gangia thav, taagia vov khaŇč mba gumgi ruu ga nzuai,
\v 23 ‚ÄúNza vov, mba phena t…®vaneŇč garim, ana th…®…® za puigim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®…®t…®vi, mbe mba phena th…®…®r kaa garav thivgiav ki. Mbe thivgiap kim, mbe mba phena t…®vaneŇč th…®ma fh…®rgiap, vhen verav garim, guma the mba phena vhen ki fhu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap gangiap, thav mba kameŇč bun mbe nzuaim, mba Fhe Bak…®men phena gari g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan gum mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani, mbe mba kameŇč mbararagiap, guigira nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Mbe nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba bigeŇč ntige ram muuŇčgip h…®g…®rie?‚ÄĚ \f b \fr 5:24 \ft KhaŇč Grikar kaman, kha kameŇč mbe tuituigia ne n…®…®Ňč sh…®rigi fhuvara. Mbe gumgi mbari khaŇč muuŇčgiap mba kameŇč dorgi, ‚ÄúMbe nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėThag…®na bigeŇč ntige h…®g…®rie?‚Äô ‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 25 Mbe maaŇč wari ga nzuav kim, guma mbe zav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúAi, nde kaŇčgire? Nde mba suigiap phena t…®vaneŇč ga suegi gumgi, mbe mbu Fhe Bak…®men phena b…®na vhen kav, mbu gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuav ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Mt 14.5; 21.26\x*Mba guma zav maaŇč mbe suaŇčgim, mba g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan won g…®…®t…®vir kov, mbe vov mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir kov, mbe zi. Mbe mben dama mbui fhuvara, mbe mba gumgi gu mbigi Ňčk…®…®a mbe seg…®rim, mbe rimgirga nen rivgi.
\s1 Mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun mba buaadegi gumgi ga suangen rivgi fhuvara.
\p 
\v 27 Mba g…®…®t…®vi, mbe Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir kov zav mbe ndim, mbe won buaadegi gumgi n…®man fegi. Mbe mbe ndim fegim, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan kha nzambarir mbe mbui,
\v 28 \x - \xo 5:28 \xt Mt 27.25; FG 2.23; 2.36; 4.18; 7.52\x*‚ÄúNza kha guma z…® bun kha gumgi gum mbigi ga suangen guigira nde th…®vigi. Nza nde th…®vigim, nde kaadogiap, ana z…® bun nzuavra kim, kha Zerusareman fhain ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zam nde nzuai buni mbararagi. Nde mba buni nzuav, ana shogi ana rimgi nen nza dagi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 5:29 \xt FG 4.19\x*Mbe ne nzuaim, Pita gum mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi mbe, mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Nza guma the suaŇčgi kameŇč z…®n Ňčg…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara!
\v 30 \x - \xo 5:30 \xt FG 3.15; 10.39; 13.29; Ga 3.13; 1 Pi 2.24\x*Nde mba shogiap, ndi khanarareŇč ga t…®gap fugim rimgi guma Zisas, nzan ndegir Fhe Bak…®me taagiap ana khavgi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 5:31 \xt FG 2.33-34; 3.15; Ef 1.20; Fi 2.9; Hi 2.10; 12.2\x*Fhe Bak…®me ana khavgiap, ana ndiga ndav, ana ndim won guva haren fagi. Ana ntigem tuavar nza kh…®vi guma kav, ana vh…®ra taagia nza ndi guma ki. Ana vh…®ra nza IsreriŇč, ana nzan kurkurarga, nza ndavi domdor…®rga, ana nza fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®z…®v, nta nd…®knd…®g…® tharga.
\v 32 \x - \xo 5:32 \xt Zo 15.26-27; FG 1.8; 2.4; 10.44\x*Nde nza gari, nza mba Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi, nza nta gangiap, nza mba bigi bun nzuai. Nza nta bun nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar, ana vh…®ra mba bigi bun nzuai. Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar mba wo z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga n…®…®Ňčgi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Gamarier khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha buaadegi gumgi, nde mbarara kha Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir muuŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 \x - \xo 5:33 \xt FG 2.37; 7.54\x*Pita gu mbe kha bunin mba buaadegi gumgi ga suaŇčgim, mba buaadegi gumgi mba buni mbararagiap, mbe guigira ndavi shigap, mbaram mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi shog…®rim, mbe vh…®zgi zav mbui.
\v 34 Mbe maaŇč mben muun za mbuim, mba buaadegi gumgi r…®gar bomadagi guma mbe ki. Ana Fherasi guma ma, ana z…®, Gamarier. Ana Fhe Bak…®me t…®vir vhuuin mbe kh…®vi guma ma. Ana maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za ana z…® ndim vun kuamkuagi. Ana khavgia th…®gap, kama havharar khaŇč mba gumgi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi ga sararim, mbe kha buaadegi gumgi kav buni nzuai ŇčaneŇč thav k…®rar heg…®p, tuga t…®vaneŇčra keg…®p, taagip vhen zir…®rga.‚ÄĚ \f c \fr 5:34 \ft Por fhum Zisas z…®n panan ruagi fhuv tugen, Gamarier, ana shure muuŇčgi mparmpare kegi. Ndu FG 22.3 gan…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 35 Gamarier maaŇč suaŇčgim, mbe mbe sarigim, mbe k…®rar hegim, Gamarier mbaram khaŇč mba harigi buaadegi gumgi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha IsreriŇč gumgi, nde big…®n thuen kha gumgir muun saŇčv, nde zaaŇčtuig…®p nd…®knd…®ga vhuun muuŇčgip big…®n thuen mben muuŇčri.
\v 36 \x - \xo 5:36 \xt FG 21.38\x*Nde kaŇčgi, ruar…®mnera Tiudas h…®gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėGu guma bak…®me ma, gu z…® ki.‚Äô Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, 400 gumgi ana z…®n vuav, ana nzuai buni khothivi. Mbe ana z…®n vuav kim, mbe ana shogim, ana rimgim, ana z…®n vui gumgi, mbe za ra vegim, ana mbui Ňčaar fhura fh…®rger…®gi.
\v 37 \x - \xo 5:37 \xt Ru 2.1-2\x*Ana Ňčaar fh…®rger…®gap, mbar vuim, mbe mba gumgi gu mbigi z…®ri ndi tugen, Gariri guma Zudas, ana h…®gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėGu z…® ki.‚Äô Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram gumgi mbari ana mbe ndigim, mbe ana z…®n vui. Mbe ana z…®n vuim, ana h…®gap ntara khavgim, mbe ana shogim, ana rimgim, mba ana z…®n vov ana khoth…®gi gumgi, mbe mbara muuŇčgiap rav tamtam vegim, ana Ňčaar vh…®ra fh…®rger…®gi.
\v 38 \x - \xo 5:38 \xt Ais 8.10; Mt 15.13\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap gangiap, gu ntige nde nzuai, nde fhumra big…®n thuen khein muuŇč thari. Nde fhura mbe gan…®ri, mbe k…®ri. Mbe kha mbui Ňčaar, ana guma wo nd…®knd…®g…®ra, ana khavgip ana muunga, nde gan…®nga, mba Ňčaar, ana mbat…®girga.
\v 39 \x - \xo 5:39 \xt Ru 21.15; FG 7.51; 9.5; 1 Ko 1.25\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®me nduara mba Ňčaara khavgip, mba Ňčaarar mbe farve kh…®ngirim, mbe muunga, nde mbe th…®varga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde maaŇč muunga, nde Fhe Bak…®me phorga shogi.‚ÄĚ
\p Gamarier mba kamen mba buaadegi gumgi ga suaŇčgim, mbe mben farfa thagi.
\v 40 \x - \xo 5:40 \xt FG 4.18\x*Mbe thav wom mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir kamgim, mbe taagia vhen verim, mbe mbe nzuaim, mbe phiv…®gar mbe khargiap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde wom Zisas z…® bun suaŇč thari.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbe sarigim, mbe k…®rar hegap, wari vui.
\v 41 \x - \xo 5:41 \xt Mt 5.10-12; 1 Pi 4.13\x*Mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi k…®rar hegap, wari vov Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigi, ana kha nd…®knd…®gar mbe mbui, mbe Zisas z…®n panan mem…®ra ndirga tukt…®gi.
\v 42 \x - \xo 5:42 \xt FG 9.22; 17.3\x*Mbe k…®rar hegap, mbe rari tug…®rat…®gap, mbe Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen verap, vh…®ra mba gumgi gu mbigi phenin vov, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav mbe nzuav, Zisas bun mbe nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas, ana Fhe Bak…®me taagip kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarav sarigi guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\c 6
\s1 Mbe Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgir kurkura zav harath…®gi gumgir farasegi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt FG 2.41; 4.35; 5.14; 9.29\x*Mba tugivigen mba Zisas farasegi Ňčaara gumgi mba Ňčaara mbuim, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mben vh…®rve guigira vh…®rk…®vgi. Mbe vh…®rk…®vgiap, mba Grik kama nzuai nt…®…®ri, mbe Aram kama nzuai nt…®…®ri phorga vhegi. Mbe mbe vhegap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde rari tug…®ra t…®gap zazera mban mba mba tivgi gumgi gu mbigir kurkurav, nde mban nzan mani rimgi mbigir kurkurigi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 6:1 \ft Araman kam, ana Zudia gum Gariri fhain ki gumgi gu mbigi nzuai kam ma. Ana maneŇč bisanera Hibruin kama fara muuŇčgi. \f*
\p 
\v 2 Mbe ne wari ga nzuaim, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi mbaram mben kamgim, mbe zim, mbe khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNza kha Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suanga Ňčaara thav, mbara gan…®v nta shaman muunga ne nzerigi fhuvara.
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt Lo 1.13; FG 1.21; 16.2; 1 T 3.7\x*Nde nzan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nde wari r…®gar harath…®gi gumgi, mbe kha gumgi gu mbigi n…®man z…®ri vhuuiŇč kav, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar guigira mbe phorga kim, mbe nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki. Nza mbe ndim feg…®rim, mbe kha mban Ňčaara gan…®nga.
\v 4 Nza nduarira zazera Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suaŇčv zazera Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin gumgi gu mbigi kh…®v…® mbe suanga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt FG 8.5\x*Mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi ne nzuaim, mba gumgi gu mbigi guigira ne vuzvugi. Mbe ne vuzvugiap mbaram, Stiven ndim fagi, ana guigira Fhe Bak…®me buni z…®n vov, ana khoth…®gap th…®ga havhargim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira ana phorga ki guma ma. Mbe ana ndim fav, Firip ndim fav, Prokorus ndim fav, Nikanor ndim fav, Timon ndim fav, Parmenas ndim fav, Nikoras ndim fagi. Nikoras, ana Antiok guma ma. Ana Zuda guma fhuvara, ana mbe ZudaiŇč mbe rotu mbui Fhe Bak…®me, ana mbe phorgap ana rotu mbui.
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt FG 13.3; 14.23\x*Mbe mba gumgi ndim fegap, mbaram mbe ndim mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgir n…®man fegim, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi mbe phorgap, mbe nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, wari won farver mbe suav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Mbe mba Ňčaarar muunga.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt Zo 12.42; FG 2.41; 12.24; 16.5; Kor 1.6\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai kameŇč za mbar vuim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe Zerusareman kav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararav, ana z…®n vov ana khoth…®gi. Mbe ana z…®n vuim, mba Fhe Bak…®men rotu gari gumgir pani vh…®rvera, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui.
\s1 Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe Stiven ga nzuav nzuai.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt FG 2.43\x*Fhe Bak…®me guigira Stivenan kurkurav, ŇčkasŇčka bak…®men ana n…®…®Ňčgim, ana mba gumgi gu mbigi r…®gar mbark…®rga mirikori bak…®vi ana nta mbui.
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt 2 T 1.15\x*Ana maaŇč mbuim, gumgi mbari mbe khavgiap, ana phorgap vhegap ana nzuai. Mba ana phorga vhegap ana nzuai gumgi, mbe kha z…®n r…®gi Fhe Bak…®me buni mbaragi phena gumgi ma, mba phena z…® khare, B…®kb…®…®gi Gumgi. Mbe mba z…®n mbe r…®gi, mbe Sairini, ki ZudaiŇč, mbe Areksandrian ki ZudaiŇč gum, mba Sirisia Ňčgu bak…®me gum, Esia Ňčgu bak…®me, mbe mba Ňčguir ki gumgi ma. \f b \fr 6:9 \ft Mba b…®kb…®…®gia ki gumgi, mbe fhum fhura harigi gumgir Ňčaara gumgi kegi, mbe ntigem mbe thav b…®kb…®…®gi. \f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Ais 54.17; Ru 21.15; FG 5.39\x*Mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ŇčkasŇčka gum nd…®knd…®ga vhuun Stiven ga nd…®…®im, mbe ana nzuai buna thueŇč daaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Mt 26.59-61\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbovara thav, mbaram mbarara zorga vov, gumgi mbari raaŇč shav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Stiven mbararagim, ana buni mbat…®gir Moses ga nzuav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me ga suaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mba gumgi gu mbigi ndavi khavav, mbaram mba mben gumgir pani ndavi khavav, vh…®ra mba ZudaiŇč t…®vir vhuuiŇč kaŇčgi gumgi, mbe vh…®ra mben ndavi khavgi. Mbe mben ndavi khavgim, mbe mbara vov, Stiven suirav ana ndigap, wari won buaadegi gumgir han vugi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Jer 26.11\x*Mbe ana ndiga vugap, mbaram gumgi mbari ndim fegim, mbe fhura ana sh…®sh…®gap, ana guiguigap bunin ana sav ana nzuai. Mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKha guma, ana zazera buni mbat…®gir Fhe Bak…®me phena nzuav, vh…®ra ana muun zav suaŇčgi t…®vi ga nzuai.
\v 14 Nza vh…®ra ana mbararagi, ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėKha Nasaret Guma Zisas, ana kha Fhe Bak…®me phena farfagip, kha Moses nza suaŇčgi t…®vi, ana ntan kurav harigi t…®vi ndim t…®g…®rga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 15 Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, mba buaadegi gumgi, mbe maaŇč piigia kav, kh…®rav Stiven gari. Mbe ana garim, ana khom guigira Ňčgara gari. Mbe ana garim, ana Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe khoma gari fara muuŇčgi.
\c 7
\s1 Stiven buaadegi gumgi phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Mbe mba ganganan ana mbuav, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan Stivenan nzav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumgi khar ndu sav ndu nzuai buni, nta guigira buni guari o, mbe guiguigi buni?‚ÄĚ
\v 2 \x - \xo 7:2 \xt Stt 11.31\x*\x - \xo 7:2 \xt Stt 12.1\x*Ana maaŇč ana nzuaim, Stiven ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nan ndegi, nde mbarara. Nzan nz…®k Abraham, ana fhum Mesopotemia nuianara ki, ana zumgum khavgiap, Haranan vugi. Ana mbara kim, mba ŇčkasŇčka ki Fhe Bak…®me Hevenan kegap, anan h…®gi.
\v 3 Fhe Bak…®me ana h…®gap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu won Ňčgu n…®…®Ňčgen won nuiana thav, won fegutari thav, harigi nuianen Ňčg…®ri. Gu mba nuianen ndu kh…®varga.‚Äô
\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4 \xt Stt 11.31; 12.4\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Abraham Kardia nuianeŇč thav, vov Haranan ki. Ana vugap maaŇč kim, ana ndia rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana sarigim, ana zav nde ntige khar ki nuianeŇč z…®gap, nen kegi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt Stt 12.7; 13.15; 15.3; 15.18; 17.8; 26.3; 48.4; Lo 2.5\x*Abraham mba tugen Fhe Bak…®me ara heav nuiana s…®ga thuen ana nd…®…®v, khaŇč ana suaŇčgi fhuvara. Khe ndun nuiana s…®geŇč ma, ndun tari zumgum ne gan…®nga, ana maaŇč ana suaŇčgi fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®me guigira khaŇč ana suaŇčgi, ana zumgum mba nuianan ana n…®…®Ňčgirim, ana won tari gum nz…®gir kov, mba nuianeŇč gan…®nga. Mba tugen vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me mba kamen Abraham ga suaŇčgim, Abraham, ana mba tugen, ana tara the tegi fhu, ana fhura ki.
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6 \xt Stt 15.16; Kis 12.40; Ga 3.17\x*\x - \xo 7:6 \xt Stt 15.13-14\x*Abraham mba tugen fhura kim, Fhe Bak…®me khaŇč ana suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėNdun tari gum nz…®gi, mbe Ňčg…®p, harigi nt…®…®rir nuianan k…®rga. Mbe mben nuianan k…®v, mbe vh…®ra fhura 400 mparir mben Ňčaara gumgi k…®rga. Mba harigi Ňčgun nt…®…®ri t…®vi mbat…®gir mben muunga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 7:7 \xt Kis 3.12\x*Mbe maaŇč mben muunga, gu maaŇč mbe mbuim, mbe fhura mben Ňčaara gumgi ki Ňčgu, gu mben farfagirga,‚Äô Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėGu maaŇč mba harigi Ňčgun muuŇčgip, gu mbe ndigirim, mbe z…®v kha Ňčgun nan ndikndig…®p nan z…® ndi vun kuamkuarga.‚Äô
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt Stt 17.10-14; 21.2-4; 25.26; 29.31‚Äď35.18\x*Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram, kha kamen Abraham phorga nzuai, ndu won tari gu nz…®gir fooŇčri. Nde warir fooŇčv, khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®ri, gu nde phorga suaŇčgi kameŇč ma. Fhe Bak…®me mba kamen Abrahama suaŇčgim, ana mbara kav Aisak tegi. Ana Aisak tegim, ana h…®gim, s…®garath…®gi raa h…®gim, ana mbaram Aisakan fooŇčgi. Ana Aisakan fooŇčgim, ana vhuuŇčgiap, mbaram Zekop tegi. Aisak Zekop tegim, Zekop vhuuŇčgiap mbaram, mba nzan 12 th…®gi nz…®gi tegi.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt Stt 37.11; 37.28; 39.2; 39.21; 41.37-41\x*‚ÄúMba tugen nzan nz…®gi, mbe wari t…®gap kav, mbe panara thav wari won Ňčgugage Zosep gari. Mbe panara thav, ana garav, mbaram ana thumkegap, ana ndim harigi Ňčgui ga n…®…®Ňčgi. Mbe ana mbe nd…®…®im, mbe ana vhezgiap, ana ndigap, vov Idz…®van ana ndim mbaim, mbe vh…®ra Idz…®van ana vhezgi. Mba tugen, mbe maaŇč Zosep ga mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me Zosep phorga ki.
\v 10 Ana ana phorga kav anan kurkurigim, ana mba simt…®gi ndi. Ana mba simt…®gi ndim, Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin Zosep ga nd…®…®im, ana mba Idz…®van ki guman pana phorga nzuaim, ana ana nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč gangiap, mbaram Zosep ndim guman panan fagim, ana Idz…®p Ňčgu garav, vh…®ra ana gari guman pana phen gum bigi, ana za nta gari.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 7:11 \xt Stt 41.54; 42.1-2\x*‚ÄúZosep, Idz…®van guman pan ana ndim fagim, ana ana bigi gari guman pan kav kim, mba tugen mba tivgim, thir vh…®zi tuga bak…®me Idz…®p Ňčgu bak…®me gum mba Kenan fhain h…®gi. Mba thir vh…®zi, tuga mbat…®k mben h…®gim, nzan ndegi mbe maaŇč mba ndigire?
\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12 \xt Stt 42.1-5\x*Mbe thir vh…®zav, kav, nzan nz…®ga Zekop, ana mbararagim, mbe Idz…®van mba ki. Ana ne mbararagiap, mbaram nzan ndegi ga sarigim, mbe fharigi ruruain, mbe mba nzuav Idz…®van vui.
\v 13 \x - \xo 7:13 \xt Stt 45.1; 45.16\x*Mbe mba fharigi ruruain Idz…®van vegap, mba vhezgiap, zav nta pav kim, nta vh…®zgim, mbe taagia phenat…®t…®gap wari wom Idz…®van vui. Mbe vov mba vhezim, Zosep wo bun mbe nzuai, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai. Gu Zozevra khare, gu nden Ňčguk ma. Nde fhum na thumkegap, na ndim n…®…®Ňčgim, mbe na ndiga z…®gim, gu khaŇč ki. Zosep wo bun mbe suaŇčgim, zumgum mba Idz…®van ki guman pan vh…®ra mba Zosep phorger…®gi nt…®…®ri, ana vh…®ra mbe kaŇčgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Stt 45.9-10; 45.17-18; 46.27\x*Zosep wo bun mbe suaŇčgiap, mbaram zumgum won ndia Zekop ga nzuav Ňčk…®…®a muuŇčgi. Ana ana nzuav Ňčk…®…®a muuŇčgim, ana mbaram Idz…®van ndav, mbaram za won tari gum mben muuiŇč gum bigi, ana za mben kov Idz…®van ndagi. Ana ndav kov ndagi gumgi gu mbigir vh…®rve khare, 75.
\v 15 \x - \xo 7:15 \xt Stt 46.1-7; 49.33\x*Mbe ndav Idz…®van kav, Zekop rimgim, nzan nz…®gi vh…®ra vh…®zgi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 7:16 \xt Stt 23.3-16; 33.19; 50.7-13; Jos 24.32\x*Mani rimgim, mbe zumgum mani Zekop gum Zosep hari ndia vov Sekeman Abraham fhum Hamoran tari han Ňčk…®…®ar vhezgi k…®ma thoon muuŇčgi mbogir mani hari ndim mboga t…®gi.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Stt 15.5; Sng 105.24-25; FG 7.5-7\x*\x - \xo 7:17 \xt Kis 1.7-8\x*‚ÄúMbe ndav maaŇč kim, mba Fhe Bak…®me fhum Abraham ga suaŇčgi kameŇč ne mba t…®rga tuk h…®r za mbui. Mba IsreriŇč Idz…®van ndav, maaŇč kav, mben sh…®k guigira k…®vgiap, mbe guigira tavahorgi.
\v 18 Mbe tavahorgiap Idz…®van kim, mba tugen, harigi guman pana mbe Idz…®p Ňčgu gari. Mba guman pan, ana Zosep kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 19 \x - \xo 7:19 \xt Kis 1.10-22\x*Mba Ňčgu gari guman pan, ana Idz…®p garav, mbaram fhura sh…®sh…®gap, nzan gumgi gu mbigi ga mbuav, mben farfav, mbaram nzan mbigi tari ruaim, ana mba tari fusurim, nta vh…®z…®r zav mbe nzuai.
\v 20 \x - \xo 7:20 \xt Kis 2.2; Hi 11.23\x*Mba Idz…®p gari guman pan maaŇč mbe mbui tugen, Moses niamuuŇč ana ruagi. Moses vh…®ra, ana tara kh…®n fhuvara, Fhe Bak…®me ana garim, ana guigira guman khoman vhuuŇč ma. Ana niamuuŇč ana ruagim, ana wo ndia phenara kim, k…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgi.
\v 21 \x - \xo 7:21 \xt Kis 2.3-10\x*Mba k…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgim, mbe zumgum ana ndigap, ana ndia phena thav vov, k…®rar harigi ŇčaneŇč ga t…®gi. Mbe ana ndim t…®gim, mbe Idz…®p Ňčgu gari guman pana kambik ana gangiap, mbaram ana wo mbuigi.
\v 22 Ana Moses ndigim, ana mba Idz…®p Ňčgu gari guman pana phenan kav, ana kama gegap kim, mbe won t…®vir ana kh…®vav kim, ana vhuuŇčgiap, za mba Idz…®viŇč t…®vi gum mben bigi, ana za nta kaŇčgi. Ana nta kaŇčgiap, ana vh…®ra ŇčkasŇčkagiap kama havharar buni nzuav Ňčari bak…®vi ga mbui guma ma.
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 7:23 \xt Kis 2.11-15\x*‚ÄúMoses kav kim, ana mparive vov, 40 th…®gim, ana mbaram kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, gu ntigem won fegi gum Ňčgugi IsreriŇč gan…®nga.
\v 24 Moses ne suaŇčgiap, raa mben ana vov, mbe gara ruav kav garim, Idz…®p guma mbe Isrer guma mbe, ana t…®va mbat…®gar ana mbuav ana shogi. Ana ana shogap kim, Moses ana gangiap, mbaram won k…®vntok Isrer guman kurav, mba Idz…®p guma shogim, ana rimgi.
\v 25 Moses vh…®ra khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, Fhe Bak…®me ana nt…®…®ri Isrerin kurkurar zav, ana ndim fagi. Ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ana nt…®…®ri IsreriŇč, ne kaŇčgi thi. Ana mba nd…®knd…®ga mbuim, ana nt…®…®ri IsreriŇč ne kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 26 Moses mba m…®timanera ana vov garim, Isrer guma manira, mani wani shogi. Mani wani shogim, ana vov mani gorav, khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄėAi, Ňčko wanira shog…® thari, Ňčko fek gum Ňčguk ma. Ňäko thaŇč nzuav mba t…®va mbat…®gar wani ga mbui.‚Äô
\v 27 Moses maaŇč mani ga nzuaim, mba fharav mba bigeŇč khavgiap, mba harigi ne shogi guma Moses ga b…®rav, mbur kh…®ngiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAi, the nza gan…® zav ndu ndim guman panan fagim ndu nza gan…® za mbui?
\v 28 Ee, ndu gurum mbu Idz…®p guma shogim, ana rimgim, ndu ntigem mba t…®vara nan muuŇčgip na shogirim, gu rimgir za mbui thi?‚Äô
\v 29 \x - \xo 7:29 \xt Kis 2.21-22; 18.3-4\x*Ana nen Moses ga suaŇčgim, Moses mba kameŇč mbararagiap, thav ra vov, Midian harigi Ňčgun ki. Ana Midian kav, muuaŇč t…®gap, tara phuni tegi.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 7:30 \xt Kis 3.1-10\x*‚ÄúMoses maaŇč kim, 40 mpari vh…®zgi. Mba 40 mpari vh…®zgim, Fhe Bak…®me won enser mbe sarigim, ana Mosesan h…®gi. Ana kha t…®va muuŇčgiap ana h…®gi. Moses vov garim, Sainai mb…®ksh…®ma han gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen kha bisaneŇč vhav, ne th…®gap shi. Mba vhav shiv, mba Fhe Bak…®me enser mba vhava vhen anan h…®gi.
\v 31 Moses mba kha bisaneŇč garim, ne shim, ana Ňčgava mbat…®gi muuŇčgiap, ana tuituigip ne gangir zav sh…®vav ne han vui. Ana sh…®vav, ne han vov, ana Guma Bak…®me kamthooŇč mbararagi.
\v 32 Ana mbararagim, Fhe Bak…®me khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGu ndun ndegir Fhe Bak…®me ma. Gu Abraham gum, Aisak, Zekop, gu mben Fhe Bak…®me ma.‚Äô Ana ne nzuaim, Moses ana mbararagiap, rivgiap, nin…®k ana mbuim, ana gan…® thagi.
\v 33 \x - \xo 7:33 \xt Jos 5.15\x*Ana gan…® thagim, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAi, ndu won Ňčgari sharive zorgiri. Ndu mba th…®gi nuianeŇč, ne nan ŇčaneŇč ma.‚Äô Ne guigira Ňčgarigi nuianeŇč ma.
\v 34 Fhe Bak…®me ne Moses ga nzuav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGu won gumgi gu mbigi IsreriŇč garim, Idz…®viŇč guigira t…®vi mbat…®gar mbe mbui. Mbe mba t…®vir, mbe mbuim, mbe nz…®…®im, gu mbe s…®s…®ma mbararagiap, gu mba Idz…®viŇč t…®n mbe ndir zav zergi. Ndu ntige khavgiri, gu ndu sararim, ndu taagip Idz…®van Ňčg…®rga.‚Äô
\p 
\v 35 \x - \xo 7:35 \xt Kis 2.14; 14.11-12; Nam 20.16\x*‚ÄúKha Mosesra, mbe IsreriŇč fhum khaŇč ana suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėThe nza gan…® zav ndu ndim guman panan fagim, ndu nza gan…® za mbui?‚Äô Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgi guma Mosesra, Fhe Bak…®me ntigem wom ana sarigi. Ana ntigem taagi Ňčg…®p mba Isrerin guman pan k…®v, taagip mbe Idz…®viŇč t…®n mbe ndigirga. Moses ntigem mba kha bisaneŇč shim, ana ne gan…® zav vuim, Fhe Bak…®me won enser ga sarigim, ana zav, mba vhava vhen h…®gap ŇčkasŇčkar Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 36 \x - \xo 7:36 \xt Kis 7.3; 12.41; 14.21; 16.1; 16.35; Nam 14.33; Sng 105.27\x*Fhe Bak…®me havharar Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgim, Moses vov, Idz…®van mbar k…®rga mirikori ana nta mbuav, mba Idz…®viŇč t…®n IsreriŇč ndigap, mben kov vui. Ana mben kov vov, vh…®ra Retsin mirikor ga mbuav, vo mba gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen vh…®ra mirikori ga muuŇčgi. Ana mben kov vov mba t…®va mbuav kim, 40 mpari vh…®zgi.
\v 37 \x - \xo 7:37 \xt Lo 8.15; 8.18; Mt 17.5; FG 3.22\x*Mba IsreriŇč kov vugi Mosesra, ana khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėFhe Bak…®me nden r…®g…®ra nden Ňčguga the ndim farim, ana na farar muuŇčgip, Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma k…®rga.‚Äô
\v 38 \x - \xo 7:38 \xt Kis 19.1‚Äď20.17; Lo 5.1-33; Ais 63.9; FG 7.53; Ro 3.2; Ga 3.19; Hi 2.2\x*Mba Mosesra nzan nz…®gir kov vov mba gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen vugap, mbe phorga kegi. Ana mben kov vov maaŇč kav, ana vov Sainai mb…®ksh…®man ndagim, Fhe Bak…®me enseri Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuin ana suaŇčgi. Mba Fhe Bak…®men enser, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga buni vhuuin ana suaŇčgim, ana mba bunin nza suaŇčgi.
\p 
\v 39 \x - \xo 7:39 \xt Nam 14.3\x*‚ÄúAna mba bunin nza nzuaim, nzan nz…®gi mba buni mbarara thagi. Mbe nta mbarara thav, mben nd…®knd…®gi mbe taagip Idz…®van Ňčg…®rgeŇč vuzvugi.
\v 40 \x - \xo 7:40 \xt Kis 32.1; 32.23\x*Mbe mba nd…®knd…®ga mbuav khaŇč Aron ga nzuai, ‚ÄėAron, ndu nza suaŇčv ntuu thari kargirim, mbe nzan kurarim, nza Ňčg…®rga. Kha nzan kov Idz…®p thav z…®gi guma Moses, nza ntigem ana kaŇčgi fhu, ana khar ki fhu, ana ram muuŇčgi.‚Äô
\v 41 \x - \xo 7:41 \xt Kis 32.2-6; Lo 9.16; Sng 106.19\x*Mbe maaŇč Aron ga suaŇčgiap, mbe mba tugen gor tuegap, ana borombaga karigi. Mbe ana kargiap mbaram, ana nzuav ndikndigap, ana ndim vun kuamkuav, shama bak…®me mbui.
\v 42 \x - \xo 7:42 \xt Sng 81.12; Jer 19.13; Ese 20.25; 20.39; 2 Te 2.11\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me k…®r mbe segi. Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgip k…®r mbe seg…®rga, mbe ra gum k…®ni Ňčkaa, mbe mben rotur muunga. Mba mbe maaŇč muunga kameŇč, mbe fhum ne khergim, ne Fhe Bak…®me kaathoori gumgi suaŇčgi buni ki gavar ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNde kha IsreriŇč, nde mba 40 mparir nde mba gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen kav, mba borombaga gum sipsivi shogap shaa ga mbui. Nde mba tugar mba shaa ga mbuav, nde kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui thi? Nde na nzuav shama mbui. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 43 Nde mba ndia rui sher phena bak…®me, ana nane fhuvara. Ana nden mbar…®p Morek ne ma. Nde vh…®ra wari won mbar…®p Refanan kaman tum, nde vh…®ra ana ndia rui. Nde wari won mbar…®vir ntuu kargiap ntan rotu mbui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu nde vhararga, nde wari won fhain nuiana thav Ňčg…®p, Babiron Ňčgu bak…®me fhain mueŇč nderen k…®rga.‚Äô\f a \fr 7:43 \ft Morek, ana harigi Ňčgui gumgi, mbe nduarira wari won farir tuma kargiap ana rotu mbui. Ana mben mbar…®v ma, Refan. Ana kama mbe ma. Mbe vh…®ra ana rotu mbui, ana vh…®ra mben mbar…®va mbe ma. Stiven mba suaŇčgi kameŇč, ana Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma Amos suaŇčgi buni ki gavar ki. Mba buni Amos 5.25-27, Amos khaŇč suaŇčgi, mba fhum kegi IsreriŇč, mbe Fhe Bak…®me rotu muuŇčgi fhu. Mbe ana nzuai buni, mbe nta daasui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi phorgap, mbe rotu mbui mbar…®vi rotu mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, zumgum Fhe Bak…®me mbe garim, mbe k…®r ana segi. Fhe Bak…®me thav BabironiŇč ga nzuaim, mbe zav IsreriŇč phorga shogap, mbe ndi vov Babiron fhain vegim, mbe BabironiŇč fhaiŇč gari guman pana piin Ňčgarim, ana mbe garim, mbe fhura mben Ňčaara gumgi ki. Ndu 2 King 24.10-16. \f*
\p 
\v 44 \x - \xo 7:44 \xt Kis 25.9; 25.40; 26.30; Hi 8.5\x*‚ÄúNzan nz…®gi mbe fhum gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen kav, mbe Fhe Bak…®men sher phen kegi. Mba sher phen, mbe IsreriŇč ana garav kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me guigira mbe phorga ki. Mbe mba sher phena mbuav, mbe guigira mba Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga suaŇčgi bunira z…®n vov, ana muuŇčgi. Mbe ana muuŇčgim, ana guigira mba Moses gangi phenan tumara gangana mbui.
\v 45-46 \x - \xo 7:45-46 \xt Jos 3.14-17; 18.1; 23.9; Neh 9.24; Sng 44.2; FG 13.19\x*\x - \xo 7:45-46 \xt 1 Sml 16.1; 2 Sml 7.1-16; 1 Kin 8.19; 1 Sto 17.1-14; Sng 89.19; 132.1-5\x*Nzan nz…®gi mba sher phena muuŇčgiap mbe vh…®zgim, mben tari mba sher phena ndigap, Zosua mben kov vov, mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi, mbe zav nzan nz…®gir nuiana s…®gen ki. Zosua mben kov vov, mbe vharigim, mbe mba nzan nz…®gi nuianeŇč thav regi. Mbe mba nuianeŇč thav regim, mbe mbaram mba sher phena muuŇčgi. Mbe mba sher phena muuŇčgiap maaŇč kav kim, Devit Ňčgui gari guman pana z…® ndigap, ana mben Ňčgui gari guman pan ki. Devit Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuun ana mbui guma ma. Devit vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėFhe Bak…®me ana kh…®rarim, ana Zekovan nz…®gir Fhe Bak…®me rotur muun saŇčv, ana mbe suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phenan muuŇčgirga.‚Äô
\v 47 \x - \xo 7:47 \xt 1 Kin 6.1-38; 8.20; 1 Sto 17.12; 2 Sto 3.1-17\x*Ana anan muun zav suaŇčgim, zumgum Soromon ana muuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 48 \x - \xo 7:48 \xt 1 Kin 8.27; 2 Sto 2.6; 6.18\x*‚ÄúNza kha vu guarara ki Fhe Bak…®me, ana gumgi mbui phenin ki fhuvara. Khe Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma mbe khaŇč nzuai,
\v 49 \x - \xo 7:49 \xt Mt 5.34-35; 23.22\x*\x - \xo 7:49 \xt Ais 66.1-2\x*‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇč khare, ‚ÄúKha buip, ana gu Ňčgui gari guman pan pigi mpirmpir…®k ma. Kha nuian, gu perav won Ňčkarveni ndi sarigi Ňčan ma. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip nde ram muuŇčgip na ndim phenan muuŇčgirie? Gu vh…®ra maaŇčgi ŇčaneŇč nan vhuksu ŇčaneŇč k…®rie?
\v 50 Ee, gu vh…®ra, gu nduara za kha bigi ga muuŇčgi fhuve?‚ÄĚ ‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 51 \x - \xo 7:51 \xt Kis 32.9; Wkp 26.41; Lo 10.16; Ais 48.4; 63.10; Jer 6.10; 9.26\x*Stiven kha bunin mba buaadegi gumgi ga nzua vov, zazera khueŇč phorga mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde guigira r…®…®r…®…®i gumgi ma. Nden ndavi vheri gum nden pani guigira havhargiap, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč khothiv…® thagi gumgi fara muuŇčgi. Nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde khuari p…®ngiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararagi fhuvara. Nde maaŇč mbuav, nde Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nzuai buni, nden nz…®gi fhum nta daasuegi, nde ntige mbe z…®n vov, zazera nta daasui.
\v 52 \x - \xo 7:52 \xt 2 Sto 36.16; Mt 21.35; 23.31; 1 Te 2.15\x*Nden nz…®gi, fhum maaŇčgi Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma, mbe t…®va mbat…®ga thuen ana muuŇčgi fhu? Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe fhum khaŇč nzuai gumgi, mbe mbe shogim, mbe vh…®zav ki. Mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėT…®var vhuuaŇč mbui guma ana z…®rga.‚Äô Mbe maaŇč nzuav kim, mba guma ntige z…®gim, nde ana ndim ana pana gumgir farve kh…®ngim, mbe ana shogim, ana rimgi.
\v 53 \x - \xo 7:53 \xt Kis 20.1; FG 7.38; Ga 3.19; Hi 2.2\x*Nde, nde Fhe Bak…®me enserir farve t…®n Fhe Bak…®me nzuai t…®vi ndigi nt…®…®ri ma. Nde anan t…®vi ndigap, nde nta z…®n vui fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mbe Ňčk…®…®ar Stiven ga segim, ana rimgi.
\p 
\v 54 \x - \xo 7:54 \xt FG 5.33\x*Stiven mba bunin mba buaadegi gumgi ga suaŇčgim, mba buaadegi gumgi, mbe guigira Stiven ga nzuav ndavi mbe shigim, mbe ana nzuav tari nd…®…®ri ph…®ri.
\v 55 \x - \xo 7:55 \xt Mt 22.44; FG 2.33-34; 5.31; 6.5\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira Stiven phorga kav, ana rugim, ana khoga buiva garim, Heven fhogi. Heven fhogim, ana Hevenan vhava Ňčaarar vhuuŇč garav, Fhe Bak…®men s…®…®n vhuuŇč gari. Ana garav, Zisas garim, ana Fhe Bak…®men guva haren th…®gap ki.
\v 56 \x - \xo 7:56 \xt Ese 1.1; Dan 7.13; Mt 3.16; FG 10.11; Kor 3.1\x*Stiven mba bigi garav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mbarara! Gu Heven garim, ana fhogim, gu Fhe Bak…®me Guma Guara garim, ana Fhe Bak…®men guva haren th…®gap ki.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 57 Stiven nen mbe nzuaim, mbe ne mbararavram, wari wo khuari p…®ngiap, ana tuarahurav, wari t…®g…®ra khuafuigia vov, ana suirigi.
\v 58 \x - \xo 7:58 \xt Lo 13.9; Ru 4.29; FG 6.13-14; 22.20; Hi 13.12\x*Mbe ana suirav, Ňčk…®…®r ana seg…®rim, ana rimgir zav ana ndigap mba Ňčgu bak…®me thav k…®rar h…®gi. Mbe k…®rar hegap fharav fhura sh…®sh…®ga bunin ana si. Mbe bunin ana segap, mbaram wari won shagi mpeeiŇč zorgiap, nta ndim guman kama mbe n…®ma suegi. Mba guman kama z…® khare, Sor. \f b \fr 7:58 \ft Isrerin t…®v khaŇč muuŇčgi, guma t…®va mbat…®ga guara thueŇčra muuŇčgirga, mbe mba guma ndigip, Ňčgu bak…®me thav k…®rar h…®g…®p, Ňčk…®…®ar ana seg…®rim, ana rimgirga. Ndu kha gava gan…®ri, mba gap khare. Wok Pris 24.13 gan…® Ňčg…®p 16 t…®g…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 59 \x - \xo 7:59 \xt Sng 31.5; Ru 23.46\x*Mbe won shagi ndi suegap, mbaram Ňčk…®…®r Stiven ga si. Mbe Ňčk…®…®r ana sim, Stiven thav khaŇč Fhe Bak…®me nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me Zisas, ndu nan tuma ndig…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 60 \x - \xo 7:60 \xt Mt 5.44; Ru 23.34; FG 9.40; 21.5\x*Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram th…®panani ph…®rgiap fav kama bak…®mera rugap, kh…®r…®p kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ndu kheiŇč mbui t…®va mbat…®ga suaŇčv mbe suaŇč thari.‚ÄĚ Stiven maaŇč suaŇčgiap thav rimgi.
\c 8
\nb 
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt FG 7.58; 8.4; 9.1; 9.13; 9.21; 11.19; 22.4-5; 22.20; 26.9-11; 1 Ko 15.9; 1 T 1.13\x*Mbe Sor n…®man mba t…®var Stiven ga mbui ne nzerara.
\s1 Sor mba Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir farfagi.
\p Mbe Stiven shogim, ana rimgi raar, mbe mba tugen, mba Zerusareman Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe farfa mbat…®gar mbe mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbe mbuim, mba Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za rav, Zudia gum Samaria Ňčgu bak…®men vegi. Mbe za vegim, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe nduarira Zerusareman ki.
\v 2 Mba Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi ga mbui gumgi mbari, mbe Stiven khuma ndiga vov, mboga t…®gav, ana nzuav nzi mbat…®ga mbui.
\v 3 Mbe ana ndim mboga t…®gim, Sor h…®gap Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana farfa mbat…®gar mbe mbui. Ana pheni tug…®ra t…®gap mba t…®var mba gumgi gu mbigi ga mbuav, mbe vhivav vov, mbe ndi b…®na sui.
\ms1 Mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Zudia gum Samarian Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\s1 Mbe Samarian Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 8:4 \xt Mt 10.23; FG 6.5; 11.19\x*Mba ra vegi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba Ňčguir vegap, mbe mba ki Ňčguir Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\v 5 Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Firip vov Samarian kav, ana Zisas bun mbe nzuai. Ana Zisas bun mbe nzuav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas, ana Fhe Bak…®me taagip kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarav sarigi guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 Firip maaŇč mbe nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe zav mba buni mbararav, ana mbui mirikori, mbe nta garav, mbe tuituigira ana nzuai buni, mbe khuarar nta t…®gi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt Mt 10.1; Mk 16.17\x*Mbe khuarar Firip nzuai buni ga t…®gap, mbe vh…®ra ana garim, ana gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve t…®n mba ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi ga vharvharigim, nta s…®s…®m mbat…®ga mbuav, mbe thamthav k…®rar hi. Ana vh…®ra bigi rimgiap s…®…®r ki gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, gum suira mbat…®gi gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, ana mbe mbuim, mbe nzezerigi.
\v 8 Ana maaŇč mbuim, mba Samaria Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ndikndiga mbat…®ga mbui.
\p 
\v 9 Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki guma mbe, ana z…® Saimon. Mba guma, ana fhum mbark…®rga tori mbat…®gi, ana nta mbuim, mba Samarian ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana garav nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Ana maaŇč mbuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu z…® ki guma bak…®me ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Saimon maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgi ruu gum mba Ňčgun ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana nzuai buni mbararagi. Mbe ana buni mbararav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha guma Saimon, ana tor ŇčkasŇčka ki guma ma. Nza kha z…®n ana r…®gi, ‚ÄėŇäkasŇčka Bak…®me.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Saimon maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap ana buni mbararagi. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana fhum tuga mpeeŇčra, ana mba won tori phorga Ňčgarim, mbe ana garav Ňčgava mbat…®ga mbuav ki.
\v 12 Mbe zumgum Firip z…®gap, Fhe Bak…®men taagi kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mba ana piin k…®rga buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav, Zisas Krais bun nzuaim, mbe ana buni mbararav, ana khoth…®gap, mbe gumgi gu mbigi, vh…®ra Zisas z…®n panan ruai.
\v 13 Mbe ruaim, Saimon vh…®ra Firip nzuai buni khoth…®gap, ana vh…®ra Zisas z…®n panan ruagi. Saimon ruagiap mbaram, Firip phorgap ana mba rui Ňčani, ana za nta ruav, ana garim, ana mbark…®rga mirikori, ana nta mbuim, ana ana garav, nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui.
\p 
\v 14 Firip Samarian kav maaŇč mbuim, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Zerusareman kav mbararagim, mbe Samarian Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararav, nta ndi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbararagiap, mbaram Pita gum Zon ga sarigim, mani mbe han vui.
\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Mt 28.19; FG 2.38; 10.48; 19.2\x*Mani vov mben h…®gap, mbaram mbe nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana won Ňäina Ňäaarar mben n…®…®nga.
\v 16 Mbe Guma Bak…®me Zisas z…®n panan ruagi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi fhuvara.
\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt FG 6.6; 19.6; Hi 6.2\x*Mani maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbe nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, mbaram wani wo farvenin mbe suim, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaarar mbe nd…®…®i.
\p 
\v 18 Saimon mba Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara gumani garim, mani wani won farvenin mbe suim, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaarar ŇčkasŇčkar mbe nd…®…®im, Saimon mbaram Ňčk…®…® ndigap, mani ga nd…®…®v, khaŇč mani ga nzuai,
\v 19 ‚ÄúŇäko vh…®ra mba ŇčkasŇčkar nan n…®…®Ňčgiri. Gu vh…®ra maaŇč muuŇčgip farver guma the kh…®ngirim, Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra won Ňäina Ňäaarar ŇčkasŇčkar anan n…®…®Ňčgirga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 8:20 \xt Mt 10.8; FG 2.38; 10.45\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Pita mbaram khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdun Ňčk…®…®a nta ndu phorg…®v mbat…®girga! Fhe Bak…®me khar nd…®…®i big…®n, ana fhura nd…®…®i big…®n ma. Ndu nd…®knd…®gi, ndu Ňčk…®…®ar ana vhezgirga thi? Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Sng 78.37\x*Ndun ndava vhee Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzerigi fhuvara. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip nza phorg…®v Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaarar muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 22 \x - \xo 8:22 \xt Dan 4.27; 2 T 2.25; Hi 12.15\x*Ndu guigira wo ndava dorg…®p, ndu mba mbui nd…®knd…®k mbat…®k, ndu guigira ana thav, Guma Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana maaŇč muuŇčgip ndu ndava vhen ki nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®k, ana ana vh…®z…® saŇčv, ana nta vh…®zgirim, ana ndu thav sarga.
\v 23 Gu khaŇč muuŇčgia ndu gangiap, gu khuen ndu nzuai. Gu ndu garim, ndu Fhe Bak…®me kha fhura nd…®…®i big…®n, ndu ana gangiap guigira ana niihegap, fhura ana ndir zav mbui. Ndu mba nd…®knd…®ga mbuim, mba nd…®knd…®k, ana kuga mbat…®ga fara muuŇčgiap, ndu ndava vhen kav ndun ndava vhee muuŇčgim, ndu t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui b…®nan ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 24 \x - \xo 8:24 \xt Kis 8.8; Nam 21.7; 1 Kin 13.6; Ze 5.16\x*Pita maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, Saimon ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇčgi, nde na suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana na korar muuŇčgip, mba nde na suaŇčgi bigi, nta nan h…® tharga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, Pita gum Zon mbaram Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun maaŇč ki gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, mbaram Guma Bak…®me mani ga muuŇčgi bigi, mani vh…®ra nta bun mbe nzuai. Mani mba bigi bun mbe suaŇčgia thugap, zumgum Zerusareman ndai. Mani Zerusareman ndav, mani mba Samaria Ňčgui sh…®gap ndav, mani Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe nzuav wani ndai.
\s1 Firip Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun Itiopia guma ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 26 Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe Firipan h…®gap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khavgip, saut fhain gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen mba Zerusareman kegap Gesan veri tuavar Ňčgir…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 \x - \xo 8:27 \xt Ais 56.3-7; Sef 3.10; Zo 12.20\x*Ana maaŇč Firip ga suaŇčgim, Firip mbaram khavgiap, vov mba tuap th…®ga veri. Ana verav, mbaram Itiopia guma garim, ana veri. Mba guma, ana Itiopian kuin Kandasi, ana ana ndim fagim, ana anan Ňčk…®…®a gum bigi gari guma pana ma. Ana vh…®ra mbe ana thuni ndigi guma ma. Ana rotur muun zav Zerusareman ndav kegap veri.
\v 28 Ana won karis ga perigim, ana hozani ana kh…®gap Ňčg…®rga verim, ana perav kav Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma Aisaia khergi gava garav veri.
\v 29 Ana verim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar Firip ga rugap kha nd…®knd…®gar ana nd…®…®i, ‚ÄúNdu thiv…®v mbu karis kuran Ňčgir…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 30 Ana mba nd…®knd…®gar Firip ga nd…®…®im, Firip mbaram khuaf…® mba karis kura th…®gap, verav mba guma mbararagim, ana Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma Aisaia khergi gava gari. Ana mba gava garim, Firip khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúEna, ndu mba gari gavar ki buni nd…®…®riveŇč kaŇčgiap nta garire?‚ÄĚ
\v 31 \x - \xo 8:31 \xt Zo 16.13\x*Firip maaŇč ana nzuaim, mba Itiopia guma ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the mba buni nd…®…®ri bun nan suaŇčgirga fhu, gu ram muuŇčgip mba buni nd…®…®ri kaŇčgirie?‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč Firip ga nzuav, mbaram khaŇč Firip ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu z…®v, na han kha karisan ndav na han khaŇč pera.‚ÄĚ \fig Firip Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun Itiopia guma ga nzuai. (8.26) |src="LB00331C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="8.26"\fig*
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 8:32 \xt Ais 53.7-8\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Firip nda vov, ana haa perigi. Ana mba gari gap, ana kha khesharigi buni ana ki. Mba buni khare,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúAna mbe sipsiva shog…®r zav ana ndiga vui fara muuŇčgi. Ana mbe mba sipsiva Ňčguga r…®gi ph…®r…® zav ana ndiga vuim, ana nz…®…®i fhu, ana vh…®ra th…®…®ni mp…®rigi.
\q1 
\v 33 Mbe vh…®ra za ana mbevav, mbe ana guigira muuŇčgi bigeŇč ga nzuav ana nzuav suaŇčgi fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra the k…®v ana suaŇčv mbe suaŇčrie? Fhuvara. The k…®v ana nt…®…®ri ga suaŇčv suaŇčrie? Mbe maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, ana kha nuiana thav vugi, ana wom kha nuianan ki fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 Mba Itiopia guma mba gaven mba buni gangia thugap, kha nzambaren Firip ga muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúEna, gu ndun nzai. Kha Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma, ana kha kherav suaŇčgi kameŇč, mba kameŇč the nzuai? Ana wora nzuai o, ana harigi guma ga nzuai?‚ÄĚ
\v 35 \x - \xo 8:35 \xt Ru 24.27; FG 18.28\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Firip mbaram fharav mba Itiopia guma mba karisan zerav gangi gaveŇč ki buni nd…®…®ri bun ana nzuai. Ana nta bun ana suaŇčgia thugap zumgum ana Zisas buni vhuuiŇč bun ana nzuai.
\v 36-37 \x - \xo 8:36-37 \xt FG 10.47\x*Ana mba bunin ana nzuav, mani verav kav, mb…® mben h…®gi. Mani verav, mb…®n hav, mba Itiopia guma khaŇč Firip ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khar gan…®, mb…®ra khare. Thag…®n big…®n na tuav mp…®rari, gu ruar…® tharie?‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 8:36-37 \ft Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, harigi buni mbari phorgap kha vezar ki. Mba buni khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFirip khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu guigira won ndava vhen Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®p, ndu ana z…®n panan ruari.‚Äô Firip nen ana nzuaim, ana khaŇč Firip ga nzuai, ‚ÄėGu Zisas Krais khoth…®gi ana Fhe Bak…®men kam ma.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 38 Ana ne Firip ga suaŇčgiap mbaram, mba karis Ňčgi hozani sh…®man suigi guma ga nzuaim, ana mba hozani ga mbuim, ni th…®gi. Mba hozani th…®gim, mba karis th…®gi. Firip mba guman kov, mani fega n…®…®n mbarav, vov mb…®n vergap, Firip mbaram mba Itiopia guma, ana Zisas z…®n panan ana ruai.
\v 39 \x - \xo 8:39 \xt 1 Kin 18.12; 2 Kin 2.16; Ese 3.12-14\x*Firip ana ruagiap, mani b…®rav, th…®var ndavra thagim, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar Firip ndiga vugim, mba guma wom Firip gangi fhu. Mba guma thav ndikndigap, taagia vov won karisan ndav, won Ňčgun veri tuap th…®ga veri.
\v 40 \x - \xo 8:40 \xt FG 21.8\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar Firip ndiga vugim, ana garav, anan Asdotan Ňčgu bak…®men ki. Ana maaŇč kav, ana tamtam mba Ňčgui bisarirer vov, Zisas bunin vhuuiŇč bun mbe nzuai. Ana maaŇč mbua vov, ana zumgum vov Sisaria Ňčgu bak…®men h…®gi.
\c 9
\s1 Sor ndava dorgi.
\r Farasegi Gumgi 22.4-16; 26.9-18
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt FG 8.3; Ga 1.13; 1 T 1.13\x*Mba tugivigen Sor mba Guma Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ana mbe shog…®rim, mbe vh…®z…® zav kama havhara nzuai. Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pana han vui.
\v 2 Ana vov, mba Fhe Bak…®me phena gari guman panan nzai. Ana kha nzambarar ana mbui. Ndu na ndim, mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phenin gumgir pani, mbe Damaskusan ki. Nde mbe ndim gavi khergirim, gu nta ndigip Damaskusan naanga. Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, mba Fhe Bak…®me phena gari guman pan ana ndim gavi khergip, ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana mba khergi gavi khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúSor maaŇč muuŇčgip Zisas suaŇčgi k…®r…® t…®va z…®n vui gumgi o mbigi, ana maaŇč mbe gangirga, ana mbe ndim b…®na sur saŇčv mbe suigip, mbe ndigi Zerusareman zirg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 3-4 \x - \xo 9:3-4 \xt FG 22.6; 26.12; 1 Ko 15.8\x*\x - \xo 9:3-4 \xt Mt 25.40\x*Ana mba gavi kherav maaŇč suaŇčgim, Sor mbaram mba gavi ndigap, Zerusarem thav, khavgia Damaskusan ndai. Ana Zerusarem tha nda vov, Damaskus Ňčgun h…®r zav mbuavra thagim, vhava mbe tor vhekvhegi fara muuŇčgiap buivar kegap, vhemkora zera zav, Sor ga sh…®rav, za ana behuigi. Mba vhava Ňčaar guigira havhargiap, Sor r…®mani ga sh…®rigim, Sor won hoza thav k…®gira n…®…®aŇč ndarigi. Ana k…®gira n…®…®aŇč ndarav mbararagim, guma kamthooŇč mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúSor, Sor, ndu thaŇč nzuav nan farfagi?‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt FG 5.39; 1 Ko 15.8\x*Ana ne nzuaim, Sor khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, ndu the?‚ÄĚ Sor ne nzuaim, ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Zisas ma, ndu nan farfagi.
\v 6 Ndu khavgip, Ňčgu bak…®men vhen Ňčgir…®. Guma the ndu zumgum muunga bigi bun ndu suanga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt FG 22.9; 26.13\x*Mba Sor phorga vui gumgi, mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, suanga buni kakagi. Mbe mba nzuai guman kamthooŇč mbararav, ana nzuav garav, ana gangi fhuvara.
\v 8 Sor mbaram khavgiap, r…®mani ndarav, gari. Ana garim, ana r…®mani guigira g…®ng…®na mbat…®ga muuŇčgi. Mbe thav ana farar suirav, ana kov Damaskusan Ňčgun vhen veri.
\v 9 Mbe ana kov Ňčgun vhen vergim, ana ra phuni khegenen, anan r…®mani mbara muuŇčgiap g…®ng…®ngiavra kegi. Ana mba gu mb…® mbegi fhu.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt FG 22.12\x*Ana mbara muuŇčgiap kim, Zisas buni khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui guma mbe Damaskusan ki, ana z…® Ananaias. Ananaias maaŇč kuim, Guma Bak…®me maaŇč r…®man ana kharav, ana z…®n kamgi, ‚ÄúAnanaias‚ÄĚ Ananaias mbaram khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, gu khar ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt FG 16.9; 21.39; 22.3\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khavgi, mbe kha z…®n r…®gi tuav th…®g…® Ňčgir…®, mba tuav z…® khare, Purara Vugi Tuav. Ndu mba tuav th…®g…® Ňčgir…®v, Zudas phenan Ňčgirg…®p, Tarsus guma Sor ga suaŇčv mben nzaŇčri. Ana ntigem, mbur kav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ki.
\v 12 Anan r…®mani g…®ng…®ngira kim, ana r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap guma mbe gangi. Mba guma z…® Ananaias. Ana Ananaias garim, ana zav wo farver ana t…®kh…®ngi. Anan r…®mani nzera zav ana mba t…®var ana muuŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt FG 8.3\x*Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč Ananaias ga nzuaim, Ananaias khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, gu gumgi vh…®rve mbararagim, mbe mba guma neŇčgegi. Mba guma Zerusareman ndu z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana farfa mbat…®gira mbe muuŇčgi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt FG 9.1-2; 9.21; 22.16; 1 Ko 1.2; 2 T 2.22\x*Ana maaŇč mbe muuŇčgiap, mbaram vov Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani han vugap, mbe nzuaim, mbe ana kh…®rav gavi ga muuŇčgiap, ana n…®…®Ňčgim, ana kham ndu z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ndi b…®na sur zav ndagi.‚ÄĚ
\v 15 \x - \xo 9:15 \xt FG 25.13; 25.22; 26.17; 27.24; Ro 1.5; 1 Ko 15.10; Ga 2.7-8; 1 T 2.7\x*Ananaias maaŇč nzuaim, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Ňčg…®. Mba guma ana ntigem, nan Ňčaara guma ma. Gu ana ndi fagi, ana ntigem, na z…® bun harigi Ňčgui gumgi ga suaŇčv, vh…®ra na z…® bun mben Ňčgui vh…®rve gari gumgir pani ga suaŇčv, ana vh…®ra na z…® bun mba IsreriŇč ga suanga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 9:16 \xt FG 20.23; 21.11; 2 Ko 11.23-28\x*Gu vh…®ra ana mba na z…® bun suaŇčv, na z…®n panan ndirga zaagi, gu nta ana kh…®varga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 9:17 \xt FG 13.52; 22.12-13\x*Fhe Bak…®me mba bunin Ananaias ga suaŇčgim, Ananaias thav vui. Ana vov, mba phena vhen vergap, mbaram won farven Sor t…®kh…®ngiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNan fek Sor, ndu mba tuavar ndaim, Guma Bak…®me Zisas ana ndun h…®gi, ana ntigem, na sarigim, gu z…®gi. Ndu r…®mani ntigem taagi gan…®rim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira ndu givarga.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Ananaias nen Sor ga nzuavra thagim, mba mb…®gama nana fara muuŇčgi big…®n Sor r…®mani thav fhura mbar vugim, Sor r…®mani taagia nzerigim, ana taagia gari. Sor r…®mani taagia garav, ana mbaram, Zisas z…®n panan ruagi.
\v 19 Sor ruagiap, ana zumgum mba gum mb…® pav, ana ŇčkasŇčka taagia ana z…®gi.
\s1 Sor Damaskusan Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 20 Sor ruagiap, ana rari mbarir ana mba Damaskusan Zisas z…®n vui gumgi phorga Damaskusan kegi.
\p Sor mben han kegap, khavgiap, ana za vov mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi pheni vhen verav za khueŇč bun nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas ana Fhe Bak…®me Kam ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 \x - \xo 9:21 \xt FG 8.3; Ga 1.13; 1.23\x*Sor maaŇč nzuaim, mba Sor mbararagi gumgi, mbe guigira Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi. Mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap kha nzambara mbui, ‚ÄúEe, kha gumara mba Zerusareman mba Zisas z…®n vui ne nzuav mba gumgi gu mbigir farfagi fhuve. Ana mben farfagiap, khaŇč ndagi. Ana khaŇč ndav mba Zisas z…®n vui nt…®…®ri, ana mbe suigip, mbe ndigi, taagip mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani han Ňčgir…® zav ndagi fhuve?‚ÄĚ
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt FG 17.3; 18.5; 18.28\x*Mbe mba suambarar Sor ga mbuim, Sor khaŇč t…®ga ŇčkasŇčkagiap Zisas z…® bun nzuav, khaŇč t…®gap guigira mba Damaskusan ki ZudaiŇč hiav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas, ana mba Fhe Bak…®me taagip won gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav farasarigi guma ma.‚ÄĚ Sor maaŇč nzuaim, mba ZudaiŇč ana nzuai buni mbararagiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, ana buni mbev…®rga buna thueŇč ki fhu.
\s1 Mbe ZudaiŇč mbe panan Sor ga kegim, ana ra vugi.
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt FG 23.12; 25.3; 2 Ko 11.23\x*\x - \xo 9:23 \xt 2 Ko 11.32-33\x*Rari vh…®rve vov vh…®zgim, mbe ZudaiŇč mbe wari fugap, Sor shogirim, ana rimgirga kama shogi.
\v 24 Mbe mba kama shogim, Sor mba kameŇč mbararagi. Mbe mba kama shogiap, mbe ZudaiŇč mbe raai gu mbarir mba Ňčgu bak…®me th…®…®r kaa, mbe nta gari. Mbe Sor shogirim, ana rimgir zav mbe ana nzuav gari.
\v 25 Mbe maaŇč ana muun zav mbuim, mba Sor nzuai buni mbararav, ana z…®n vui gumgi mba maan ana kov vov, mba Ňčgu bak…®me b…®na vhuigi b…®na gaar ndagi. Mbe ndav ana nzuaim, ana k…®r…®ma bak…®me peregim, mbe mpiin ana fav, ana kh…®gap ana ndim thooŇč mbugum mbarigim, ana k…®rar vergi.
\s1 Sor Zerusareman ki.
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 9:26 \xt FG 22.17; Ga 1.17-19\x*Mbe maaŇč Sor ga muuŇčgim, ana mbaram vov, Zerusareman vergi. Ana vov Zerusareman h…®gap, mbaram mba Zisas z…®n vuav, ana khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi phorg…® k…®r zav mbuim, mbe anan rivgi. Mbe khuen ana khoth…®gi fhu, ana guigira Zisas z…®n vov ana khoth…®gi guma ma.
\v 27 \x - \xo 9:27 \xt FG 4.36; 9.4; 9.20-22; 1 Ko 9.1; 15.8\x*Mbe mba nd…®knd…®gar ana mbuim, Barnabas mbaram Sorar kov, mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgir han vui. Barnabas ana ko vov, ana bun mbe nzuai. Ana ana bun nzuav, mba Guma Bak…®me tuavar ana h…®gap ana suaŇčgi ne bun mbe nzuai. Barnabas nen mbe nzuav, ana vh…®ra Sor khaŇč t…®gap Damaskusan Zisas z…® bun suaŇčgi ne bun vh…®ra mbe nzuai.
\v 28 Barnabas Sor bun mbe suaŇčgim, Sor mbaram mbe phorgap Zerusareman kav, mbe phorga rui. Ana mbe phorga ruav, ana r…®vi fhu, ana khaŇč t…®gap Guma Bak…®me z…® bun nzuai.
\v 29 \x - \xo 9:29 \xt FG 6.1; 9.23; 11.20; 2 Ko 11.26\x*Ana vh…®ra khaŇč t…®gap mba Grik kama kaŇčgiap ana nzuai ZudaiŇč phorga nzuav khaŇč t…®gap mbe nzuav mbe dai. Ana maaŇč mbe mbuim, mbe ana shogirim, ana rimgirga tuavi ndi gari.
\v 30 \x - \xo 9:30 \xt Ga 1.21\x*Mbe maaŇč ana muun zav mbuim, mba ana phorgap Zisas z…®n vov ana khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ne mbararagiap mbaram ana ko vov, Sisaria Ňčgu bak…®men vergap, ana sarigim, ana Tarsus Ňčgu bak…®men vugi. \f a \fr 9:30 \ft Zumgum Barnabas Sorarnan vov Antiokan Ňčg…®r zav, ana nzuav garav Tarsusan vugi. Ndu FG 11.25 gan…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 31 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap za mba Zudia fhaiŇč gum, Gariri gum, Samaria fhain ki siosir ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za nzerara ki. Mba harigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gir mbe mbui fhu. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, sios th…®gap havhargiap mba Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi guigira vh…®rk…®vgi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me piin ki t…®va z…®n vuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mben kurkurav, mben ndavi havhargi, mbe thivgia havhargiap, r…®vi fhu.
\s1 Pita Ainiasan kurigim, ana nzerigi.
\p 
\v 32 Mba tugivigen, Pita za mba bigi ga ruav, vov Rida Ňčgu bak…®men verga ana ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui, ana mbe phorga ki.
\v 33 Pita maaŇč kav mba Ňčgun, ana guma mbe gangi. Mba guma z…® khare. Ainias. Ana bigi za rimgim, ana rui fhu, ana won kaara kim, harath…®gi mpari vh…®zgi.
\v 34 \x - \xo 9:34 \xt FG 3.6; 3.16; 4.10\x*Ana mbara muuŇčgiap kim, Pita khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAinias Zisas Krais ntigem ndu muuŇčgim, ndu nzerigi, ndu khavgip, won kaa gum bigi vhuuva.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, ana vhemkora khavgi.
\v 35 \x - \xo 9:35 \xt 1 Sto 5.16; FG 11.21\x*Ana khavgim, mba Ridan ki gumgi gu mbigi gum, mba Saronan mbas…®k taan ndava m…®…®t…®gar ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana gangiap, mbaram wari won ndavi domdorgiap Guma Bak…®me z…®n vui.
\s1 Pita Tabitar kurigim, ana khavgi.
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 9:36 \xt 1 T 2.10; Ta 3.8\x*Mba tugen Zopan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui mbiga mbe ki. Mba mbiga z…® khare, Tabita. Mbe Grik kaman kha z…®n ana kaai, Dorkas. Dorkas ana zazera t…®vir vhuuiŇčra mbui mbik ma. Ana vh…®ra mba bigi sosuagi gumgi gu mbigir kurkurigi mbik ma.
\v 37 Ana mba tugen r…®…®v kav rimgi. Ana rimgim, mbe ana khuma ruagiap, ana ndiga ndav, ana ndim, mba vun ndagi vundava t…®gim, ana ki.
\v 38 Mba Rida Ňčgu bak…®me, ana Zopa Ňčgun hara ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba Zopan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi mbari ki. Mbe kav, Pita Ridan ki kameŇč mbararagiap, mbe mbaram Pita nzuav guma phuni ndi mbarav khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko Ňčg…®p khaŇč Pita suaŇčri, ‚ÄėPita, ndu vhemkora nza han z…®ri. Ndu suigsuig…® thari.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 39 Mani zav maaŇč Pita ga suaŇčgim, Pita mbaram khavgiap, mani phorga vui. Pita mani phorga vov h…®gim, mbe mbaram Pitar kov mba vun ndagi vundavar ndai. Pita ndav, mba vundavar ndav th…®gim, mba mani rimgi mbigi, mbe zav Pita han thivgiap, wari nzi. Mbe nziav, mba Tabita fhum Ňčamra kav mbe ndim samgi shagi, mbe ntan Pita kh…®vi.
\v 40 \x - \xo 9:40 \xt Mt 9.25; Mk 5.40-41; Zo 11.43; FG 7.60\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Pita mbaram za mba gumgi gu mbigi ga vharigim, mbe za k…®rar hegi. Mbe za k…®rar hegim, Pita mbaram th…®panani ph…®rgiap, fav, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Ana Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, mbaram dorgap, mba mbiga khuma garav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúTabita, ndu khavik!‚ÄĚ Pita maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, mba mbik r…®mani segav, Pita garav, mbaram khavgia peregi.
\v 41 Ana khavgia perigim, Pita mbara vov, ana hara suirav, ana ragim, ana khavgia th…®gi. Ana khavgia th…®gim, Pita mbaram mba Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gum mba mani rimgi mbigir kamgim, mbe ana han zim, ana anan mbe kh…®vav khaŇč mbe nzuai, Tabita taagia khavgi.
\v 42 Pita Tabitar kurigim, ana taagia khavgim, mba kameŇč za mba Zopa Ňčgu bak…®me ruigim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za ne mbararagi. Mbe ne mbararagiap, mbe gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera Guma Bak…®me khoth…®gi.
\v 43 \x - \xo 9:43 \xt FG 10.6\x*Mbe Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gim, Pita rari vh…®rvera Zopan kegi. Ana Zopan kha guma phorga ana phena kui. Mba guma z…® khare, Saimon. Saimon, ana borombaga ndirar mbark…®rga Ňčaari vh…®rve ga mbui guma ma.
\c 10
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me enser Korniriusan h…®gap, ana phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Mt 8.5; FG 27.1-3\x*Mba tugivigen, guma mbe Sisarian Ňčgu bak…®men ki. Mba guma z…® khare, Kornirius. Kornirius, ana Roman 100 th…®gi ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan ma. Mbe kha z…®n mben kaai, mbe Itarin Ňägu Bak…®me Fhain Ntari Ga Mbui G…®…®t…®vi ma.
\v 2 \x - \xo 10:2 \xt FG 8.2; 10.22; 10.35; 22.12\x*Kornirius, ana Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n vui guma ma. Ana phorga ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, mbe guigira Fhe Bak…®men r…®vav, ana piin ki nt…®…®ri ma. Ana vh…®ra Ňčk…®…®r vh…®rver mba bigi sosuagi Zudain kurkurigi guma ma.
\v 3 \x - \xo 10:3 \xt FG 3.1; 10.30; 11.13\x*Ana raa mben ra vera vov Ňčkotugur phuni khegene ndim, ana r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap, big…®n mbe gari.
\v 4 Ana Korniriusan kamgim, Kornirius kh…®rav, ana garav, guigira rivgiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuman Rum, khar ram muuŇčgi bigeŇč khare?‚ÄĚ \fig Enser Kornirius phorga nzuai. (10.1)|src="HK00193C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="10.1"\fig*
\p Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®me enser khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKornirius, ndu mba Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, ndu vh…®ra won Ňčk…®…®a gum bigir mba bigi sosuagi gumgi gu mbigin kurkurigi t…®vi, Fhe Bak…®me mba bigi gangi.
\v 5 Ndu ntigem, gumgi thari ga sararim, mbe Zopan Ňčg…®p, kha guman kuv z…®rga. Mba guma z…®, Saimon, ana z…® mbe Pita.
\v 6 \x - \xo 10:6 \xt FG 9.43\x*Ana mba harigi Saimon han ana phenan ki. Ana mba han ki, Saimon, ana borombaga ndirar Ňčgari guma ma. Ana phen mbas…®k gaara ki.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Mba Fhe Bak…®me enser mba kamen Kornirius ga suaŇčgiap vugi. Ana vugim, Kornirius mbaram won Ňčaara guma phuninin kaav, mbaram won ntari ga mbui g…®mat…®va mben kamgi. Ana mba kamgi g…®mat…®v, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi z…®n vui guma ma. Ana vh…®ra Kornirius phorga ki guma ma.
\v 8 Kornirius mben kamgim, mbe ana han zim, ana za mba ana h…®gi bigi, ana thukh…®ngira mba bigir mbe neŇčgegap mbe sarigim, mbe Zopan vui.
\s1 Pita r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap big…®n mbe gangi.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 10:9 \xt FG 11.5\x*Mbe vuav kav, tuava kuigap, m…®timanera mbe khavgiap wari vui. Mbe vov, ph…®…®Ňč han mbaim, mbe Zopa Ňčgun h…®r zav mbui. Mbe vov, Ňčgun han mbaim, mba tugera Pita Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suan zav phena k…®rar ndai.
\v 10 Pita Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav kav th…®hegi. Ana th…®hegim, mbe mba tuavra kim, ana mbaram r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap big…®n mbevi gari.
\v 11 \x - \xo 10:11 \xt FG 11.5-17\x*Ana garim, buip fhogim, ana shaa bak…® fhara muuŇčgi big…®na mbe garim, mbe mpiin ana khorin fegi fara muuŇčgiap ana ndim mbarigim, ana zeri.
\v 12 Ana zerim, Pita gari, za kha nuiana ki s…®gi gum korigi gumgi pi nt…®…®ri, gumgi pi fhuv nt…®…®ri, nta zam mba shaar vhen ki.
\v 13 Pita nta garav mbararagim, Fhe Bak…®me khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúPita, ndu khavgip, kha s…®gi shog…®p ntan mb…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 \x - \xo 10:14 \xt Wkp 11.1-47; Lo 14.3; 14.7; Ese 4.14\x*Pita mbaram Fhe Bak…®me mbararagiap, ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me, gu mbeg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara! Gu tuga then ndu n…®man khaŇč muuŇčgi s…®ga mbat…®gi the mbegi fhu. Gu vh…®ra khe nza mb…®rgeŇč thagi s…®gi khare.‚ÄĚ
\v 15 \x - \xo 10:15 \xt Mt 15.11; Mk 7.15; 7.19; FG 10.28; Ro 14.14-20; 1 Ko 10.25\x*Pita ne nzuaim, Fe Bak…®me wom phenat…®t…®gap khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi big…®n the mbat…®gi fhuvara. Ndu ana muuŇčgi bigi, ndu khaŇč nta suaŇč thari, ‚ÄėNta mbat…®gi.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Mba bigi h…®r…® mpuani khegene ga muuŇčgim, Pita nta gangim, nta vhemkora taagia Hevenan ndagi.
\p 
\v 17 Pita mba bigi gangiap, nta n…®…®Ňčge nzuav nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbuavra kim, mba Kornirius sarigi gumgi, mbe zav mbar hegi. Mbe hegap, Saimon phena nzuav mben nzaim, mbe Saimon phenan mbe kh…®vigim, mbe vov, Saimon phena th…®mkamani thivgi.
\v 18 Mbe zav thivgiap, mben nzav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha guma Saimon, ana z…® mbe Pita, ana khaŇč kire? Ee, fhuve?‚ÄĚ
\v 19 \x - \xo 10:19 \xt FG 11.12; 13.2\x*Pita mba gangi bigi, ana nta nd…®knd…®g…®ra kim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ana nd…®knd…®ga khavgiap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma phuni khegene mbur ndu nzuav gari.
\v 20 Ndu khavgip, ndun Ňčgirg…®p, mbe phorg…®p Ňčg…®. Ndu nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rver muun thari. Gu nduara mbe sarigim, mbe zegi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Ana mba nd…®knd…®gar Pita nd…®…®im, Pita mbaram verav, mba gumgi gangiap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nara nzuav gari, gura khare. Nde bigeŇč nzuav na ndim garire?‚ÄĚ
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt FG 10.1-2; 22.12\x*Pita maaŇč nzuaim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Kornirius, mba 100 th…®gi ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan nza sarigim, nza zegi. Kornirius, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me r…®vav, ana nzuai t…®vi vhuuiŇčra z…®n vui guman ma. Ana vh…®ra mba ZudaiŇč gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira ana vuzvugi guma ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®me enserar Ňčaar anan h…®gap, khaŇč ana suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėNdu ana han ana phenan Ňčg…®rim, ana ndu nzuai buni mbarararga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 23 \x - \xo 10:23 \xt FG 10.45; 11.12\x*Mbe maaŇč Pita ga suaŇčgim, Pita mbaram mben kov phena vhen vergim, mbe ana phorga kuigim, ana m…®timanera khavgiap, mbe phorgap, mbe vui. Pita mbe phorga vuim, mba Zopan ana phorgav Zisas z…®n vui gumgi mbari, mbe vh…®ra Pita phorga vui.
\s1 Pita Kornirius phenan vui.
\p 
\v 24 Mbe mba m…®timanera khavgia vov, Sisarian hegi. Mbe zim, Kornirius mbe nzuav garav kav, ana mbaram za won fegutari gum won khurkhuu ga suaŇčgim, mbe za vov ana phenan wari fugi.
\v 25 Mbe za wari fugap kim, Pita vov, Kornirius phenan havra thagim, Kornirius vov, Pitar ndikndigap, mbaram won th…®panani ph…®rgiap Pita n…®man fagi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 10:26 \xt FG 14.13-15; VB 19.10\x*Pita mbaram ana nzuaim, ana khavgia th…®gim, ana khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu vh…®ra, gu guma kh…®n ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Pita maaŇč ana nzuav, mbaram ana phorga mani phena vhen verav, Pita mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve garim, mbe Kornirius phena vhen phoga vhuigap ki.
\p 
\v 28 \x - \xo 10:28 \xt Zo 4.9; FG 15.8-9; Ga 2.12-14; Ef 3.6\x*Pita khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde za khueŇč kaŇčgi. Nza ZudaiŇč, nzan t…®v khaŇč nzuai, nza ZudaiŇč, nza harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri phorg…® keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhu. Nza vh…®ra mbe phorg…® k…®v, buni suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhu. Gu ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me khuen na kh…®vigim, gu kaŇčgi. Gu ntigem khaŇč suanga fhu, harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, mbe Fhe Bak…®me n…®man mbat…®gi o, gu mbe phorg…® keg…®rga fhu. Gu maaŇč suanga tukt…®gi fhu.
\v 29 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde na nzuav kama ndim mbarigim, gu nde daaŇč thav, gu nde suaŇčgi kameŇč mbararagiap, gu z…®gi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu taagia nden nzai, nde thaŇč nzuav na nzuav kama ndi mbarigim, gu z…®gi?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 10:30 \xt FG 1.10; 3.1\x*Ana ne nzuaim, Kornirius ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúEna, big…®n mueŇč nan h…®gim, feth…®gi rari vh…®zgi. Gu ruar…®mraar wo phenan kav, ra verav phuni khegene ndim, gu kav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ki. Gu Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav kim, guma mbe shagi guigira hurgiap Ňčgara gari, ana fhura hav, na n…®man mbar th…®gi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 10:31 \xt Dan 10.12; Hi 6.10\x*Ana th…®gap khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėKornirius, Fhe Bak…®me ndu ana nzuai buni, ana nta mbararav ana vh…®ra ndu mba bigi sosuagi gumgir kurkurav mbe n…®…®Ňčgi bigi, ana vh…®ra nta gangiap, ana ndun khurkhura za mbui.
\v 32 Ndu Zopan kha guma ga suaŇčv kama ndi mbarari. Mba guma z…® khare, Saimon, ana z…® mbe khare Pita. Ana kha guma han ana phenan ki. Mba guma, ana z…® vh…®ra Saimon, ana borombaga ndirar Ňčgari guma ma. Ana phen mbas…®k gaara ki.‚Äô
\v 33 Mba Fhe Bak…®me enser maaŇč na suaŇčgia thagim, gu za kha gumgi ga sarigim, mbe ndu nzuav mbar vugi. Ndu t…®var vhuuaŇč muuŇčgiap, ndu nzerara z…®gi. Nza ntigem, nza zam Fhe Bak…®me n…®man ki. Ana mba nza suanga kaman havhareŇč, ana nen ndu suaŇčgi. Ndu ntigem nen nza suaŇčrim, nza ne mbarararga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pita Kornirius phenan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 34 \x - \xo 10:34 \xt Lo 10.17; 1 Sml 16.7; Ro 2.11; Ga 2.6; Ef 6.9; Kor 3.25; 1 Pi 1.17\x*Pita Kornirius suaŇčgi kameŇč mbararagiap, mbaram khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuigi guarara, gu ntigem kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me t…®va bavira za kha gumgi gu mbigi ga mbui.
\v 35 \x - \xo 10:35 \xt Zo 9.31; Ro 2.13; 1 Ko 12.13; Ga 3.28; Ef 3.6\x*Ana za kha Ňčgui gumgi, mba ana piin kav ana nzuai t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi, ana za t…®var vhuuŇčra mbe mbui.
\v 36 \x - \xo 10:36 \xt Sng 107.20; Ais 52.7; 57.19; Mt 28.18; Ro 10.12; VB 17.14\x*Nde Fhe Bak…®me nza IsreriŇč ana nza suaŇčgi kameŇč, nde ne kaŇčgi. Ana mba nza suaŇčgi buni vhuuiŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėZisas Krais, ana za kha nuianan ki gumgir Guma Bak…®me ma. Ana mbe mbuim, mbe za Fhe Bak…®me phorgap ndava bavira ki.‚Äô
\v 37 \x - \xo 10:37 \xt Mt 3.16; 4.12-17; Ru 4.14; 4.17-20; Zo 3.2; Hi 1.9\x*Nde mba za Zudian h…®gi bigeŇč, nde ne kaŇčgi. Mba bigeŇč, Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma, ana mba Garirir mba gumgi gu mbigi, ana mba ruarga buni bun mbe suaŇčgia thugim, mba bigeŇč h…®gi.
\v 38 Nde kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me Nasaret guma Zisas farasarav, won Ňäina Ňäaarar ana nd…®…®av, vh…®ra ŇčkasŇčka bak…®men ana n…®…®Ňčgim, Zisas za tamtam kha Ňčguia ruav, gumgi gu mbigir kurkurigi. Ana maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me, ana ana phorga kav, anan kurkurigim, ana mba Satan farfagi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe mbuim, mbe taagia nzerigi.
\v 39 \x - \xo 10:39 \xt FG 2.32; 5.30\x*Nza ana mba Zudia gum Zerusareman muuŇčgi bigi, nza za nta gangiap, nta bun nzuai gumgi ma. Nza mba bun nzuai guma, mbe ana ndim, khanarareŇč ga ntorgim, ana rimgi.
\v 40 \x - \xo 10:40 \xt FG 2.24; 1 Ko 15.4-7\x*Ana rimgim, ra phuni khegene vh…®zgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgiap, ana sarigim, ana wom vov mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®man h…®gim, mbe ana gangi.
\v 41 \x - \xo 10:41 \xt Ru 24.42-43; Zo 14.17-24; 15.27; FG 1.8; 13.31\x*Ana maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, ana khavgiap, ana za mba Zudain h…®gi fhuvara. Ana nza mba fhum Fhe Bak…®me wo buni vhuuiŇč bun suan zav farasarigi gumgi, ana nzara h…®gi. Ana vh…®ra rimgiap taagia khavgim, nza ana garav, nza vh…®ra ana phorga mbegi.
\v 42 \x - \xo 10:42 \xt Mt 28.19-20; FG 17.31; Ro 14.9-10; 2 Ko 5.10; 2 T 4.1; 1 Pi 4.5\x*Nza ana phorga pim, ana wo buni vhuuiŇč bun suan zav kama havharar nza nd…®…®v, vh…®ra khueŇč bun suan zav nza suaŇčgi. Ana mba Fhe Bak…®me kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suan zav farasarigi guma ma.
\v 43 \x - \xo 10:43 \xt Ais 33.24; 53.5-6; 53.11; Jer 31.34; Dan 9.24; Mai 7.18; Sek 13.1; Ro 10.11; Ga 3.22\x*Mba fhum Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi ana bun nzuav khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi, gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana z…® mbararav, ana buni khothiv…®rga, mbe ana z…®n panan, Fhe Bak…®me mbe fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgirga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi.
\p 
\v 44 \x - \xo 10:44 \xt FG 4.31; 8.15-16; 11.15; 15.8\x*Pita Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč buna Kornirius gu mbe nzuavra kim, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaara sarigim, ana mbe han zergi.
\v 45-46 \x - \xo 10:45-46 \xt FG 2.4; 10.23; 11.18; 19.6; Ga 3.14\x*Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mben han zergim, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui ZudaiŇč gumgi, mbe Pita phorga zegi. Mbe mba harigi gumgi gu mbigi mbararagim, mbe Ňčguir kaa ga vhov Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuagi. Mba Pita phorga zegi gumgi, mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKhar gan…®. Fhe Bak…®me fhura won Ňäina Ňäaarar mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi ga nd…®…®i.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Pita khaŇč mbe nzuai,
\v 47 \x - \xo 10:47 \xt FG 8.36; 11.17; 15.8-9; Ro 10.12\x*‚ÄúKheiŇč nza fhara mba Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi t…®vara muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, the mbe ruargen nza th…®v…®rie?‚ÄĚ
\v 48 \x - \xo 10:48 \xt FG 2.38\x*Pita maaŇč suaŇčgiap khaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Zisas z…®n panan ruagiri.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč mbe suaŇčgim, mbe ruai. Mbe ruagiap, khaŇč Pita ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu rari thari nza phorg…®v keg…®p Ňčg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\c 11
\s1 Pita Zerusareman ndav mba h…®gi bigi bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, gum mba mbe phorgav Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe tamtam Zudia fhain ki. Mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi mbararagi, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararagiap, mbe vh…®ra nta ndigi.
\v 2 Mbe mba buni vhuuiŇč ndigim, Pita Zerusareman ndaim, mba Zerusareman kav, Zisas z…®n vui gumgi, mbe ne mbararav khaŇč t…®gap mba fooi t…®va suirav havhargiap, ana z…®n vui nt…®…®ri ma. Mbe Zerusareman ki. Mbe ne nzuav Pita ga vhegi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 11:3 \xt FG 10.28; Ga 2.12\x*Mbe ana vhegap khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu ram mbui t…®va muuŇčgiap vov, warir fooŇč thagi gumgi, ndu mbe phenan vugap, ndu mbe phorga mbegi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Mbe maaŇč Pita nzuaim, Pita mbaram mba ana h…®gi bigi, ana za ntan mbe neŇčgegi. Ana ntan mbe neŇčgav khaŇč mbe nzuai,
\v 5 \x - \xo 11:5 \xt FG 10.9-48\x*‚ÄúGu Zopan Ňčgu bak…®men kav, gu Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav kav, gu r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap big…®na mbe gangi. Gu garav, shaa bak…®me fara muuŇčgi big…®na mbe, gu ana garim, buip fhogim, ana zeri. Mbe mpiin ana khorin fegi fara muuŇčgiap ana ndim mbarigim, ana zeri.
\v 6 Ana zerim, gu tuituigip ana gangir zav mbuav, gu ana garav, gu mbark…®rga s…®gi vh…®rve, gu nta gari. Gu nta garav, gu gumgi dai s…®gi, gu nta garav, gu ruaŇčruaŇčgi s…®gi gu nta gari. Gu vh…®ra mpari gum p…®ri gari, gu vh…®ra korigi gari.
\v 7 Gu nta garav, gu Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč mbararagim, ana khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėPita, ndu khavgip mbu s…®gi shog…®p ntan mb…®.‚Äô
\v 8 Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč nzuaim, gu khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me, gu mbeg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara! Gu tuga then ndu n…®man khaŇč muuŇčgi s…®ga mbat…®ga the mbegi fhu. Gu vh…®ra thagi s…®gi mbari vh…®ra khare.‚Äô
\v 9 Gu maaŇč nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®me wom phenat…®t…®gap khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi big…®n the, ndu khaŇč ana suaŇč thari, ana mbat…®gi. Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi, nta za bigir vhuuiŇčra.‚Äô
\v 10 Mba bigi h…®r…® mpuani khegene ga muuŇčgim, gu nta gangim, nta taagia buivar ndagi.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúMba bigi taagia buivar ndagim, mba Kornirius na nzuav sarigi guma phuni khegene, mbe za gu ki phena th…®ma thivgi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 11:12 \xt Zo 16.13; FG 10.19; 10.23; 10.45\x*Mbe thivgim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar kha nd…®knd…®gar na nd…®…®i, ‚ÄėNdu mbe phorg…®v Ňčg…®ri. Ndu nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rver muuŇč thari.‚Äô
\v 13 Nza Kornirius phena vhen vergim, ana mbaram mba Fhe Bak…®me enser ana phenan vhen vergap, ana phorga suaŇčgi ne bun nza nzuai. Ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėMba Fhe Bak…®me enser khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu gumgi thari ga sararim, mbe Zopan Ňčg…®p, Saimonan kuv ndu han z…®ri. Saimon, ana z…® mbe khare, Pita.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 \x - \xo 11:14 \xt FG 16.31\x*Ana z…®v, buni tharir ndu suanga, ana mba ndu suanga buni, ndu ntan panan Fhe Bak…®me taagip ndu ndiv, mba ndu phenan ki nt…®…®ri, ana za mbe ndigirga.‚Äô
\v 15 \x - \xo 11:15 \xt FG 2.4\x*Kornirius mba bigir nza neŇčgega thugim, gu mbaram kama hegap, mbe phorga nzuavra thagim, Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaara sarigim, ana mba fhum fhara guarara, nzan han zergi farara muuŇčgiap, mben han zergi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 11:16 \xt Jol 2.28; Mt 3.11; Zo 1.26; 1.33; FG 1.5\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgia, gangiap, gu mba Guma Bak…®me fhum suaŇčgi kameŇč ga nd…®rigi. Ana fhum khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėZon Gumgi Ruai Guma, ana fhum mb…®n gumgi gu mbigi ruagi. Nde Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar nde ruarga.‚Äô
\v 17 \x - \xo 11:17 \xt FG 10.47; 15.8-9\x*Nza fhum Guma Bak…®me Zisas Ňäina khoth…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me fhura won Ňäaarar nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Ntige mbara muuŇčgi, ana fhura won Ňäina Ňäaarar mbe n…®…®Ňčgi. Na gu ram muuŇčgi khesharigi guma, gu Fhe Bak…®me nduara mbe mbui Ňčaar, gu ana th…®v…®rie?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 11:18 \xt FG 13.48; 14.27; Ro 10.12-13; 15.9; 15.16\x*Pita mba buni mbe neŇčgegim, mba gumgi mba buni mbararagiap, mbe wom Pita ga vheg…®rga nd…®knd…®k mben ki fhu. Mbe thav Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza ntige kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra ndavi domdor…®rganeŇč harigi Ňčgui gumgi kh…®rigi, mbe vh…®ra zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndirga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Antiokan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ruagi gumgi gu mbigi ki.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 11:19 \xt FG 8.1-4\x*Mba tugen, mbe Stiven shogi ana rimgim, mbe vh…®ra t…®vi mbat…®gar mba Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve mbe rav tamtam vov, mbe mbari vov Fonisia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain vuim, mbe mbari rav Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rigen vuim, mbe mbari rav Antiok Ňčgu bak…®men vegi. Mbe vegap, maaŇč kav Zisas muuŇčgi bigi gum ana buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p Mbe mba buni vhuuiŇč bun harigi Ňčguir gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai fhuvara. Mbe mba bigi bun ZudaiŇč gumgi gu mbigira nzuai.
\v 20 Mbe maaŇč mbuim, gumgi mbari vh…®ra mben r…®gar ki, mba gumgi mbe mbari Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rige gum, Sairini Ňčgu bak…®me gumgi ma. Mbe vh…®ra ndav, Antiokan kav, mbe vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me Zisas buni vhuuiŇč bun mba GrikiŇč ga nzuai.
\v 21 \x - \xo 11:21 \xt FG 2.41\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Guma Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka mbe phorga kim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe nzuai buni mbararav, nta khoth…®gap, ndavi domdorav Guma Bak…®me z…®n vui.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 11:22 \xt FG 4.36\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba Zisas buni z…®n vov ana khoth…®gap ruagi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Zerusareman kav mba bigi kameŇč mbararagiap, mbe mbaram, Barnabas ga sarigim, ana Antiokan vergi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 11:23 \xt FG 2.41; 5.14; 6.5; 11.21; 13.43\x*Ana verav garim, Fhe Bak…®me guigira mben kurkurav t…®var vhuuŇčra mbe mbuim, ana mbe gangiap, guigira ndikndigi. Ana ndikndigap, mbaram mba gumgi gu mbigi ana wom za mbe nd…®knd…®gi khavi, mbe guigira Guma Bak…®me z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\v 24 Barnabas, ana vh…®ra guman vhuuŇč ma. Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira ana rugap ki. Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k guigira havhargi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe Guma Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir vhen zeri.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 11:25 \xt FG 9.30\x*Barnabas maaŇč mbe thav, Sor ga nzuav garav Tarsusan vui.
\v 26 \x - \xo 11:26 \xt 1 Pi 4.16\x*Ana vov, maam Sor gangiap, ana kov taagiap Antiokan z…®gi. Ana Sorar kov, mani Antiokan z…®gap, mani maam mba Zisas z…®n vuav, ana z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi, mani mbe phorga ki. Mani mbe phorga kav, mani gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera, mani Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe nzuav mbe kh…®vigi. Mani maaŇč mbuav, mbe phorga kim, mpari mbave vh…®zgi. Mba tugen, Antiokan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe fhara guarara Zisas z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi z…® ndigi.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 11:27 \xt FG 13.1; 15.32; 21.9; 1 Ko 12.28; Ef 4.11\x*Mba tugen, Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi mbari, mbe Zerusareman kegap, Antiokan zergi.
\v 28 \x - \xo 11:28 \xt FG 21.10\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma mbe, ana z…® khare, Agabus, ana Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ana rugim, ana an ŇčkasŇčkar panan khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba tivgip thir vh…®z…®rga tuga bak…®me za kha Rom guman pan gari Ňčguir h…®g…®rga.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, zumgum Sisar Krodius Ňčgui gari guman pan ki tugen, mba thir vh…®zi tuga bak…®me h…®gi.
\v 29 \x - \xo 11:29 \xt Ro 15.26; 1 Ko 16.1; 2 Ko 9.1\x*Agabus ne suaŇčgim, mba Zisas z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi ne mbararagiap, mbaram, wari t…®gap kama shogiap, mbaram, Ňčk…®…®a ndi, mba Zudian Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir kurkura zav nzuai. Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgiap mba Zisas z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za wari kh…®nan Ňčk…®…®a ndia za sui.
\v 30 \x - \xo 11:30 \xt FG 12.25\x*Mbe mba Ňčk…®…®a ndi suegap, mbaram, Barnabas gum Sor ga sarigim, mani mba Ňčk…®…®a ndiga ndav, mba Zisas z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani ga n…®…®Ňčgi.
\c 12
\s1 Herot Zems shogi ana rimgim, ana Pita ndim b…®na kh…®ngi.
\p 
\v 1 Mba tugen, Herot ana Ňčgui gari guman pan kav, ana h…®gap, Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mbarir farfa zav nzuaim, mbe mben suigiap, mbe ndim b…®na suegi. \f a \fr 12:1 \ft Kha Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Herot, ana mba fhum Ňčgui vh…®rve gangi guman pan Herot nz…®k ma. Mba Herot, ana Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan kim, Maria Zisas tegi. Mba Herot, ana Ňčgui vh…®rve guman pan Agripa tegi ndia ma. \f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Mt 4.21; 20.23\x*Ana nzuaim, mbe Zon fega Zems, mbe ntari ga mbui kozan ana fh…®ra thugim, ana rimgi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt FG 4.3\x*Ana maaŇč Zems ga muuŇčgim, mba ZudaiŇč ne gangiap, mba t…®va vuzvugi. Ana mbaram mba mbe vhuui fhuv viktuma pi tuga bak…®men, ana vh…®ra Pita suirigi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Kis 12.1-27\x*Ana Pita suirav, ana ndim b…®na kh…®ngiap, mbara ana ndim feth…®gi ph…®nan mbarigi g…®…®t…®vi farve kh…®ngi. Mba feth…®gi ph…®nan ki g…®…®t…®vi mba warir kurkurav ana gan…®nga. Mba feth…®gi ph…®nan ki g…®…®t…®vi, mbe za wari t…®kh…®ngiap, mben vh…®rve khaŇč muuŇčgi, ph…®k bavira mporath…®gi. Herot khuen rargap, Pita ndim b…®na kh…®ngim, ana ki. Ana mba Pasova tuga bak…®me vh…®zgirim, ana za Pita ndigi Ňčg…®p mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®man ana suaŇčv suanga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 12:5 \xt Ze 5.16\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Pita b…®nan kim, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni z…®n vuav ana khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap ana nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčrim, ana Pitar kurarga.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me enser Pitar kurigim, ana b…®na thav k…®rar h…®gi.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt FG 5.23\x*Herot Pita suaŇčv suanga tuga sarigi. Ana gurmaŇčgip, ana suaŇčv suanga, mba maan Pita g…®mat…®va phuni k…®t…®ga r…®ga kui. Mbe shen phuninin ana kegap, g…®…®t…®vi mbari ndim th…®mkamanin fegim, mbe mba b…®na th…®mkamani garav ki.
\v 7 Mbe kav kim, Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe fhura mbar h…®gi. Ana h…®gim, vhava Ňčaar mbe mba b…®na vhee sh…®rigi. Ana mbaram Pita kuvs…®geŇč shogap, ana vhurav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúPita ndu vhemkora khavik.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč ana nzuaim, mbe mba Pita harani kegi shenani, ni fhura fh…®rgia n…®…®eŇč r…®gi.
\v 8 Mba sheni fh…®rgiap n…®…®eŇč r…®gim, mba Fhe Bak…®me enser khaŇč Pita nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khavgip wo shagi shargip, won Ňčkari shariveni shaara.‚ÄĚ Ana ne nzuaim, Pita mbara muuŇčgi. Ana mbara muuŇčgim, mba Fhe Bak…®me enser khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu won shaa mpeeŇč sharav na z…®n z…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt FG 10.3; 10.17; 11.5\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Pita mbaram khavgiap, mba Fhe Bak…®me enser phorga vui. Mba Fhe Bak…®me enser guigira mbe bigen Pita ga mbui. Ana maaŇč Pita ga mbuim, Pita khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ana r…®ma kui.
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Sng 34.7; Dan 3.28; 6.22; FG 5.19; Hi 1.14; 2 Pi 2.9\x*Ana Pitar kov, mani vov, mba b…®na th…®mkamani gari g…®…®t…®vir h…®ga vov, mba ain th…®mkamani gari g…®…®t…®vir h…®gap, mbaram vov Ňčgu bak…®men vui. Mani vov nin him, ni nduara fh…®rgim, mani k…®rar h…®gap, tuav mbe th…®ga veri. Mani mba tuav th…®ga verav, mba Fhe Bak…®me enser fhura Pita thav vugi.
\p 
\v 11 Ana Pita thav vugim, Pita nd…®knd…®k taagia ana zim, ana mbaram khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúO, gu ntige kaŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe sarigim, ana zav, Herot farve t…®n na ndiav, vh…®ra mba ZudaiŇč nan muun zav mbui nd…®knd…®gi, ana vh…®ra mben t…®n na ndigi.‚ÄĚ
\v 12 \x - \xo 12:12 \xt FG 4.23; 12.5; 12.25; 15.37\x*Pita nen wo nzuav, mbaram Zon niamuuŇč Maria phenan vui, Zon z…® mbe khare, Mak. Mba phenan gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe wari fugap kav, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\v 13 Pita mbaram vov, mba phena th…®ma fukfugi. Ana th…®ma fukfugim, mba phenan Ňčgari Ňčaara mbik, ana z…® Roda, ana ana nzuav th…®ma fh…®r…® zav zi.
\v 14 Ana zav, Pita kama mbararagiap, ana ndava vhee guigira ndikndiga mbat…®ga mbuim, ana th…®ma fh…®r…® thagi. Ana thav taagia khuaf…® vhen verav, khaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúPita zav, mbu th…®mkamanin ki!‚ÄĚ
\v 15 \x - \xo 12:15 \xt Mt 18.10; FG 26.24\x*Ana maaŇč mbe nzuaim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu ŇčanŇčani o?‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč ana nzuaim, ana khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúFhuvara. Ana guigi guarara mbu th…®mkamanin.‚ÄĚ Mbe thav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúMbar, anan Ňčina ndu mbui.‚ÄĚ\f b \fr 12:15 \ft Mba tugen ZudaiŇč vh…®rve mbe khueŇč khoth…®gi, Fhe Bak…®me enseran Ňčaar khare, ana guman kera ki, ana vh…®ra mba gumara fara muuŇčgi. \f*
\p 
\v 16 Mbe maaŇč ana nzuaim, Pita mba th…®mkamanin kav th…®ma fukfugara ki. Mbe thav zav, th…®ma fh…®rgiap, ana gari. Mbe ana gangiap, mbe guigira Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 12:17 \xt FG 13.16; 19.33; 21.40\x*Mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga mbuim, Pita mbaram, mbe th…®ri mp…®rav farvera mbe nzuai. Ana mbe nzuaim, mbe th…®…®ri mp…®rigim, ana mbaram mba Guma Bak…®me ana kurav, ana ndigap, mba b…®na thav k…®rar h…®gi nen mbe neŇčgi. Ana mba bigir mbe neŇčga vov, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha bigi bun Zems gum mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčgiri.‚ÄĚ Pita maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbe thav harigi Ňčanen vugi. \f c \fr 12:17 \ft Kha Zems ana Zisasan Ňčguk ma. Ndu Garesia 1.19 gan…®ri. Ana Zerusareman Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman pan kege. \f*
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 12:18 \xt FG 5.22-24\x*Pita mba maan b…®na thav vugim, m…®n thugim, mba b…®na gari g…®…®t…®vi, mbe garim, Pita mba b…®na vhen ki fhu. Mbe mbaram Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, rivgiap, nduarira warir nzav, khaŇč wari ga nzuai, ‚ÄúMbaia, Pita maaŇč ki?‚ÄĚ
\v 19 Mbe Pita nzuav warir nzaim, mba kameŇč vov Herotan h…®gim, Herot kaŇčgi, Pita mbu b…®nan ki fhu. Ana mbaram gumgi mbari ga sarigim, mbe vov Pita ndi gari. Mbe vov Pita ndi garav, mbe ana gangi fhu. Herot mbaram mba b…®nan Pita gangi g…®…®t…®vi, ana kama havharar khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúGu mbe shogirim, mbe vh…®zgirga.‚ÄĚ Herot maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana zumgum Zudia thav khavgiap, verav, Sisarian vergap anan ki.
\s1 Herot Rimgi.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt 1 Kin 5.9-11; Ese 27.17\x*Herot Ňčgui gari guman pan ana guigira vhega mbat…®gar Taia Ňčgu bak…®me gum Saidonan Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi ga mbui. Ana mbe vhegim, mbe mbaram wari t…®kh…®ngiap zav ana gari. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe ana gari fhain kega zi mba, mbe nta pi. Mbe ana gan…® zav, mbe fharav vov, mba Ňčgui gari guman pan ki ŇčaneŇč gari guman pan Brastus, phorga nzuaim, ana mbe m…®nmbarigi.
\p Ana mbe m…®nmbarigim, mbe zumgum vov Herot garav, ana nzai, ana mbe korar muuŇčgip, ana mba mbe vhegi kameŇč rimgirga.
\p 
\v 21 Mbe vov maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, Herot mbaram ra mben mbe sarigi. Ana mba raan, ana Ňčgui gari guman pan wo nz…®…®i s…®…®aŇč muuŇčgip, won mpirmpir…®ga perav, mba buna bak…®men mbe suanga.
\v 22 Ana mba kamen mbe nzuaim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe kaav, nz…®…®v, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKhe tor mbe kamthooŇč ma. Khe guma kamthooŇč fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt 1 Sml 25.38; 2 Sml 24.17; Sng 115.1; Dan 5.20\x*Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Herot mba kameŇč mbararagiap, khaŇč mbe suaŇč thagi, ‚ÄúNde Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuari‚ÄĚ. Ana maaŇč muuŇč thagim, Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe zav ana shogi. Ana ana shogim, r…®mr…®m mbat…®k mbe ana h…®gim, faari ana ndava vhee pim, ana rimgi.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 12:24 \xt Ais 55.11; FG 6.7; 19.20; Kor 1.6\x*Ana rimgim Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč, nta khaŇč t…®ga vov k…®vgiap Ňčgui vh…®rvera vui.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 12:25 \xt FG 11.29-30; 12.12; 13.5; 13.13; 15.37\x*Barnabas gum Sor, mani Zerusareman wani won Ňčaara vh…®zgiap, mbaram taagia Antiokan veri. Mani verav, Zon Mak ndigim, ana mani phorga veri.
\c 13
\ms1 Por Zisas buni vhuuiŇč bun harigi Ňčgui vh…®rve ga suaŇčgi.
\s1 Mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ndig…®p, harigi Ňčguir Ňčg…®r zav Barnabas gum Por ndim fagi. \fig [map]|alt="Map of Por na Barnabas i go raun na autim gutnius." src="paul1.tif" size="span" copy="The British and Foreign Bible Society" ref="Farasegi Gumgi 13"\fig*
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt FG 11.27\x*Khe AntiokiŇč neŇčgi buni khare. Mben gumgi mbari, mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Mben gumgi mbari, mbe Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vir mba Zisas z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vi. Mba Ňčaara mbui gumgi z…®ri khare, Barnabas gum, Simeon, ana z…® mbe Niger, Rusius, Sairini Ňčgu bak…®me guma, Sor gum, Manain. Manain, ana mba Ňčgui gari guman vhari Herotan khurkhum ma. \f a \fr 13:1 \ft Kha z…® ‚ÄúNiger‚ÄĚ, ne khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúPh…®…®gi.‚ÄĚ MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gumgi mbari kha ndiknd…®ga mbui, Simeon, ana Afrika guma ma. \f*
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt FG 9.15; Ro 10.15; Ga 1.15; Ef 3.7-8; 1 T 2.7; Hi 5.4\x*Tuga mben mba gumgi gu mbigi, mba thav mbe Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbuav ki. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar kha nd…®knd…®gar mbe nd…®…®i. ‚ÄúNde Barnabas gum Sor ndi farim, gu mba manin kamgi Ňčaar, mani anan muuŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt FG 6.6\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mban mb…®rgen wari th…®vav, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, wari won farir mani kh…®ngiap, mani ga nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, mani ga sarigim, mani vui.
\s1 Barnabas gum Sor Saiprusan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; 13.13; 13.46; 15.37; 15.39\x*Mbe maaŇč mani ga muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mani ga rugim, mani vov Serusia Ňčgu bak…®men vergi. Mani vov, Serusian maam kema r…®gi. Mani kema r…®gim, mba kem mani ndiga vov, Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rigen vugi.
\v 5 Mani Saiprusan vugap, mbaram vov, Saramis Ňčgu bak…®me vugap, mbaram vov mbe ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi pheni vherir verav Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Zon Mak vh…®ra mani phorga vugap, manin kurkurigi.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 13:6 \xt 2 T 3.8\x*Mani za mba Saiprus r…®gak…®r…®ge ruigi. Mani rua vov, Pafos Ňčgu bak…®men vugi. Mani Pafosan vugap, mani guma mbe gari, ana ki, mba guma z…® khare, Barzisas. Ana mbar ki mbar ki tori gum bigi ga mbui guma ma. Ana vh…®ra Zudain guiguigi kamthooŇč guma ma.
\v 7 Mba guma, ana mba Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari Sergius Paurus, phorga ki guma ma. Sergius Paurus, ana nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč kav bigi kaŇčgi guma ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuiŇč mbararar zav, Barnabas gum Sor ga nzuav Ňčg…®…®a muuŇčgim, mani ana han zi.
\v 8 Mba tori ga mbui guma, mbe Grik kaman kha z…®n ana kaai, Erimas. Erimas, ana h…®gap, Barnabas gum Sor mbui Ňčaara mbev…® za mbui. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, mba Ňčgui gari guman panan vhari, ana Zisas khoth…®g…®rgane, ana ne thagi.
\v 9 Ana mba vuzvuk ana kim, Sor ana z…® mbe khare, Por, ana guigira Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar ana rugap ki. Ana purara Erimas garav, khaŇč ana nzuai. \f b \fr 13:9 \ft Kha z…® Sor, ana Hibruin kaman z…® ma. Por, ana Grikin kaman z…® ma. Mbe gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Sor Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbua ruav, nduara kha z…®n wo t…®gi, Por. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana mba Grikin kama nzuai gumgi gu mbigi phorga Ňčgari. \f*
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Mt 13.38; Zo 8.44; 1 Zo 3.8\x*‚ÄúNdu Satanan kam ma. Ndu kha t…®vir vhuuiŇč, ndu za panan nta kegi guma ma. Ndu bigi guiguigi t…®vi gum t…®vi mbat…®gi guigira ndun ndava vhee givigi. Ndu vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me bunin vhuuiŇč, ndu khaŇč nta nzuai, ‚ÄėNta gugugi buni ma.‚Äô Ee, ndu mba t…®vi, ndu nta thamthargeŇč thagire?
\v 11 \x - \xo 13:11 \xt Kis 9.3; 1 Sml 5.6; FG 9.8\x*Ndu mbarara! Fhe Bak…®men farve ntigem ndu th…®g…®rga, ndun r…®mani ntige mp…®rarga. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip tuga mpeeŇčnera keg…®rga, ndu ran Ňčaara gangirga fhuvara.‚ÄĚ Por nen Erimas ga nzuavra thagim, buiva ph…®gage g…®ng…®ngi fara muuŇčgi big…®na mbe vhemkora zav, Erimas r…®mani vharigi. Mba big…®na ph…®gage zav, ana vharigim, ana fhura tamtam vuav, won harar suirav tuavar wo kh…®v…®rga guma ga nzuav nzuai.
\v 12 Erimas maaŇč muuŇčgim, mben Ňčgu gari guman panan vhari, ana gangiap, guigira Guma Bak…®me khoth…®gi. Ana Guma Bak…®me khoth…®gap, ana mbe Guma Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuaim, ana nta nzuav Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi.
\s1 Barnabas gum Sor Antiokan Pisidia fhain Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 13:13 \xt FG 13.5; 15.38\x*Por maaŇč thav khavgiap, wo phorga rui gumgir kov, mbe Pafos Ňčgu bak…®me thav, kema ndigap, Pamfiria fhain Perga Ňčgu bak…®men vui. Mbe Perga Ňčgu bak…®men vegap, Zon Mak maam mbe thav, taagia Zerusareman ndai.
\v 14 Zon Mak mbe thav, Zerusareman ndaim, Por won gumgir kov, mbe Perga thav vov, Pisidia fhain Antiokan Ňčgu bak…®men hegi. Mbe vov Antiokan kim, Sabat raa h…®gim, mbe vov ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phen vhen vergap, wari piigiap ki.
\v 15 \x - \xo 13:15 \xt Ru 4.16; FG 13.27; 15.21; Hi 13.22\x*Mbe piigiap kim, mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararagi phena gari gumgir pani, mbe Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi ki gava mueŇč garav mbe suaŇčgiap, mbaram mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma suaŇčgi buni ki gava mueŇč garav mbe nzuai. Mbe mba buni garav mbe suaŇčgia thugap, mbaram khaŇč mba guma mbe nzuai. Ndu Ňčg…®p, khaŇč Por gum ana phorga Ňčgara rui gumgi ga suaŇčri, ‚ÄúNde nzan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nde maaŇč muuŇčgip kha gumgi gu mbigi ndavi havhar…®rga buna thueŇč k…®v, nde ne suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 13:16 \xt FG 12.17\x*Ana maaŇč Por ga suaŇčgim, Por mbaram khavgia th…®gap, farvera mba gumgi gu mbigir vharkaim, mbe buni suaŇč thav, th…®…®ri p…®ngi. Mbe th…®…®ri p…®ngim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha IsreriŇč gumgi, gu nde kha harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, nde Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vov, ana piin ki, nde na mbarara!
\v 17 \x - \xo 13:17 \xt Kis 1.7; 6.6; 12.5; Lo 7.6-7; Sng 105.23-24\x*Khe Isrerin Fhe Bak…®me, ana nzan nz…®gir wora mbuiav khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi, mbe anan gumgi gu mbigi ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe won nuiana thav vov, Idz…®van kim, ana t…®var vhuun mbe muuŇčgim, mbe guigira tavahorgi. Mbe tavahorgim, ana zumgum won ŇčkasŇčkar mbe ndiga Idz…®p thav z…®gi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 13:18 \xt Kis 16.35; Nam 14.34; Lo 1.31; Sng 95.10; FG 7.36\x*Ana mben kov, mba gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanan kav, ana nduara mben simt…®gi ndiav kim, 40 mpari vh…®zgi. \f c \fr 13:18 \ft Gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen kh…®…®nan kav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen kh…®…®nan kim, ana tuituigira nza garav kim, 40 mpari vh…®zgi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 13:19 \xt Lo 7.1; Jos 14.1; Sng 78.55\x*‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me mben t…®vi mbat…®gi simt…®gi ndiav, ana vh…®ra Kenanan nuiana s…®gen ana harath…®gi Ňčgui bak…®vir farfagiap, mbaram mba nuiana s…®gen IsreriŇč ga n…®…®Ňčgi. Mba nuiana s…®geŇč Isrerir nuianeŇč k…®rga.
\v 20 \x - \xo 13:20 \xt Het 2.16; 1 Sml 3.20\x*Mba simt…®gi mben hav kim, 450 mpari vh…®zgi. Mbe IsreriŇč zumgum mba nuiana s…®geŇč ndigim, Fhe Bak…®me mbe gan…® zav, mbe nzuav gumgir pani ndi fegim, mbe mbe garav kim, zumgum Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma Samuer h…®gi.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Sml 8.5; 8.19; 10.1; 10.21\x*‚ÄúSamuer h…®gim, mba tugen mbe IsreriŇč, mbe Ňčgui gari guman pana vuzvugi. Mbe ne vuzvugiap, Fhe Bak…®me nzuaim, ana mbaram mbe Ňčgui gari guman pan k…®r zav Sor ndi fagi. Ana mben Ňčgui gari guman pan kav, mbe gari. Sor mben Ňčgui gari guman pan kav kim, 40 mpari vh…®zgi. Sor ana Kisan kam ma, ana Benzaminan sh…®ga mbe ma.
\v 22 \x - \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Sml 13.14; 15.23-26; 16.12-13; 2 Sml 2.4; Sng 89.20; Hos 13.11\x*Ana mbe garav kim, Fhe Bak…®me, ana vharav Devit ndi fagim, ana mben Ňčgui gari guman pan ki. Ana Devit ndi fav, ana bun mbe nzuav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėGu Zesin kama Devit gangiap, na ndava vhee gu guigira ana vuzvugi. Ana na vuzvugi, ana nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga.‚Äô
\v 23 \x - \xo 13:23 \xt 2 Sml 7.12-16; Sng 132.11; Ais 11.1; Ru 1.32; 1.69; Ro 11.26\x*Fhe Bak…®me fhum khaŇč suaŇčgi. Gu taagip kha Isrerin nuiana ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir saŇčv farasarav sararga guma, ana Devitan nz…®ga the k…®rga. Mba guma z…® khare, Zisas.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 13:24 \xt Mt 3.1-2; Mk 1.4; Ru 3.3; Ro 11.26\x*‚ÄúZisas zumgum z…®rga, Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma ana fhara zav khaŇč IsreriŇč ga nzuai, mbe za ndavi domdor…®v ruagiri.
\v 25 \x - \xo 13:25 \xt Mt 3.11; Mk 1.7; Ru 3.16; Zo 1.20-27\x*Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma z…®gap, won Ňčaara mbuav kav, ana won Ňčaara vh…®z…® zav khaŇč nzambaren mbe muuŇčgi. ‚ÄėNde nd…®knd…®gi gu the? Gu mba z…®r zav nzuaim, nde rarga ki guma fhuvara. Nde mba rarga ki guma, ana na z…®n zi. Mba guma, gu ana Ňčkari sharive mpiiŇč fh…®rgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 13:26 \xt Mt 10.6; Ru 24.47; FG 13.16; 13.46\x*‚ÄúNde nan gumgi gu mbigi, nde Abrahaman tari gum nde mba harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, nde Fhe Bak…®men piin ki, nde na mbarara. Mba Fhe Bak…®me taagip kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarav maan zav nzuai guman kameŇč, ana nzara nzuav ana ndi mbai.
\v 27 \x - \xo 13:27 \xt Ru 23.34; 24.20; 24.44; Zo 16.3; FG 3.17; 15.21; 1 Ko 2.8\x*Mba Zerusareman ki gumgi gu mben gumgir ruu, mbe tuituigiap kha guma kaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi suaŇčgi buni, mbe zazera Sabatar nta garav nta nzuaim, mbe tuituigiap nta nd…®knd…®gi fhuvara. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAna rimgirga.‚Äô Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi fhum suaŇčgi kameŇč, ne guigira mba tegi.
\v 28 \x - \xo 13:28 \xt Mt 27.22-23; Mk 15.13-14; Ru 23.21-23; Zo 19.15\x*Mbe ana muuŇčgi big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč ga nzuav ana nzuav, ana shogim, ana rimgi fhuvara. Mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari Pairat ga nzuai, ‚ÄėAna rimgirga.‚Äô
\v 29 \x - \xo 13:29 \xt Mt 27.57-61; Mk 15.42-47; Ru 18.31; 23.50-56; Zo 19.28-30; 19.36-42\x*Mbe mba fhum Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi, mba gumgi mba t…®var ana muunga, ne suaŇčgi. Mbe za mba t…®vara ana muuŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, ana rimgim, mbe mbaram vov, khanararain ana khuma daaŇčgiap, ana ndiga vov, mboga t…®gi.
\v 30 \x - \xo 13:30 \xt Mt 28.6; FG 2.24\x*Mbe maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 13:31 \xt FG 1.3; 1.8\x*Mbe rari vh…®rvera maaŇč ana mbuim, mba ana phorgap Garirin kegap, Zerusareman ndagi gumgi, mbe ana gangi. Mbe ana gangiap, mbe ntigem mba bigi bun suanga gumgi kav, mbe mba bigi bun ZudaiŇč ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 13:32 \xt Stt 12.3; Sng 2.7; FG 13.23; Ro 1.4; 4.13; Ga 3.16; Hi 1.5; 5.5\x*‚ÄúNza nde nzuai buni vhuuiŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nza mba Fhe Bak…®me fhum nzan nz…®gi ga suaŇčgi kameŇč, ana khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi ‚ÄėGu guma the sararim, ana z…®v, taagi nde ndirga.‚Äô
\v 33 Ana ne suaŇčgiap, mbaram taagiap Zisas khavgi. Ana taagia Zisas khavgiap, ana mba fhum nzan nz…®gi ga suaŇčgi kameŇč, ana ntigem nza mbe tari ki tugen, ana mba kameŇčra z…®n vugi. Kha bigin kameŇč, ne Ňägavi Ki Gap 2 ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄėNdu nan Kam ma, gu ntigem ndun Ndia ki.‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 34 \x - \xo 13:34 \xt Ais 55.3\x*Ana rimgim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgi. Ana wom rimgip mba mbogar k…®v khurgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana mba Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇčra z…®n vugi. Ana khaŇč nzuai,
\q1 ‚ÄėGu t…®var vhuuŇčra ndun muuŇčv, gu bigir vhuuiŇčra ndun n…®…®nga. Gu mba fhum Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Devit ga suaŇčgi t…®vara muuŇčgirga.‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 35 \x - \xo 13:35 \xt Sng 16.10; FG 2.27; 2.31\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar harigi kama mueŇč vh…®ra ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄėNdu mba won Ňäaara Guma Guar, ndu won Ňčaarar muun zav ana farasarigi, ndu fhura ana gan…®rim, ana rimgip khurgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 13:36 \xt 1 Kin 2.10; FG 2.29\x*‚ÄúNza Devit kaŇčgi, ana kha nuianan kav, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me nzuai Ňčaari, ana nta muuŇčgi. Ana nta mbuav kav, rimgim, mbe ana ndim ana nz…®gi ndi mbogi ga r…®gi Ňčanen ana ndi mbok ga t…®gim, ana khurigi.
\v 37 Devit rimgiap, mba t…®va muuŇčgi. Kha Fhe Bak…®me taagia khavgi guma, ana rimgiap, khurigi fhuvara.
\v 38 \x - \xo 13:38 \xt Dan 9.24; Ru 24.47; FG 10.43; 1 Zo 2.12\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde nzan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nza khaŇč muuŇčgia t…®gap kha bunin nde nzuai. Nde kha guma Zisas kaŇčgiri, ana nde fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®z…® zav zergi.
\v 39 \x - \xo 13:39 \xt Ais 53.11; Ro 3.28; 8.3; 10.4; Hi 7.19\x*Nde mba Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, nde fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgip, khaŇč nde suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇč ga mbui gumgi ma. Fhuvara. Nde kha guma Zisas, nde ana khothivi gumgi, ana za nde fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana za nta vh…®zgip, ana kha z…®n nden kam…®nga, nde t…®vir vhuuiŇč ga mbui gumgi ma.
\v 40 \x - \xo 13:40 \xt Ais 29.14\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde warir r…®v…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®rim, mba Fhe Bak…®me kaathoori gumgi, mbe fhum suaŇčgi bigeŇč nden h…®g…®rga. Mbe fhum khaŇč suaŇčgi.
\b
\q1 
\v 41 \x - \xo 13:41 \xt Hab 1.5\x*‚ÄėNde ntige khar kav Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi buni nz…®…®i gumgi, nde warir r…®v…®ri. Nde muuŇčv k…®v Ňčgava mbat…®gar muuŇčgip, wari mbat…®girga. Nde Ňčamra k…®rim, gu nde r…®gar harigi khesharigi bigen muuŇčgirga. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the gu muunga bigeŇč bun nde suaŇčgirga, nde ne khoth…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\b
\p 
\v 42 Por mba buni suaŇčgiap, mani Barnabas gum k…®rar h…®r zav mbuim, mba gumgi gu mbigi khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko ntigem kha Ňčaaren Sabatar, Ňčko taagip z…®v, kha nza suaŇčgi buni thari phorg…®p nza suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\v 43 \x - \xo 13:43 \xt FG 11.23; 14.22; Ta 2.11; Hi 12.15; 1 Pi 5.12\x*Mbe maaŇč mani ga suaŇčgim, mani mba Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena thav, k…®rar h…®gap, wani vui. Mani vuim, ZudaiŇč vh…®rve, gum harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe mbe phorgap Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui t…®va z…®n vui, mbe Por gum Barnabas z…®n vui. Mbe mani z…®n vuim, mani mbe nzuav, wom mbe nd…®knd…®gi khavav, khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip Fhe Bak…®me vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®p, ana vh…®ra mbe kora muuŇčgi ne nd…®knd…®k suira havhargirga nen mbe nzuai.
\p 
\v 44 Por gum Barnabas maaŇč mbuav kav, zumgum harigi Sabatar mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe s…®ga mbige zam, zav phoga vhuigap, Por gum Barnabas Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč nzuaim, mbe nta mbararagi.
\v 45 \x - \xo 13:45 \xt FG 14.2; 18.6; 1 Pi 4.4; Zu 1.10\x*Mba gumgi vh…®rve za phoga vhuigap, mani nzuai buni mbararagim, mba ZudaiŇč mba t…®va gangiap, mbe guigira ndavi mbat…®gi. Mbe ndavi mbat…®giap, mbe mbaram Por nzuai buni mbevav guigira ana nz…®…®i.
\v 46 \x - \xo 13:46 \xt Ais 55.5; Ru 7.30; FG 3.26; 18.6; Ro 1.16; 10.19\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Por gum Barnabas khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäka guigira fharav nde ZudaiŇč Ňčka Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuin nde suanga. Nde khaŇč mbui, nde Ňčka khar nzuai buni, nde k…®r nta si. Nde k…®r nta segap, nde nduarira khaŇč warira nzuai, ‚ÄėNza mba zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô Nde nduarira maaŇč nzuaim, nde mbarara. Ňäka ntigem, wom kha bunin nde suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ňäka kha bunin harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri ga suanga.
\v 47 \x - \xo 13:47 \xt Ais 42.6; 49.6; Ru 2.32\x*Ňäka kha bunin harigi nt…®…®ri ga suanga, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč nza suaŇčgi. ‚ÄėGu ndu ndi fagim, ndu za kha harigi Ňčguive ga sh…®g…®p, tuavar mbe kh…®v…®rga vhava Ňčaar ma. Ndu za kha nuianan kha Ňčguiver ki gumgi gu mbigir kurkurarim, gu taagi mbe ndirga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 48 \x - \xo 13:48 \xt FG 11.18\x*Mani maaŇč nzuaim, mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi ne mbararagiap, mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me buni guigira vhergi.‚ÄĚ Mbe guigira Guma Bak…®me bunin ndikndigi. Mbe ndikndigim, Fhe Bak…®me zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndir za farasarigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za Zisas bun nzuai buna vhuueŇč khoth…®gi.
\v 49 Mbe ana khothivim, mba Guma Bak…®me bunin vhuuin kameŇč za mba fhaiŇč ga ruigi.
\v 50 \x - \xo 13:50 \xt FG 17.4; 17.12\x*Mba kameŇč za mba fhaiŇč ga ruigim, mba ZudaiŇč thav, khavgiap, mba z…® kav mben t…®va z…®n vov, mbe phorga rotu mbui mbigi, mbe mben ndavi khavi. Mbe mben ndavi khavav, vh…®ra mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgir pani, mbe vh…®ra mben ndavi khavi. Mbe mben ndavi khavim, mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe hegap, t…®va mbat…®gar Por gum Barnabas ga mbui. Mbe t…®va mbat…®gar mani ga mbuav, mba fhaiŇč thav Ňčg…®r zav mani ga vharigi.
\v 51 \x - \xo 13:51 \xt Mt 10.14; Mk 6.11; Ru 9.5; 10.11; FG 18.6\x*Mbe mani ga vharigim, mani Ňčg…®r zav wani wo Ňčkarvenin ki vher…®na p…®zi. Mani maaŇč muunga, mba gumgi gu mbigi mba t…®va gangip kaŇčgira, nza kha gumani ga muuŇčgi bigeŇč ga suaŇč kameŇč k…®rga. Mani maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbaram maam Antiok thav khavgia vov, Aikoniaman vugi.
\v 52 \x - \xo 13:52 \xt Mt 5.12; Zo 16.22; FG 2.46\x*Mani vuim, mba Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira mbe rugap kim, mbe guigira ndikndigi.
\c 14
\s1 Barnabas gum Por Aikoniaman Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Por gum Barnabas Aikoniaman, mani Antiokan kav muuŇčgi t…®vara mbui. Mani vov, mbe ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen verav Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuin mbe nzuai. Mani guigira Fhe Bak…®men bunin vhuuiŇč, mani suambara vhuuŇčra ntan mbe mbuim, ZudaiŇč vh…®rvera gum GrikiŇč vh…®rvera, mbe mani nzuai buni khoth…®gi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 14:2 \xt FG 13.45\x*Mbe mani buni khoth…®gim, mba ZudaiŇč mbari, mbe mani buni khoth…®gi fhu. Mbe khavgiap, mbaram mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi mbari ndavi ga sim, mbe mbaram mba mani khothivi gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav ndavi mbat…®gi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 14:3 \xt Mk 16.20; FG 19.11; Hi 2.4\x*Por gum Barnabas tuga mpeeŇčra Aikoniaman kegi. Mani kav, mani Guma Bak…®men kora muumbara bun mbe nzuai, mani r…®vi fhuvara. Mani maaŇč mbuim, Guma Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčkar mani ga nd…®…®im, mani mbark…®rga mirikori ga mbui. Mani maaŇč mbuim, Guma Bak…®me mba t…®vir mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vi. Mbe mba t…®vi gan…®v, kaŇčgirga, mani mba nzuai buni, nta guigi guarara.
\v 4 Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®vir mbe kh…®vim, mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe r…®g…®ra wari sh…®rigi. Mbe mbari, mbe Zudain ndagi. Mbe mbari, mbe mba Zisas farsarigi Ňčaara gumanin ndagi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 14:5 \xt FG 14.19; 2 T 3.11\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, zumgum ZudaiŇč gumgi gum mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi. Mbe hegap, wari won gumgir panin kov, mbe t…®va mbat…®gar Por gum Barnabasan muun za mbui. Mbe vh…®ra Ňčk…®…®ar mani ga seg…®rim, mani rimgir za mbui.
\s1 Barnabas gum Sor Rikonian Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 14:6 \xt Mt 10.23\x*Barnabas gum Por mba gumgi maaŇč manin muun za mbui bigeŇč mbararagiap, mbaram wani ra vov, Rikonia fhain Ristra gu Derbe Ňčgu bak…® nin vov, mba mani gaar ki Ňčgui, mani za nta rui.
\v 7 Mani nta ruav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 14:8 \xt Zo 9.1; FG 3.2\x*Mani nta rua vov, Ristra Ňčgu bak…®men vugi. Mba Ňčgun, guma mbevi ki. Mba guma, ana won niamuuŇč ndava vheera kim, anan Ňčkarveni rimgim, ana niamuuŇč ana ruagi. Mba guma ana rui fhu. Ana mbara muuŇčgiap peravra ki.
\v 9 \x - \xo 14:9 \xt Mt 8.10; 9.28-29; FG 3.4\x*Mba guma perav kav, Por nzuai buni mbararagi. Por mbaram kh…®rav, ana garav, ana ana kaŇčgi. Mba guma ana nzuai buni, ana nta khoth…®gi, ana taagiap nzerarga.
\v 10 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Por kama havharav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khavgip th…®g…®‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč ana nzuavra thagim, mba guma za fega mbarav, khavgia thiva rui.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 14:11 \xt FG 8.10; 28.6\x*Ana khavgia thiva ruim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve mba Por muuŇčgi bigeŇč gangiap, mbe Rikonian kaman kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha mbar…®vi, nta gumgi ga gegap, nzan han zergi.‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgiap, kha z…®n Barnabas ga n…®…®Ňčgi, nzan mbar…®v Zus. Mbe mba z…®n ana n…®…®Ňčgiap, mbaram Por buni nzuaine nzuav, mbe kha z…®n Por ga n…®…®Ňčgi, nzan mbar…®v Hermes. \f a \fr 14:12 \ft Grikin gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe khueŇč khoth…®gi, mbar…®vi vh…®rve ki. Zus, ana za mben mbar…®vi gari mbar…®v ma. Hermes, ana mben buni ndia rui Ňčaara mbui mbar…®v ma. \f*
\p 
\v 13 Mben mbar…®va Zus rotu mbui phen, ana mba Ňčgu bak…®me behuigi b…®na gaar k…®rar ki. Mbe mba z…®nin Barnabas gum Por ga n…®…®Ňčgiap, mbaram mba mben mbar…®var Zus rotu gari guma, ana borombaga puri mbari ndigap, mbaram mbark…®rga k…®m…®ri shivi vhuuiŇč mbari b…®zgiap, nta ndigap, mba Ňčgu bak…®men vhen veri b…®na th…®mkamanin zeri. Ana gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rver kov Barnabas gu Por ga nzuav shaman muun zav zi.
\p 
\v 14 Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba Zisas farasarigi Ňčaara gumani mba kameŇč mbararagiap, mani guigira mba kameŇč ga nzuav Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, mbaram wani wo shagi suigav, nta karasuegi. Mani wani wo shagi karasuegap, khuaf…®rav vov, mba gumgi gu mbigi r…®gar vergap, nz…®…®v, khaŇč nzuai,
\v 15 \x - \xo 14:15 \xt Kis 20.11; 2 Sml 12.21; Sng 33.6; 146.6; FG 10.26; 1 Ko 8.4; 1 Te 1.9; Ze 5.17\x*‚ÄúNde Ňčkan k…®vntogi, nde thaŇč nzuav mba t…®va mbui? Ňäka guma kh…®nani ma. Ňäka ndera fara muuŇčgi. Ňäka kha Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nde nzuai ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Ňčka kha buni vhuuiŇč bun nde suaŇčrim, nde mba fhura sh…®sh…®gap rotu mbui bigi, nde nta thav k…®r nta seg…®p, nde guigira zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Fhe Bak…®me han z…®rga. Mba Fhe Bak…®me, ana kha buip gum nuiana mbuav mbas…®ga mbuav, ana ki bigi, ana za nta muuŇčgi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 14:16 \xt Sng 81.12; FG 17.30; 1 Pi 4.3\x*Ana fhum nzan nz…®gi ki tugen, ana za fhura kha gumgi gu mbigi garim, mbe won vuzvugi z…®n vegi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 14:17 \xt Sng 147.8; Jer 5.24; 14.22; FG 17.27; Ro 1.20\x*Ana vh…®ra ana mba tugen, ana za wo ndi zorgim, gumgi gu mbigi ana kakagi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana zazera t…®var vhuuŇčra nde mbui. Ana nde nzuav mboga mbuim, ana buivar kega zeri. Ana nde nzuav mban vhuuiŇč vh…®rve ga muuŇčgim, nta hegi. Ana mban vh…®rvera nde n…®…®Ňčgim, nde ndavi mb…®rav, ndikndigap, wari ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Mani mba kameŇčra mbe suaŇčgia thav, mani khaŇč t…®gap Ňčaara bak…®mera mbuav mba gumgi gu mbigi th…®vav mbe nzuai. Mbe mani ga suaŇčv shaman muunga fhuvara.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 14:19 \xt FG 13.45; 17.13; 2 Ko 11.25; 2 T 3.11\x*Mbe maaŇč manin muun za muuŇčgiap kim, zumgum ZudaiŇč mbari Antiokan kegap ndaim, mbe mbari Aikoniaman kegap, ndav, Ristran ndav, mba gumgi gu mbigi ndavi ga sav mbe nzuaim, mba gumgi gu mbigi mbe panan Por ga kegi. Mbe panan Por ga kegap, mbaram Ňčk…®…®ar ana segi. Mbe Ňčk…®…®ar ana segim, ana Ňčama rimgim, mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ana zama rimgi. Mbe ne suaŇčgiap, ana khuma Ňčg…®rga vov mba Ňčgu bak…®me thav, ana ndiga vov, mba Ňčgu bak…®men b…®na k…®ra hiiŇč kh…®ngi.
\v 20 Mbe ana Ňčg…®rga vov kh…®ngim, mba Zisas buni vhuuiŇč khothivi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za zav, ana forgia thivgim, Por wom khavgi. Por khavgiap wom mba Ňčgu bak…®me vhen vergi. Ana taagia mba Ňčgu bak…®me vhen vergap, ana m…®timanera, ana Barnabas phorgap, mani khavgiap, Derbe Ňčgu bak…®men vugi.
\s1 Barnabas gum Por Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ndavi khavav, mbe ndavi havhari bunin mbe nzuai.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Mt 28.19\x*Barnabas gum Por vov, Derbe Ňčgu bak…®men vugap, maam Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav, mani gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera ndigim, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Mani maam mbe ndigim, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vuim, mani zumgum taagia vov, Ristra gum Aikoniam gum Antiok, mani ntan vergi.
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt Mt 7.14; FG 11.23; 15.32; 18.23; 1 Te 3.3\x*Mani vergap, mani mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mani maam mbe ndavi khavav, mbe ndavi havhari buni mbe nzuai. Mani mbe nzuav kama havharar khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui t…®v, nde guigira ana suirav, havhargiri. Nza Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga Ňčgun Ňčgir…® saŇčv, nza fharav simt…®gi vh…®rve ki tuav, nza ana Ňčg…®g…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 \x - \xo 14:23 \xt FG 13.1-3; 15.40\x*Mani maaŇč mbe suaŇčgia thugap, mbaram mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba Ňčgu phuni khegenen ki, mani mbe gan…®nga gumgir pani ndi fi. Mani mben gumgi pani ndi fegap, mbaram mbe nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suan zav mba thagi. Mani mba thav, mbaram Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Mani mba t…®var muuŇčv, mba Guma Bak…®me khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mani mbe ndim, Guma Bak…®me farve kh…®ngirga.
\s1 Barnabas gum Por taagia Antiokan Siria Ňčgu bak…®me fhain vugi.
\p 
\v 24 Barnabas gum Por maaŇč mbe muuŇčgiap, mbaram zumgum khavgiap, wani vov, Pisidia fhaiŇč sh…®rav vov, Pamfiria fhain h…®gi.
\v 25 Mani Pamfirian h…®ga vov, Perga Ňčgu bak…®men Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Mani maam Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčgiap, zumgum vera vov, Atarian vergi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 14:26 \xt FG 13.1-3; 15.40\x*Mani Atarian vergap, maam kema ndigap, vov Antiokan vugi. Mba Antiokan kav Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mbe fhum, Por gum Barnabas ndim Fhe Bak…®me farve ga suav ana phorga nzuav khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúO, Fhe Bak…®me, ndu kha gumani korar muuŇčgirim, mani kha Ňčaarar muunga.‚ÄĚ Mbe mani ga nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgim, mani vov, mba Ňčaara muuŇčgiap, mani ntige taagia vov, mba Antiokan vugi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 14:27 \xt FG 11.18; 15.4; 15.12\x*Mani vov mba Antiokan vugap, mani mbaram mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir kamgim, mbe zav wari fugi. Mbe za zav wari fugim, mani mbaram, za mba Fhe Bak…®me manin kurigim, mani ana ŇčkasŇčka panan muuŇčgi bigi, mani za ntan mbe neŇčgegi. Mani mba bigi neŇčga vov, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me vh…®ra harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, ana khoth…®g…®rga tuav, ana vh…®ra ana fh…®rgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Mani mba bigir mbe neŇčgegap, mani rari vh…®rvera mba Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mani mbe phorga kegi.
\c 15
\s1 Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi Zerusareman phok bak…®men ki.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt Wkp 12.3; Zo 7.22; Ga 2.12; 5.2; Kor 2.8; 2.11; 2.16\x*Por gum Barnabas Antiokra ki. Mani Antiokra kim, gumgi mbari, mbe Zudian kegap, Antiokan zergi. Mbe zergap, mba Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi ma, mbe ZudaiŇč fhuvara. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe nzuav, mbe kh…®vav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Moses suaŇčgi t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®v warir fooŇč tharga, Fhe Bak…®me taagip nde ndigirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt FG 11.30; Ga 2.1\x*Mbe vergap, mba suambarar mbe mbuim, Por gum Barnabas ne mbararagiap, mbaram ne nzuav mba Zudian kega zergi gumgi phorga nzuav, mbe daai. Mani ne nzuav mbe daav, mbe phorgap khaŇč t…®gap kama shogi. Mbe kama shogiap mbaram, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Por gum Barnabas farasarav, mbaram mba harigi gumgi mbari phorga farasegi. Mba gumgi, mbe Zerusareman naaŇčv, mba Zisas farasarigi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gum mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani phorg…®p mba kameŇč ndiv th…®gar maanga.
\p 
\v 3 Mbe Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbe sarigim, mbe nda vov, Fonisia gum Samaria k…®t…®gen daav, mani k…®t…®gar maam Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu, mbigi, mbe kha kamen bun mbe nzuav ndai. Mbe khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, ndavi dorgim, mbe ana z…®n vui.‚ÄĚ Mbe ne bun nzuaim, mba maaŇč kav Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mbe ne mbararagiap, mben ndavi guigira mben vhergi.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 15:4 \xt FG 14.27\x*Mbe nda vov, Zerusareman hegim, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir gumgir pani, Zisas mba farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe mbe gangiap, mben ndikndigi. Mbe mben ndikndigim, Por gu Barnabas mbaram mba Fhe Bak…®me manin kurkurigim, mani ana ŇčkasŇčkar panan muuŇčgi bigi, mani nta bun mbe nzuai.
\v 5 Mani mba buni bun mbe nzuaim, mba Fherasi mbari, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Mbe hegap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, mbe nza ZudaiŇč, mbe nza phorg…®p, nza Fhe Bak…®me z…®n Ňčg…®r za mbui. Mbe vh…®ra mba Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®p, mbe vh…®ra warir fooŇčgiri.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 15:5 \ft Ndu Firipai 3.2 gan…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 6 Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Zisas mba farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gum, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mben gumgir pani, mbe wari fugap mba suaŇčgi kameŇč ndim th…®gar mbai.
\v 7 \x - \xo 15:7 \xt FG 10.1-43\x*Mbe mbe phorgap buni vh…®rvera ndi th…®gar mbarigim, Pita mbaram khavgia th…®gap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nza phorg…®p Zisas z…®n vui gumgi, nde khueŇč kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me fhum nza kha Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, Fhe Bak…®me mba Ňčaarar nzan farve kh…®ngi. Ana mba Ňčaarar nzan farve kh…®ngiap, ana khueŇč nzuav na farasarigi. Gu ana buni vhuuiŇč bun harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčrim, mbe ana buni vhuuiŇč mbararav mbe ana khothiv…®rga.
\v 8 \x - \xo 15:8 \xt 1 Sto 28.9; FG 1.24; 2.4; 10.44; 11.15\x*Nde khueŇč kaŇčgiri, Fhe Bak…®me ana za kha gumgi gu mbigi ndavi vheri kaŇčgiap, ana won Ňäina Ňäaarar mbe nd…®…®i. Ana won Ňäina Ňäaarar nza n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vara muuŇčgiap, ana mbe n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana khuen nza kh…®vav mba t…®var mbe muuŇčgi. Ana ndava vhee mbe ndirgeŇč nzuav ndikndigi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 15:9 \xt FG 10.15; 10.28; 10.34-35; Ro 10.11; 1 Ko 1.2; 1 Pi 1.22\x*Ana vh…®ra, ana t…®va then nza mbuav, ana harigi t…®var mbe mbui fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe ana khoth…®gim, mba tuavra ana mbe muuŇčgim, mbe ana n…®man Ňčgarigi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 15:10 \xt Mt 11.30; 23.4; Ru 11.46; Ga 3.10; 5.1\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde ntige thaŇč nzuav Fhe Bak…®men mpari? Nde mba simt…®gir Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgir ph…®g…®r naaŇč thari. Fhum nzan nz…®gi gum nza ntige vh…®ra, nza mba simt…®gi ndigirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 11 \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Ro 3.24; Ga 2.16; Ef 2.5-8; Ta 2.11\x*Nza khueŇč khoth…®gi, Guma Bak…®me Zisas nzan kora muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me fhura nza ndigi. Ana mba t…®vara muuŇčgiap, ana vh…®ra mba harigir Ňčgui gumgi ndigi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 15:12 \xt FG 14.27\x*Pita mba buni suaŇčgim, mba phogar kav buni nzuai gumgi, mbe buna thueŇč suaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe fhura Barnabas gu Por buni khuara t…®gi. Mbe mani khuara t…®gim, mani mbaram Fhe Bak…®me manin kurkurav, won ŇčkasŇčkar mani ga nd…®…®im, mani anan ŇčkasŇčkar panan, mba harigi Ňčguir han kav, mbark…®rga mirikori mani nta muuŇčgi. Mani mba bigir mbe neŇčgi.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 15:13 \xt FG 12.17; Ga 2.9\x*Mani mba bigir mbe neŇčgega thugim, Zems mbaram khavgiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nza phorgap Zisas z…®n vui gumgi, nde na mbarara.
\v 14 \x - \xo 15:14 \xt FG 15.7-9\x*Saimon Pita ntigera Fhe Bak…®me mbu harigi fhaiŇč gumgi gu mbigi kora muuŇčgiap, ana mbe mbari ndigap, mben wora mbuigi, ne suaŇčgi.
\v 15 Ana mba nde suaŇčgi kameŇč, mba Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi, mbe fhum mba kameŇčra suaŇčgi. Mbe mba kameŇčra suaŇčgim, mbe ne khergim, ne ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai,
\v 16 \x - \xo 15:16 \xt Amo 9.11-12\x*‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba Devitan nz…®gi gum, tori, ana Ňčkaa, mbe mba sher phen ph…®reregi fara muuŇčgiap ki. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap ki. Gu zumgum taagi z…®rga, gu taagi ana muuŇčgirim, ana khavgi th…®g…®rga. Mba phena bigi vurgia mbat…®gi, gu harigi Ňčkaar muuŇčgip, gu mba phenan muuŇčgirim, ana taagia khavgi th…®g…®rga.
\v 17-18 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgirga, mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe na suaŇčv gan…®nga. Mbe mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, gu mben wora mbuigi, mbe nan gumgi gu mbigira.‚ÄĚ Khe Guma Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇč ma. Ana fhum guarara kha bigi h…®rgeŇč suaŇčgi.‚Äô
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap, na nd…®knd…®k khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nza fhura mba harigi Ňčgui nt…®…®ri, mbe ndavi domdorgiap, Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui, nza fhura simt…®gar mben n…®…®nga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 20 \x - \xo 15:20 \xt Stt 9.4; Kis 34.15-17; Wkp 17.10-16; 18.6-23; 1 Ko 6.9; 6.18; 8.1; Ga 5.19; Ef 5.3; Kor 3.5; 1 Pi 4.3\x*Nza khaŇč muunga, ne nzerara, nza gava the khergip, mbe ndi maaŇčv khaŇč mbe suanga. ‚ÄėNde guma the mbar…®ven tuma kargip, ana n…®ma t…®g…®rga s…®k, nde ana mb…® thari. Mba t…®v, Fhe Bak…®me ana garim, ana Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzaŇčnzaŇčgi. Nde vh…®ra ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari k…®m…® thari. Nde vh…®ra guma fh…®rar fagim, rimgiap, v…®z…®n korgiap ndavar vergi s…®k, nde ana mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra v…®z…®nan mb…® thari.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 15:21 \xt FG 13.15\x*Nde za khueŇč kaŇčgi. Fhum guarara kegap zav, ntige kha tugen, harigi Ňčgui mben Ňčgui bak…®vir zam gumgi kav, Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, mbe nta bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe vh…®ra Sabat tug…®ra t…®gap, Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phenin ana suaŇčgi t…®vi garav, nta bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai.‚ÄĚ \f b \fr 15:21 \ft Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe IsreriŇč mbe wo nuianara ki fhuvara. Mbe fhum guarara, mbe za tamtam kha nuianan ki Ňčgui bak…®vi, mbe za nta fhain vov, ntan kegi. Mbe ntan kav, mben Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui pheni za mbe mba kegi Ňčgui bak…®vir ki. Ndu Farasegi Gumgi 2.5-11 gan…® Ňčg…®p th…®g…®ri. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba Ňčguir ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi vh…®rvera, mbe nta mbararagi. \f*
\s1 Mbe gava ndim harigi Ňčguir kav Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi ndi mbai.
\p 
\v 22 Mbe mba gava khergiap, mbaram Zisas mba farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gum, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mben gumgi pani, mbe wari fugap, kama shogi. Mbe kama shogiap, mbaram wari won guma phunini farasarigi. Mba gumani z…®ni khare, mbevi Zudas, ana z…® mbe khare, Barsabas, mbevi Sairas. Mani mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari guman panani ma. Mbe mani farasarav, mani ga sarigim, mani Por gum Barnabas phorgap Antiok Ňčgu bak…®men veri.
\p 
\v 23 Mani verim, mbe mba khergi gavar mani farve kh…®ngi, mba gav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza kha Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gum nza khaŇč Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, nza kha gava khergiap nde ndi mbai. Nde nza phorgap Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi, nde mba harigi Ňčgui Antiok Ňčgu bak…®men ki, za mba Siria fhaiŇč gum Sirisia fhain ki. Nza raara vhuun nde nd…®…®i.
\v 24 \x - \xo 15:24 \xt FG 15.1\x*Nza khaŇč muuŇčgiap mbararagi, nzan gumgi mbari khaŇč kegap nden han verav, buni mbarir nde suaŇčgi. Nde mba buni mbararagiap, Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi. Mbe mba bunin nde nzuav, nde nd…®knd…®gi tuara muuŇčgi. Nde khueŇč kaŇčgiri, nza maaŇč nden muun zav mbe sarigim, mbe vergi fhuvara.
\v 25 Nza mba khesharigi bigeŇč mbararagim, ne h…®gim, nza thav wari t…®gap ndava bavira kav, kama shogiap nden khurkhuma phuni farasarav, mani ga sarigim, mani nza guigira vuzvugi fegani Barnabas gum Por, mani mani phorgav mbar vergi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 15:26 \xt FG 13.50; 14.19; 1 Ko 15.30; 2 Ko 11.23; 11.26\x*Nza guigira vuzvugi fegani, Por gu Barnabas, mani guigira rimgirga t…®vara mbui. Mani vh…®ra nen r…®vav nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais z…® bun suangeŇč thamthagi fhuvara.
\v 27 Mani mbar verim, nza Zudas gum Sairas ga sarigim, mani nden han mbar veri. Mani nden han Ňčgir…®v, nde mba nza khergi gava gan…®nga, mani vh…®ra wani wo kamthoonira vh…®ra mba bunin nde suanga.
\v 28 \x - \xo 15:28 \xt Mt 23.4\x*Nza vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nza phorga kim, nza kama shogap, kha kameŇč suaŇčgi. Nza suaŇčgi kameŇč khare. Nza simt…®gar nde phufu thagi. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap khaŇč nde nzuai, ‚ÄėNde kha t…®vira z…®n Ňčg…®ri.‚Äô Mba t…®vi khare.
\v 29 \x - \xo 15:29 \xt Wkp 17.14; FG 15.20; 21.25; VB 2.14; 2.20\x*‚ÄėNde guma the tuma kargip ana n…®man t…®g…®rga s…®k, nde anan mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra v…®z…®nan mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra guma fh…®rar fagim rimgi s…®k, nde vh…®ra ana mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi, gumgi gu mbigi mbe ruarir wari k…®…®v, mba t…®vi ga mbui, nde mba t…®vir muuŇč thari.‚Äô Nde maaŇč muuŇčgip tuituigira wari gan…®v, khaŇč muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi nde ntan muuŇč tharga ne nzerara. Nza nde nzuai bunira khare. Nde nzerara k…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gu mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, mbe za mba bunin mba gava khergia thugap, mbaram mba gumgi ga sarigim, mbe Antiokan veri. Mbe verav, Antiokan h…®gap, mbe mbaram Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi fugap, mba gavar mbe n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 31 Mbe mba gavan mbe n…®…®Ňčgim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba gavar gangiap, mbe mbe th…®g…® havhargirga bunin vhuuin mbe suaŇčgim, mbe mba buni vhuuiŇč gangiap, guigira ndikndigi.
\v 32 \x - \xo 15:32 \xt FG 11.27; 13.1; 14.22\x*Zudas gu Sairas, mani vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumani ma. Mani maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mani guigira bunin vhuuiŇčra mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, mbe ndavi khavav, mben ndavi havhari.
\v 33-34 Mani mba t…®var mbe mbuav, maneŇč tuga mpeeŇčra mbe phorgap Antiokan kegap, mba Antiokan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zumgum mani phorga perav, mbegav Ňčg…®rkama vhuun mani ga mbuav, ndava m…®…®t…®gar mani ga n…®…®Ňčgiap, mani ga sarigim, mani taagiap mba mani ga sarigim, mani zergi gumgi gu mbigir han ndagi. \f c \fr 15:33-34 \ft Farasegi Gumgi 15.33 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 34 th…®g…®ri. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi mbari, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, buni mbari phorga kha vezar ki. Mba buni khaŇč muuŇčgia nzuai, ‚ÄúSairas won nd…®knd…®gar kurav, ana Antiokra ki.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 35 Zudas gum Sairas taagia ndagim, Por gu Barnabas, mani Antiokra ki. Mani Antiokan kav, mani Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi phorga Ňčgarav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbe kh…®vi. Mani Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun harigi gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai.
\s1 Por gum Barnabas wani t…®gap ndava bavira ki fhuvara.
\p 
\v 36 Por gu Barnabas Antiokan kim, rari mbari vh…®zgim, Por khaŇč Barnabas ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäka taagiap mba fhum Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav ruigi Ňčgui bak…®vir Ňčg…®p, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gan…®nga. Ňäka Ňčg…®p mben k…®r…® t…®vi gangip kaŇčgirga, mbe nzerara ki o, fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 37 \x - \xo 15:37 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; Kor 4.10; 2 T 4.11\x*Por maaŇč suaŇčgim, Barnabas mbaram Zon, ana harigi z…® mbe, Mak, ana vh…®ra ana kuv mani wani phorg…® Ňčg…®rgane vuzvugi.
\v 38 \x - \xo 15:38 \xt FG 13.13; Kor 4.10\x*Ana ne vuzvugim, Por thav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNe nzerigi fhuvara. Mba guma, ana fhum Pamfiria fhain Ňčka thav, ana Ňčka phorg…® ruv kha Ňčaarar muuŇč thagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Ňčka ntigem ana kuv Ňčg…®g…®rga fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 39 Mani ne nzuav wani ga vhegap, wani sh…®rigi. Mani wani sh…®rav, Por nduara Ňčgarim, Barnabas nduara Ňčgari. Mani wani sh…®rav, Barnabas Zon Mak ndigap, mani vov kema ndigap, Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rigen vugi.
\v 40 Por mbaram, Sairas ndigap, mani Ňčg…®r za mbuim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®men ndava m…®…®t…®k Ňčko phorg…® k…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 41 Mbe maaŇč mani ga suaŇčgim, mani za mba Siria fhaiŇč gum Sirisia fhaiŇč ga ruav, Por Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ndavi khavav, mbe ndavi havharav, mani rui.
\c 16
\s1 Timoti Por phorga vui.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 16:1 \xt FG 14.6; 2 T 1.5\x*Por maaŇč mbuav vov, Derbe gum Ristran Ňčgunin vugi. Mba Ristra Ňčgu bak…®men Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui guma mbe ki. Mba guma z…®, Timoti. Ana niamuuŇč Zudar mbik ma. Ana niamuuŇč vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui mbik ma. Ana ndia, ana Grik guma ma.
\v 2 \x - \xo 16:2 \xt Fi 2.19-22\x*Mba Ristra gum Aikoniaman Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana t…®vi bun nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúTimoti, ana guman vhuuŇč ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt 1 Ko 9.20; Ga 2.3-5\x*Por mba buni mbararagiap, mbaram ana wo phorg…® Ňčg…®rgen Timoti vuzvugi. Por wo phorg…® Ňčg…®rgen ana vuzvugiap, mbaram h…®gap Timotin fooŇčgi. Por khueŇč nzuav mba t…®var ana muuŇčgi. Ana mba fhain ki ZudaiŇč ga nd…®knd…®gap, mba t…®var Timoti ga muuŇčgi. Mba fhain ki ZudaiŇč, mbe za Timoti kaŇčgi, ana ndia, ana Grik guma ma.
\v 4 \x - \xo 16:4 \xt FG 15.23-29\x*Por maaŇč ana muuŇčgiap, mbe mba Ňčgui bak…®vi ga ruav, Zisas mba farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi gum mbe Zerusareman kav Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, mba fhum Zerusareman kav suaŇčgi buni, mbe mba bunin Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Mbe mbe nzuav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha buni z…®n Ňčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \x - \xo 16:5 \xt FG 2.47\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vov, khaŇč t…®ga havhargi. Mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargim, harigi gumgi gu mbigi, rari tug…®ra t…®gap zav, mben vhen verim, mben vh…®rve guigira vh…®rk…®vgi.
\s1 Por Masedonia guma gangi.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 16:6 \xt FG 18.23\x*Por gum, Sairas, Timoti, mbe Frigia gu Garesia fhainin r…®g…®nera vui. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar Esia fhain Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun suangen mbe th…®vigi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 16:7 \xt 2 T 1.15\x*Mbe vov, Misia fhaiŇčra th…®gap, mbe mbaram Bitinia fhain vhen Ňčgir…® za mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar maaŇč wom mbe th…®vigi.
\v 8 Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbaram Misia fhaiŇč kambarav, vera vov Troas Ňčgu bak…®men vergi.
\v 9 Mbe Troasan vergap, maan Por r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap big…®na mbe gangi. Ana Masedonia guma mbe garim, ana th…®gap anan kaav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu kha mbas…®ge r…®g…®p khuen Masedonian nzan kurari.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 \x - \xo 16:10 \xt 2 Ko 2.13\x*Por maan mba bigeŇč gangiap, nza vhemkora tuav gangiap, Masedonian vegi. Nza khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, Fhe Bak…®me Masedonian wo buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe suan zav nzan kamgi. \f a \fr 16:10 \ft Kha gap, Farasarigi Gumgi, ana Ňčani mbarir kha khesharigi kameŇč ki, ‚ÄúNza ki.‚ÄĚ Gumgi vh…®rve kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Ruk vh…®ra Por phorga tugi mbarir ruigap, ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap khaŇč nzuai. Nza mba tugivigen Ruk vh…®ra Por phorga vov, Firipai th…®gap, Firipain kegi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Por Firipai thav, harigi Ňčguir vugi buni nza nta garav, nza wom nza gari fhu. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza kaŇčgi, Ruk Por phorga vov Firipaira th…®gi. Ndu FG 16.40 gan…®ri. \f*
\s1 Ridia Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vuav, Zisas z…®n pananan ruagi.
\p 
\v 11 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza Troasan kema ndigap, nza za vov Samotres phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorgap, nza m…®timanera mba kem maaŇč kega vov, Neaporis phorgi.
\v 12 Nza vov Neaporis phorgap, nza maam Neaporisan kegap, th…®var vov Firipain vegi. Firipai ana fhum Rom ana ndiga kegi Ňčgu bak…®me ma. Ana mba Masedonia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain fharigi Ňčgu bak…®men ki. Nza vov anan vugap, rari mbarir ana kegi.
\v 13 Nza maaŇč kav, nza Sabatar vov mba, Ňčgu bak…®men b…®na th…®mkamani mbugum k…®rar hegap, wari vov mb…® mben taan vegi. Nza khueŇč nd…®knd…®ga wari vegi, nza Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suanga Ňčana thueŇč ki thi. Nza ne suaŇčgia vov, mba mb…®n taan vegap, nza mbigi mbari garim, mbe phoga vhuigap wari ki. Nza mbe gangiap, nza mben haa piigiap, mbe phorga nzuai.
\v 14 Nza mbe phorga nzuav kim, mbiga mbe, ana z…®, Ridia, ana nza nzuai buni mbararagi. Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui mbik ma. Ana Taiatairan mbik ma. Ana vh…®ra shaar h…®var sh…®gar Ňčgari mbik ma. Mba tugen Fhe Bak…®me ana ndava dorgim, ana khuaran Por nzuai buni ga t…®gi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt FG 16.33; 18.8\x*Ana mba tugen, ana Zisas z…®n panan ruagi. Ana ruaim, ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, mbe zam Zisas z…®n panan ruagi. Ana ruagiap mbaram khaŇč nza nzuai, ‚ÄúNde guigira kha nd…®knd…®gar nan muunga, gu Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui, nde mba nd…®knd…®gar nan muuŇčv, nde z…®v na phenan k…®.‚ÄĚ Ana nen nza nzuav, ana khaŇč t…®gap wo phenan k…®r zav nza nzuaim, nza thav ana kama z…®n vugi.
\s1 Por gu Sairas Firipain b…®neŇč r…®gi. \fig [map]|alt="Map of Namba 2 Taim Pol i go raun na autim gutnius" src="paul2.tif" size="span" copy="The British and Foreign Bible Society" ref="Farasegi Gumgi 16"\fig*
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 16:16 \xt FG 19.24\x*Nza Ridia han ana phenan kav, raa mben Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suan zav ana phorga nzuai Ňčanen vui. Nza vuim, fhura Ňčaara kh…®na mbui mbiga mbe, ana tuavar nzan purigi. Mba mbik, ana Ňčina mbat…®ga mbe ana vhen ki. Mba Ňčina, ana vhen kav, nd…®knd…®gap ana nd…®…®im, ana zumgum h…®rga bigi, ana nta bun nzuai. Mba mbik maaŇč mbuim, ana gari gumgir pani, ana mba mbui Ňčaarar panan Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rvera ndi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 16:17 \xt Mk 1.24; 1.34\x*Mba mbik tuavar nzan purav, mbaram nza z…®n zi. Ana nza z…®n zav, kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumgi, mbe za kha bigi kharav vun guarara ki Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara gumgi ma. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me taagip nde ndirga tuav bun nde nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt Mk 16.17\x*Nza maaŇč kim, mba mbik rari vh…®rvera, ana mba t…®var nza mbui. Ana mba t…®var mbe mbuav kim, Por guigira ana mbararargen vhugi. Por vhuga thav, dorga th…®gap, khaŇč mba Ňčina mbat…®ga nzuai ‚ÄúGu Zisas Krais z…®n panan ndu nzuai, ndu mba mbiga thav k…®rar h…®g…®p Ňčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ Por ne nzuavra thagim, mba Ňčina mbat…®k vhemkora mba mbiga thav k…®rar h…®gap vugi.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt FG 19.25-26; 2 Ko 6.5\x*Mba Ňčina mbat…®k mba mbiga thav k…®rar h…®gap vugim, mba mbiga gari gumgir pani gari, mbe wom Ňčk…®…®a ndirga tuav ki fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap gangia thav, Por gum Sairas suirav, mani Ňčg…®rga vov, mbe phogi ga vhui Ňčanen wari won gumgir pani han vugi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt 1 Kin 18.17; Mt 5.11; Mk 13.9; FG 17.6\x*Mbe maam mani ndigav, vov bigi ndiv th…®gar mbai gumgir pani han vugap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumani, mani Zuda gumani ma. Mani zav, nza Ňčgu bak…®men z…®gap, simt…®ga bak…®me khavgi.
\v 21 Mani vh…®ra nza RomiŇč muuŇč thagi t…®vi mbari, maam mba t…®vir muun zav, nzan gumgi gu mbigi mbari ga nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 \x - \xo 16:22 \xt 2 Ko 6.5; 11.23-25; Fi 1.30; 1 Te 2.2\x*Mbe mani ga nzuav nzuaim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra zav maam wari fugap, mbe vh…®ra fhura mani ga sh…®sh…®gap, bunin mani ga sav, mani ga nzuai. Mbe mba bunin mani ga sav mani ga nzuaim, mba mben bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgi mbaram, mani shagi zorgiap, gumgi mbari ga nzuaim, mbe zav mpiiŇčs…®gar mani khari.
\v 23 Mbe khara mbat…®gar mani ga muuŇčgim, mben bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgi, mani ndi phena t…®vaneŇč ga sur zav, mbaram kama havharar mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®va nd…®…®v, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu zaaŇčtuigira kha gumani gan…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 24 Mba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgi kama havharen mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®va suaŇčgim, mba g…®mat…®v mbaram Por gu Sairas ndim, mba phena t…®vanen vhee guarara ki ŇčaneŇč kh…®ngi. Ana mani ndi kh…®ngiap, mani suani ndim, khanararaŇč bak…®me mueŇč thooŇč kh…®ngim, mani suani nderigi.
\p 
\v 25 Mbe Por gu Sairas ndim, phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngim, mani maaŇč r…®gar Ňčgavi ga mbuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ki. Mani maaŇč mbuim, mani phorgav phena t…®vanen ki gumgi, mbe kav mani mbararagi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 16:26 \xt FG 4.31; 5.19; 12.7; 12.10\x*Mbe mani mbarararv kim, kh…®mkh…®ga bak…®me fhura k…®g…®ra mbarav mba phena t…®vaneŇč suirav ne n…®…®Ňčkuim, mba phena t…®vanen th…®…®r kaa fhura fh…®reregim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč ki gumgi, mben hari gum suira kegi sheni, nta fhura fh…®reregi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 16:27 \xt FG 12.18-19\x*Mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®v, mba th…®…® garim, nta fh…®reregim, ana kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, kha phena t…®vanen ki gumgi, mbe zama regi thi? Ana mba nd…®knd…®ga muuŇčgiap thav, won ntari ga mbui kos sigap nduara wora shogi r…®m…®n za mbui.
\v 28 Ana maaŇč muun za mbuim, Por ana gangiap, kama bak…®mera ana kaav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAi, ndu nduara won farfa thari. Nza za khar ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 29 Por ne nzuaim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®v ne mbararagiap, thav mbaram vhava nzuav mba gumgir kaai. Ana mben kaaim, mbe vhava ndiga zim, ana mbaram mba vhava ndigap, ana Ňčaarar khuaf…® mba phena t…®vanen Por gum Sairas ki Ňčanen veri. Ana verav, ana guigira rivgiap, nin…®k ana mbuim, ana vera vov, fhura wo fega Por gum Sairas Ňčkarveni n…®man kh…®ngi. \fig Mbe Por gu Sairas ndim, phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngim, mani maaŇč r…®gar Ňčgavi ga mbuav, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav ki. (16.25) |src="LB00337C.tif" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="16.25"\fig*
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 16:30 \xt Ru 3.10; FG 2.37; 9.6\x*Ana mani n…®ma r…®ga kegap, mbaram zumgum khavgiap, Por gum Sairas kov k…®rar h…®gap, manin nzav khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma rumani, gu ram muuŇčgi t…®var muuŇčgirim, Fhe Bak…®me taagi na ndigirie?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 16:31 \xt Zo 3.16; 3.36; 6.47; 1 Zo 5.10\x*Ana mba nzambaren mani ga muuŇčgim, mani ana Ňčgarkarav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Guma Bak…®me Zisas bun nzuai buna vhuueŇč khoth…®g…®p, ana z…®n Ňčg…®rga, Fhe Bak…®me taagip ndu ndiv, ana maaŇč muuŇčgip, ana za ndu phenan ki nt…®…®ri, ana vh…®ra mbe ndig…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Por gum Sairas maaŇč ana suaŇčgia thugap, mbaram za Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun ana nzuav, ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, mani vh…®ra mbe nzuai.
\v 33 \x - \xo 16:33 \xt FG 16.15\x*Mani Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuin ana suaŇčgim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®v mba maaŇčra maan r…®gar mani ndiga vov, mani nzuu ruagi. Ana mani nzuu ruagim, mani mba maaŇčra Zisas z…®n pan ana ruav, vh…®ra ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, mani vh…®ra mbe ruagi.
\v 34 Mani mbe ruagim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®v mba maaŇčra manin kov, wo phenan vugap, mba pav, manin kua pi. Ana mba pav manin kua pav, ana phenan ki nt…®…®ri, mbe khueŇč nzuav guigira ndikndiga mbat…®ga mbui, nza ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi.
\p 
\v 35 Mba maan kegap m…®n thugim, m…®timanera, mba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani, mbaram g…®…®t…®vi gari gumgir pani mbari ga sarigim, mbe zav, khaŇč mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®va nzuai, ‚ÄúMba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani khaŇč ndu nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu mba gumani ndiv k…®rar mbararim, mani Ňčg…®ri.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 36 Mbe maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, mba phena t…®vaneŇč gari g…®mat…®v vov, khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúMba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani khaŇč na nzuai ‚ÄėNdu mba gumani ga sararim, mani k…®rar h…®g…®p Ňčg…®ri.‚Äô MaaŇč muuŇčgim, Ňčko ntige phena t…®vaneŇč thav k…®rar h…®g…®p, wani Ňčg…®p, ndava m…®…®t…®ga ndig…®p, wani k…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 37 Ana maaŇč Por ga nzuaim, Por mbaram khaŇč mba g…®…®t…®va ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäka Rom gumani ma. Ram muuŇčgi ne nzuav, mba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani Ňčka buni mbararargeŇč thagi. Mbe Ňčka buni mbararav, mbe Ňčka kaŇčgirga, Ňčka big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi o, fhu. Mbe vh…®ra fhura kha gumgi gu mbigi n…®man Ňčka shogi. Mbe Ňčka shogiap, vh…®ra Ňčka ndim phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngi. Mbe maaŇč Ňčka muuŇčgiap, mbe ntigem fhura nimnera Ňčka sarari Ňčka Ňčg…®r za mbui thi? Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mbe nduarira z…®p Ňčka suaŇčv, Ňčka kuv k…®rar h…®rga.‚ÄĚ \f b \fr 16:37 \ft Mba tugar, Rom Ňčgu bak…®men ki Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan, ana z…® Sisar, ana za mba Mediterenian mbas…®ga bak…®me fhain ki Ňčgui bak…®vi, ana za nta gari guman pan ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe RomiŇč, mbe z…® bak…®me ki. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mben t…®v khaŇč nzuai, Rom guma the fhura b…®neŇč r…®g…®rga, g…®…®t…®vi farfa mbat…®gar ana muuŇčgirga, tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe RomiŇč vh…®ra, mbe tugi mbarir mbe harigi Ňčgui gumgi gari, mbe vh…®ra Rom gumgi guari fara muuŇčgia ki. Por ndia maaŇč muuŇčgi guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Por niamuuŇč ana tegim, ana Rom fhaiŇč guma ma. Ndu FG 22.24 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 29 th…®g…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 38 Por maaŇč mba g…®…®t…®vi gari gumgir pani ga suaŇčgim, mbe Por suaŇčgi kameŇč ndigap, mba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani han vui.
\v 39 \x - \xo 16:39 \xt Mt 8.34\x*Mba bigi ndi th…®gar mbai gumgir pani ne mbararagia thav, wari vov phena t…®vanen vegap, mbe nduarira Por gum Sairas phorga nzuav, manin kov, k…®rar h…®gi. Mbe manin kov, k…®rar h…®gap, khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko kha Ňčgu bak…®me thav, wani Ňčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 40 Mbe mba phena t…®vaneŇč thav, mani ndim k…®rar mbarigim, mani vov, Ridia phenan vugi. Mani vov, Ridia phenan kav, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mani mbe ndavi khavav, mbe ndavi havhari buni mbarir mbe suaŇčgia thugap, zumgum mba Ňčgu bak…®me thav wani vui.
\c 17
\s1 TesaronaikaiŇč Por gu Sairas shog…®r za mbui.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt 1 Te 1.1-2; 2.1-2\x*Por won khurkhuun kov, mbe Amfipores Ňčgu bak…®men vui. Mbe vov mba Ňčgu bak…®me thav Aporonia Ňčgu bak…®men vui. Mbe vov, mbe vh…®ra mba Aporonia Ňčgu bak…®me thav, mbe Tesaronaika Ňčgu bak…®men vui. Mbe mba Ňčgu bak…®men, mbe ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phenan ki.
\v 2 Mbe vov, mba Ňčgu bak…®men vegap, Por zazera mbui t…®v, ana mba t…®va z…®n vui. Ana Sabat phuni khegenen ana vov, mba ZudaiŇč phorgap Fhe Bak…®me bunin mbararagi phena vhen vergap, ana Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gava garav, Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuiŇč mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuai.
\v 3 \x - \xo 17:3 \xt Ru 24.26; FG 3.18; 9.22; 18.28; Ga 3.1\x*Ana Fhe Bak…®men bunin vhuuin mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuav, ana Fhe Bak…®men bunin vhuuiŇč n…®…®Ňčge bun mbe nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba Fhe Bak…®me taagip wo gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav farasarigi guma, ana fharav zaa ndiv, rimgip, taagip khavgirga.‚ÄĚ Por nen mbe nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu mba Zisasra, gu khar ana buni vhuuiŇč bun nde nzuai. Mba gumara, Fhe Bak…®me taagip wo gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav ana farasarigi.‚ÄĚ
\v 4 \x - \xo 17:4 \xt FG 13.50; 15.22; 15.27; 15.40; 28.24\x*Por Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi mbari mben r…®gar Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gap, mbe Por gu Sairas z…®n vui. Mbe mani z…®n vuim, GrikiŇč mbari, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui. Mbe vh…®rvera khavgiap mani z…®n vui. Mbe mani z…®n vuim, mba z…®ri ki mbigi vh…®rve, mbe vh…®ra mani z…®n vui.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 17:5 \xt Ro 16.21\x*Mbe za mani z…®n vuim, mba ZudaiŇč mbe gangiap, mben ndavi guigira mbat…®gi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap vov, mbe mba phogi ga vhui Ňčanin vov, mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi mbari ndigi. Mbe mbe ndigap, mbaram gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve phorga ndigap, mbe mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi ndavi ga sav, mbe ndavi khavi. Mbe mben ndavi ga sav, mbe ndavi khavim, mbe vov, Zeson phena th…®mkamani thivgi. Mbe Por gum Sairas ga nzuav gari. Mbe mani gangip, mani suirav, mani ndigi Ňčg…®p k…®rar mbu gumgi gu mbigi farve kh…®ngirga.
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt FG 16.20\x*Mbe ne nzuav vov, Zeson phenan Por gu Sairas ndi garavra thav, mbaram hegap, Zesonan suirigi. Mbe Zesonan suirav, mbaram Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi mbari, mbe vh…®ra mben suigiap, mbe ndigap, mba Ňčgu bak…®me gari gumgir pani han vui. Mbe mbe ndiga vov kaav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha nuiana ruav za kha nuianan t…®vi mbat…®gi khavi gumgi, mbe ntige za khaŇč hegi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 17:7 \xt Ru 23.2; Zo 19.12; 1 Pi 2.13\x*Mbe zav khaŇč hegim, Zeson mbe ndiga vov wo phena t…®gim, mbe ana phorga ki. Mba gumgi, mbe Sisar nzuai t…®vi, mbe nta daasui. Mbe nta daasuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėHarigi Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pana mbe ki. Mba guman pana z…® khare, Zisas.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 8 Mbe ne nzuaim, mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mben gumgir pani, mbe ne mbararagiap, mbe guigira Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, mbe za tamtam kaav, nz…®…®va nzuai.
\v 9 Mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe maaŇč mbui, mba Ňčgu bak…®me gari gumgir pani, mbe Zeson, Por gu, Sairas ndi wo phena t…®ga kegi ne nzuav ana nzuav mba ana phorga zegi gumgi, mbe khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúMbe wo muuŇčgi bigeŇč ga vhezgirga, nza mbe fh…®rgirim, mbe Ňčg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por gu Sairas Berian Ňčgari.
\p 
\v 10 Mba Tesaronaikan ki gumgi gu mbigi mba t…®va mbuim, Zisas khoth…®gav ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe maan Por gu Sairas ga sarigim, mani Beria Ňčgu bak…®men veri. Mani vov, Berian h…®gap, vov ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen vergi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 17:11 \xt Ais 34.16; Ru 16.29; Zo 5.39\x*Mba Beria Ňčgu bak…®men ki ZudaiŇč, mbe t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ma. Mben t…®vi guigira mba Tesaronaikan ki ZudaiŇč t…®va kambarigi. Mbe Por nzuai buni mbararagiap, mbe guigira nta vuzvugi. Mbe nta vuzvugiap, mbe rari tug…®ra t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gava garav, Por suaŇčgi buni phorgap nta gari. Mbe khueŇč nzuav nta gari. Por nzuai buni, nta guigira o, fhu.
\v 12 Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe ZudaiŇč gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, ana khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba z…®ri ki GrikiŇč mbigi vh…®rve, mben gumgi vh…®rve, mbe vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 17:13 \xt FG 13.50; 14.19\x*Por Berian kav Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe nzuav kim, mba Tesaronaikan ki ZudaiŇč zumgum mba kameŇč mbararagiap, mbe mbari khavgiap Berian Ňčgu bak…®men vergi. Mbe vergap, maam mba gumgi gu mbigi nd…®knd…®gi tuara mbuim, mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga mbuav, Por gu Sairas ga nzuav ndav sigi.
\v 14 Mba gumgi gu mbigi ndav sigim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vhemkora Por ga sarigim, ana mbas…®k taan vergi. Por vergim, Sairas gu Timoti Beriara ki.
\v 15 Mani kim, mbe Poran kov veri. Mbe ana kov vera vov, Atens Ňčgu bak…®me thivgi. Mbe Atens thivgiap, taagia naan za mbuim, Por mbaram Sairas gu Timoti ga nzuav Ňčk…®…®a mbuav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mani ga suaŇčrim, mani vhemkora nan han zir…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Atensan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 16 Por, Sairas gu Timoti ga nzuav Ňčk…®…®a muuŇčgiap, mani rarga Atensan ki. Ana kav, Atensan Ňčgun garim, mbe nduarira ntuu kargiap nta rotu mbui ntuu vh…®rve ki. Por nta gangiap, ndav guigira mbat…®gi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt FG 18.19\x*Por maaŇč muuŇčgiap thav vov, ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen vergap, ZudaiŇč gu mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbuim, ana Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuai. Ana mbe phorga nzuav, ana vh…®ra rari tug…®rat…®gap mbe phogi ga vhui Ňčanen vov nen ki gumgi gu mbigi, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbe kh…®vav mbe nzuai.
\v 18 Por mbe phorga nzuaim, mba EpikuriaiŇč gum StoikiŇč t…®vi kaŇčgi gumgi, mbe Por kaadogap ana phorga nzuai. Mbe mbari khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKha fhura tamtam buni nzuai guma, ana ram suan za mbui?‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, mbe mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúAria, ana harigi Ňčguir tori buni bun nzuai thi?‚ÄĚ Mbe mba suambarar Por ga mbui, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Por Zisas buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe nzuav, ana vh…®ra ana rimgiap taagia khavgi ne bun mbe nzuai. Ana mba bunin mbe nzuaim, mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mba kamen ana nzuai. \f a \fr 17:18 \ft Fharigi kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGrikiŇč r…®gar gumgi vh…®rve, mbe fhum ZudaiŇč t…®vi kaŇčgi gumgi suaŇčgi t…®vi, mbe nta z…®n vuavra ki. Mba t…®vi z…®n vui nt…®…®ri khare, EpikuriaŇč gum StoikiŇč.‚ÄĚ \f*\f b \fr 17:18 \ft Mba zumgum h…®gi kameŇč khaŇč nzuai. Mbe Grikin kaman mba rimgia mboga t…®gap taagia khavgi ne, mbe kha zit…®r ne ga mbui, Anastasis. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kangiap, nta kheri gumgi mbari, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Por GrikiŇč kaman Zisas bunin vhuuin mbe nzav, kha kameŇč Anastasis zitav mbe suaŇčgim, mbe tuituigiap ne kaŇčgi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe GrikiŇč khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, Por harigi Ňčguir tori zitagi. \f*
\p 
\v 19 Mbe mba kamen Por ga suaŇčgiap, mbaram anan kov, mba Areopagus mb…®ksh…®man phogi ga vhui buaadegi gumgir pani han vugi. Mbe anan kov, mben han vugap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNza ndu kha gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav, mbe nzuai bunin Ňčkaa kaŇčgi za mbui.
\v 20 Nza vh…®ra ndu buni mbararagim, nta guigira harigi khesharigi. Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza ndu nzuai buni n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgi za mbui.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Mba Atensan Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi, mbe zav Atensan ki, mbe harigi bigi ga mbui fhuvara. Mbe zazera harigi buni gu nd…®knd…®gir Ňčkaa, mbe nta mbararganeŇč vuzvugi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe nduarira mba bunin Ňčkaa, mbe nduarira ntan warira phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 22 Mba buaadegi gumgi Por suaŇčgi buni n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgi zav ana nzarigim, Por mbaram mba Areopagus mb…®ksh…®man mba buaadegi gumgir pani n…®man khavgia th…®gap khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha Atensan ki gumgi, gu nde garim, nde guigira havhargiap mbark…®rga t…®vi, nde nta z…®n vov rotu mbui.
\v 23 Gu fharav vov, nde rotu mbui bigi, gu za nta gangi. Gu nta gara vov, gu artar mbe garim, mbe khaŇč muuŇčgi kamen ana khergi. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėKhe nza kaŇčgi fhuv mbar…®vir artar ma.‚Äô Nde mba kaŇčgi fhuv Fhe Bak…®me, nde fhura ana rotu mbui. Gu ntigem mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nde nzuai.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 17:24 \xt Mt 11.25; FG 7.48; 14.15\x*\x - \xo 17:24 \xt 1 Kin 8.27; Ais 42.5\x*‚ÄúMba Fhe Bak…®me, ana kha nuiana muuŇčgiap, ana ki bigi, ana za nta muuŇčgi. Mba Fhe Bak…®mera, ana kha Heven gum nuiana gari Guma Bak…®me ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, gumgi wari won farir muuŇčgi pheni, ana ntan ki fhu.
\v 25 \x - \xo 17:25 \xt Jop 12.10; Sng 50.12; Sek 12.1; FG 7.48\x*Ana vh…®ra big…®n the sosuagiri ma, guma won farver big…®n then muuŇčgip ana kurkurarie? Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana nduara guma ga muuŇčgiap, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ana n…®…®Ňčgiap, ana za bigir kha gumgi gu mbigi ga n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 26 Fhe Bak…®me guma bavira muuŇčgim, ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi ndi t…®gi, mba guma, ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigir nz…®k ma. Ana mba guma ga muuŇčgim, ana kha gumgi ndi t…®gim, mbe za kha nuianan ki. Ana mba guma ga muuŇčgim, ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi ndi t…®gim, mbe k…®v, t…®v hor…®rga tugi gu k…®rga Ňčani mbe n…®…®Ňčgi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 17:27 \xt Lo 32.8; Sng 145.18; Ais 55.6; Jer 23.23; FG 14.17; Ro 1.20\x*Fhe Bak…®me guma ga muuŇčgiap, ana khueŇč vuzvugi, gumgi gu mbigi, mbe taagi ana han z…®v, guigira ana kaŇčgirga, ana ne vuzvugi. Ana ne vuzvugiap, mbe ndi t…®gi, mbe k…®v vh…®ra ana suaŇčv gan…®nga. Ana vh…®ra, ana nza thav saman ki fhuvara.
\v 28 \x - \xo 17:28 \xt Kor 1.17; Ta 1.12; Hi 1.3\x*‚ÄėAna vh…®ra nduara b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n nza nd…®…®im, nza ki. Ana nduara ŇčkasŇčkar nza nd…®…®im, nza rui.‚Äô Kha kameŇč nden t…®vi kaŇčgi gumgi mbari, mbe vh…®ra ne nzuai. Mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNza vh…®ra, ana tari ma.‚Äô \f c \fr 17:28 \ft Ves 18 khaŇč muuŇčgi t…®va muuŇčgi, Por ZudaiŇč t…®vi kaŇčgi gumgi fhum suaŇčgi kamenira, mbe phorga nzuai. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgirga, mbe tuituigip ana nzuai buni kaŇčgirga. \f*
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 17:29 \xt Ais 40.18-20; 44.10-17; FG 19.26\x*‚ÄúNza maaŇč muuŇčgiap Fhe Bak…®men tari ki. Nza thaŇč suaŇčv khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®rie, Fhe Bak…®me, ana gor gum, sirva, k…®m, ana nta fara muuŇčgi? Fhuvara! Nza mba nd…®knd…®gar muunga fhu. Nza vh…®ra kha nd…®knd…®gar muunga fhu. Ana guma nduara won nd…®knd…®k gu farven kargi bigin ma. Nza mba nd…®knd…®gar muunga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 17:30 \xt FG 14.16; Ro 3.25; Ta 2.11-12; 1 Pi 1.14\x*‚ÄúFhum tugen gumgi tuituigia kaŇčgi fhuvara, maaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me, mben tugen ana pim mbe muuŇčgi bigi ga nzuav mbe suaŇčgi fhuvara. Ana ntigem kha tugen ana khaŇč t…®gap kama havharar za kha nuianan ki Ňčguir ki gumgi ga nzuai, mbe za ndavi domdorgiri.
\v 31 \x - \xo 17:31 \xt Sng 9.8; 96.13; FG 2.24; 10.42; Ro 2.16; 14.10\x*Ana vh…®ra za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv suanga tuga mbe sarigi. Mba tugar, ana won t…®var vhuuŇč z…®n Ňčg…®p, ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga. Fhe Bak…®me mba tugen guma mbe farasarigi, ana mba guman panan, ana mba gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga. Ana mba farasarigi guma, ana rimgia mboga t…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me taagia ana khavgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza guigira Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®rga, ana mba Ňčaarar ana n…®…®Ňčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Por mba bunin mbe suaŇčgim, mba gumgi mba guma rimgiap mboga t…®gap taagia khavgi ne mbararagiap, mbe gumgi mbari Por nz…®…®v, ana nzuai. Mbe mbari khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNza wom kha buni suaŇčrim, nza nta mbarararganeŇč vuzvugi.‚ÄĚ
\v 33 Mbe maaŇč Por ga nzuaim, Por mbe thav vui.
\v 34 Por vuim, gumgi mbari ana z…®n vov, Zisas khoth…®gi. Ana z…®n vov, Zisas khoth…®gi guma mbe khare, Dionisius. Ana mba Areopagus mb…®ksh…®man phogi ga vhui buaadegi gumgi phorga phogi ga vhui bomadagi guma mbe ma. Ana z…®n vui mbiga mbe, ana z…® Damaris, ana vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gim, harigi gumgi gu mbigi mbari, mbe vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gi.
\c 18
\s1 Por Korinan Ňčgu bak…®men Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Por zumgum Atena Ňčgu bak…®me thav, khavgia vov, Korinan Ňčgu bak…®men vugi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Ro 16.3; 1 Ko 16.19; 2 T 4.19\x*Por Korinan Ňčgu bak…®men vugap, ana maam Zuda guma mben h…®gi. Mba guma z…®, Akuira. Akuira Ňčgu n…®…®Ňčge khare, ana Pontus Ňčgu bak…®me fhaiŇč guma ma. Ana won muuŇč Prisiran kov, mani maneŇč fhumra Itari fhaiŇč thav wani z…®gi. Mani khaŇč muuŇčgiap, Sisar Krodius fhum khaŇč ZudaiŇč ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Rom Ňčgu bak…®me thav wari Ňčg…®p harigi Ňčguir k…®ri.‚ÄĚ Mani maaŇč muuŇčgiap zav, Korinan ki. Mani maaŇč kim, Por vov, manin h…®gi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt FG 20.34; 1 Ko 4.12; 1 Te 2.9; 2 Te 3.8\x*Por mani mbui Ňčaarara mbui. Mbe wari t…®gap sher pheni sai. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap Por mani phorgap maaŇč kav, mbe wari t…®gap Ňčgarav ki.
\v 4 Por maaŇč kav, ana zazera Sabari tug…®rat…®gap, ana vov ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen verav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mba ZudaiŇč gu GrikiŇč kh…®vav mbe nzuai. Ana ZudaiŇč gu GrikiŇč nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rgane vuzvugi. Ana mbe nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rim, mbe Zisas khoth…®g…®rga.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt FG 9.22; 17.3; 17.14-15; 18.28\x*Por maaŇč mbuav kim, Sairas gu Timoti Masedonia Ňčgu bak…®me thav zergim, Por mbaram wo mbui Ňčaari mbari, ana za nta thav, ana rari tug…®rat…®gap zazera Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Ana khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, khaŇč ZudaiŇč ga nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas ana Fhe Bak…®me taagip wo gumgi gu mbigi nd…®r zav suaŇčgiap farasarigi guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Ese 18.13; FG 13.45-46; 13.51; 20.26; 1 Pi 4.4\x*Por maaŇč ZudaiŇč ga nzuaim, mbe ana buni mbararargeŇč thav hegap, ana nz…®…®v ana nzuai. Mbe ana nz…®…®v ana nzuaim, Por thav khaŇč muuŇčgi, ana wo sharigi shagi vher…®na mbozav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNden ntuu zumgum vhavar Ňčgirg…®p, shirga, nden simt…®k ma. Nden vhav na shigirga tukt…®gi fhu. Gu big…®na mbat…®ga thuen nde muuŇčgi fhuvara. Gu ntigem nde thav, gu Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč, gu nta bun harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi ga suanga.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Por maaŇč mbe suaŇčgia thugap, mbaram Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena thav khavgia vov, guma mbe phenan vugi. Mba guma z…® khare, Titius Zastus. Mba guma ana Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbui guma ma. Ana phen mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena hara ki.
\v 8 \x - \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Ko 1.14\x*Mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena gari guman pan, ana z…® Krispus. Ana wo phenan ki nt…®…®rir kov, mbe za Zisas buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gi. Mbe Zisas khoth…®gim, mba Korin Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera Por buni mbararav, mbe vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n panan ruagi.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Jos 1.9; Ais 41.10; Jer 1.8; 1.18-19; Mt 28.20; Zo 10.1; FG 23.11; 1 Ko 2.3\x*MaaŇč mben, Por r…®ma kui fara muuŇčgiap garim, Fhe Bak…®me ana h…®gap, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu r…®v…® thari. Ndu na buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčri. Ndu th…®…®ni p…®n…® thari.
\v 10 Gu ndu phorga ki. Guma the ntigem khavgip t…®va mbat…®k thuen ndun muuŇčgirga fhu. Gu khaŇč muuŇčgiap nen ndu nzuai, na gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve kha Ňčgu bak…®men ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč Por ga suaŇčgim, Por Korin Ňčgu bak…®mera kim, mpari mbave mporath…®gi k…®ni phorga vh…®zgi. Ana mpari bavira mporath…®gi k…®nin maaŇč kav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mba gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vigi.
\p 
\v 12 Por maaŇč mbuav kim, Gario h…®gap, Akaia Ňčgu bak…®me fhaiŇč gari guman pan ki. Gario guman pan kim, mba ZudaiŇč, mbe zam hegap, panan Por ga kegi. Mbe panan Por ga kegap, ana nzuav suan zav ana ndiga vui. Mbe ana ndiga vugap, ana nzuav khaŇč nzuai,
\v 13 ‚ÄúKha guma, ana Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi daaŇčsurga t…®vir kha gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vav ana vh…®ra harigi t…®var Fhe Bak…®me rotur muun zav mbe nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 \x - \xo 18:14 \xt FG 23.29; 25.11; 25.19\x*Mba ZudaiŇč maaŇč nzuaim, Por mbe buni Ňčgarka zav mbuim, Gario h…®gap, khaŇč mba ZudaiŇč ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde ZudaiŇč, kha guma maaŇč muuŇčgip RomiŇč nzuai t…®vi khara th…®g…®p, t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgirga, gu nde ZudaiŇč nzuai buna thueŇč mbararagirga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Zo 18.31; FG 23.29; 25.18-19\x*Nde fhura ana nzuai buni, nde nta mbararav, nde wari wo nzuai buni gum, nde wo bigi z…®ri gum, nde won t…®vira nzuav, ana ndiga na han z…®gi. Nde mba bigira nzuav ana ndiga na han z…®gi, ne nzerigi fhuvara. Nde big…®n ma, nde nduarira ana phorg…®v suaŇčv mba bigi ndiv th…®gar mbarari. Gu mba khesharigi bigi, nde nta suaŇčv suanga buna thueŇč mbararagirga fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Gario maaŇč mba ZudaiŇč ga suaŇčgiap, mbaram, mbe vharigim, mbe sagi.
\v 17 Gario mbe vharigim, mba Korinan ki gumgi, mbe hegap, mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena gari guman pan Sostenes, mbe ana suirav, mba buni nzuai Ňčanera, ana shogav ana Ňčgaa rui. Mbe Gario n…®mara ana shogim, Gario ne nzuav buna thuen mbe suaŇčgi fhu. \f a \fr 18:17 \ft Mbe mba fhain tuituigiap Grikin kama kaŇčgi fhuvara. Mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi mbari, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe ZudaiŇč nduarira wari wo guman pana vhegap, ana shogi. \f*
\s1 Por taagiap Antiokan Siria fhain vui.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 18:18 \xt Nam 6.18; FG 21.24; Ro 16.1\x*Por Korin Ňčgu bak…®mera kim, rari vh…®rve vh…®zgim, ana zumgum Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi phorga nzuav, mben harir suigiap, mbe thav vov, Senkria Ňčgu bak…®men vegap, fega Sirian ndai keman mbarav ndai. Por vuim, Prisira gu Akuira, mani vh…®ra ana phorga vui. Por verav Senkrian kav, ana fhum Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi kameŇč z…®n vov wo pana ph…®rgi. \f b \fr 18:18 \ft Mbe ZudaiŇč khaŇč mbui, mbe kama havharan buna thuen Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suaŇčgip, mbe wo pani sh…®…®Ňč thav fhura k…®v k…®v, mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi bigen muunga tuk h…®g…®rga. Mbe mba bigen muuŇčgip, mbe za wari wo pani sh…®rga. \f*
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt FG 17.17; Ro 1.10; 1 Ko 4.19; Hi 6.3; Ze 4.15\x*Mbe kema ndiga nda vov, Efesus phorgi. Mbe Efesus phorgap, Por mbaram Prisira gum Akuira ndi maaŇč t…®gap, ana nduara vov, ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen vergap, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin ZudaiŇč kh…®vav mbe nzuai.
\v 20 Por mbe nzuaim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu thaneŇč tuga mpeeŇčra nza phorg…® k…®ri.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč ana nzuaim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúGu ne muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Ana maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbe phorga nzuav, mben harir suigap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me vuzvuk ma, ana vuzvugirga, gu taagi nden han z…®rga.‚ÄĚ Ana nen mbe suaŇčgiap, taagia vov kema ndigap, Efesus thav vui.
\v 22 Por Efesusan kema ndigap, nda vov, Sisaria phorgi. Ana vov Sisaria phorgap, kema thav, nda vov, Zerusareman ndav, mba Zerusareman Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi phorga nzuav, mben harir suigi. Ana mben harir suigiap, zumgum mbe thav vera vov Antiokan vergi.
\p 
\v 23 Por tuga mpeeŇčnera Antiokan kegap, vugi. Ana vuav tamtamra mba Garesia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain ki Ňčgui gum Frigia fhain ki Ňčgui, ana nta ruav, Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe Zisas khoth…®g…®p, th…®g…® havhargirga bunin mbe nzua rui.
\s1 Aporos Efesusan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 24 Por maaŇč mbuav ruim, Zuda guma mbe, ana Areksandria Ňčgu bak…®me guma ma, ana zav Efesusan ki. Ana z…® Aporos. Ana buni vhuuiŇč nzuai guma ma, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar, anan buni vhuuiŇč, ana guigira nta kaŇčgi guma ma.
\v 25 \x - \xo 18:25 \xt FG 19.3; Ro 12.11\x*Mbe vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me muun zav suaŇčgi t…®vir ana kh…®vigim, ana nta kaŇčgi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana nd…®knd…®k khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, mba bigi bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav, mbe kh…®vi. Ana ntan mbe kh…®vav, vh…®ra Zisas muuŇčgi bigi, ana ntara bun mbe nzuai. Ana ntara bun mbe nzuav, vh…®ra Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma gumgi gu mbigi ruagi, nera kaŇčgi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 18:26 \xt FG 19.8\x*Ana maaŇč mbuav, ana vh…®ra vov ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen verav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Ana maaŇč mbuav, ana vh…®ra gumgi gu mbigir r…®vi fhu. Ana mba buni nzuaim, Prisira gu Akuira ana buni mbararagiap, mani ana suaŇčgiap, ana ko wani wo phenan vugap, Fhe Bak…®me nzuai tuavar ana kh…®vi, ana tuituigip ana kaŇčgirga.
\v 27 \x - \xo 18:27 \xt FG 9.22; 17.3; 18.5; 1 Ko 3.6; 2 Ko 3.1\x*Aporos maaŇč kegap, zumgum maaŇč thav, khavgiap, Akaia fhain Ňčg…®r za mbui. Ana Ňčg…®r za mbuim, mba Efesusan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra ana mba Ňčg…®r zav mbui nd…®knd…®k, mbe vh…®ra mba nd…®knd…®ga vuzvugiap, ana kurav, ana nd…®knd…®ga havhargim, ana vui. Ana vuim, Efesusan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbaram gava khergiap, mba Akaian Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ndi mbav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha guma ndigip t…®var vhuun ana muuŇčri.‚ÄĚ Mbe gava kherav maaŇč suaŇčgim, Aporos vov, Akaia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain h…®gi. Ana h…®gap, mba fhain Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana khaŇč t…®gap mben kurkurigi. Ana kurkurigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me mben kora muuŇčgiap, mbe ndigim, mbe ana khoth…®gi.
\v 28 Aporos khaŇč t…®gap mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®man Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Ana ZudaiŇč suaŇčgi nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi Ňčgarkav, nta mbevav mbe nzuai. Ana mba bunin mbe nzuav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar buni vhuuin mbe nzuav, mbe hiav, khaŇč mbe nzuai ‚ÄúZisas ana Fhe Bak…®me taagip wo gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav suaŇčgiap farasarigi guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\c 19
\s1 Por Efesusan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. \fig [map]|alt="Map Namba 3 Taim Pol i go raun na autim gutnius" src="paul3.tif" size="span" copy="The British and Foreign Bible Society" ref="Farasegi Gumgi 19"\fig*
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 19:1 \xt 1 Ko 1.12; 3.6\x*Aporos Korinan ki tugen, Por mba mb…®ksh…®…®r ki Ňčguia ruav kav, ana zumgum zav, Efesus Ňčgu bak…®men z…®gi. Ana zav, Efesusan Zon khoth…®gap Zisas z…®n vui gumgi mbarir h…®gi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 19:2 \xt FG 2.38; 8.16\x*Ana mbe gangiap, kha nzambaran mbe muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúNde Zisas khoth…®gap, Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi o, fhu?‚ÄĚ Ana mba nzambaran mbe muuŇčgim, mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhuvara. Nza Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara the ki kama thueŇč mbararagi fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 19:3 \xt Mt 3.11\x*Mbe maaŇč nzuaim Por, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap nde ram mbui khesharigi ruar…®a muuŇčgi?‚ÄĚ Por maaŇč mbe nzuaim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma nza ruagi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 19:4 \xt Mt 3.11; Mk 1.4; 1.7-8; Ru 3.4; 3.16; Zo 1.15; 1.26-30; FG 18.25; 19.4\x*Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúZon Gumgi Ruai Guma fhum gumgi gu mbigi ruav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNde ndavi domdor…®v, ruari. Nde ruav, mba na z…®n zi guma, nde na khoth…®g…®ri.‚Äô Nde kha Zon Gumgi Ruai Guma bun suaŇčgi guma, ana Zisas ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Mbe Por buni mbararagiap, mbe Zisas z…®n panan ruagi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 19:6 \xt FG 2.4; 6.6; 8.17; 10.44-46\x*Mbe ruagim, Por won farven mbe kh…®ngim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara mbe rugim, mbe harigi Ňčguir kaa ga vov vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\v 7 Mbe mba tugar Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ndigi gumgi, mben vh…®rve ph…®k bavira phunini th…®gi.
\p 
\v 8 Mbe Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaara ndigim, Por vov ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen vergap, khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me wo gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga buni vhuuin mbe kh…®vav, mbe nzuav kim, kh…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 19:9 \xt FG 9.2; 2 Ko 6.14-18; 2 Pi 2.2\x*Por Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuin mbe nzuaim, mben gumgi gu mbigi mbari, mbe ndavi havhargiap, Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč khoth…®gi fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve n…®mara, Fhe Bak…®me nzuai tuavi, mbe buni mbat…®gir nta nzuai. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Por mbe thav, Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, ana mbe ndigap, mbe wom ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen veri fhu. Por zazera rari tug…®rat…®gap vov, Tiranus shure phenan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\v 10 \x - \xo 19:10 \xt 2 T 1.15\x*Por mba phenara maaŇč mbuav kim, mpari mpuveni vh…®zgi. Ana maaŇč mbuim, Esia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za Guma Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč mbararagi. Mbe ZudaiŇč gu GrikiŇč, mbe wari t…®g…®ra.
\s1 Skevan tari, mbe Ňčina mbat…®ga vharvhara za mbui.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 19:11 \xt FG 14.3\x*Por maaŇč kav Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuaim, Fhe Bak…®me Poran kurkurigim, ana Fhe Bak…®me ŇčkasŇčkar panan, mbark…®rga mirikori bak…®vi ga mbui.
\v 12 \x - \xo 19:12 \xt FG 5.15\x*Por maaŇč mbuim, gumgi gu mbigi Por wo fhava mb…®ri haŇčgisivi gu vhaa r…®gi shagi, mbe nta ndia vov, r…®…®i gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®im, mben r…®mr…®…® vh…®zim, ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi mbe thamtha vui.
\v 13 \x - \xo 19:13 \xt Mk 9.38\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, ZudaiŇč mbari, mbe tamtam mba bigi ga ruav, gumgi gu mbigi t…®n ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi ga vharvharigi. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mbe mbari Guma Bak…®me Zisas z…®n mparav, ana z…® zitav, gumgi gu mbigir t…®n ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi ga vharvhara za mbui. Mbe ruav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Por bun nzuai Zisas z…®n panan kama havharar nde nzuai, nde k…®rar h…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Mba ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guma pan, Skeva, ana harath…®gi tari tegi. Anan tari ruav mba suambarar mba ŇčiniŇčgi mbat…®gi ga mbui.
\v 15 \x - \xo 19:15 \xt Mk 1.24; 1.34\x*Mbe mba suambara mbua ruav kav, raa mben mbe mba suambarara Ňčina mbat…®ga mbe mbuim, mba Ňčina mbat…®k mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Zisas kaŇčgi, gu Por kaŇčgi. Gu nde kaŇčgi fhu, nde theiŇč?‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Mba Ňčina mbat…®k mba nzambaran mbe muuŇčgiap, mba vhen ndagi guma ga rugim, ana khavgiap, fega mba gumgi t…®n mbarav, hor mbat…®gar mbe mbuav, guigira mbe kambarigi. Ana mbe shogap, guigira mben fhavir farfav, mben shagi, ana za nta suigap, nta r…®za suegi. Ana maaŇč mbe muuŇčgim, mbe v…®zi fhavi ga fuigap, mba phena thav, mbugara regi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 19:17 \xt Ru 7.16; FG 2.43; 5.5; 5.11\x*Mba bigeŇč mben h…®gim, mba Efesusan ki ZudaiŇč gu GrikiŇč, mba bigeŇč mbararagiap, mbe guigira rivgi. Mbe rivgia thav, Guma Bak…®me Zisas z…® ndi vun kuamkuagi.
\v 18 Mbe maaŇč mbuav, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve mbe Zisas khoth…®gap, mbe zav, mba harigi gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve n…®man, mbe fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta bun nzuai.
\v 19 Mbe nta bun nzuaim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe kugi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, tori mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgi. Mbe mba kugi gu tori mbat…®gi kaas…®gi ki gavi, mbe nta ndiga zav phok kh…®ngiap, mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve n…®man nta mpooi. Mbe mba phok kh…®ngi gavi, nta vhezgi vhez khaŇč muuŇčgi, 50,000 rarir Ňčgarigi guma ga vhezi vheza tukt…®gi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 19:20 \xt FG 6.7; 12.24\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men bunin vhuuiŇč khaŇč th…®ga havhargia za mba bigir vuim, gumgi gu mbigir vh…®rve, mbe th…®ga havhargiap Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui.
\s1 EfesusiŇč kakama mbat…®gar Por ga mbui.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 19:21 \xt FG 18.21; 20.22; 23.11; Ro 1.13; 15.24-28; Ga 2.1\x*Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka Efesusan h…®gap, khaŇč t…®gap Ňčgari. Ana Ňčgarav Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar Por ga rugap ana nd…®knd…®ga khavgiap, nd…®knd…®gar ana nd…®…®im, ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu fharav Masedonia fhain Ňčg…®g…®p, Ňčg…®p, Akaia fhain Ňčg…®g…®p, gu zumgum Zerusareman naanga. Gu Ňčg…®p, mba fhaiŇč gangip, gu vh…®ra zumgum Ňčg…®p, Rom gangirga.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 \x - \xo 19:22 \xt Ro 16.23; 2 T 4.20\x*Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbaram, won kurkurigi guma phunini, Timoti gu Erastus, ana mani ga sarigim, mani fharav, ana n…®ma t…®gap Masedonian vugi. Mani vugim, Por nduara maneŇč tuga mpeeŇčra Esia Ňčgu bak…®men kegi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 19:23 \xt 2 Ko 1.8\x*Mba tugen gumgi mbari mbe Guma Bak…®me nzuai tuavi, mbe panan nta kegi. Mbe panan nta kegap, nta kaadogiap, ntara bak…®me khavgi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 19:24 \xt FG 16.16-19\x*Mba gumgi maaŇč mbuim, guma mbe ana z…®, Demitrius, ana sirvar bigi kari guma ma. Ana mba sh…®ga mbui guma ma. Ana mba sh…®ga mbuav, ana mba sirvar, mbe won mbar…®va bak…®me, Artemis, rotu mbui pheni bisaŇčrire ntuu kargi. Ana mba Ňčaarar gumgi mbari ga n…®…®Ňčgim, mbe sirvar pheni gum harigi bigi ntuu karav, ntan panan Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rvera ndi.
\v 25 Demitrius mba gumgi fugap, mbaram mba harigi bigi ga mbui gumgi mbari phorgap fugap, khaŇč mbe nzuai. ‚ÄúNde nza wari t…®gap Ňčaara bavira mbui nt…®…®ri ma. Nza kha sh…®ga mbuim, Ňčk…®…®a nzerara him, nza Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rvera ndi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 19:26 \xt Sng 115.4; Ais 44.10-20; Jer 10.3; FG 17.29; 2 T 1.15\x*Kha guma Por, ana z…®gap, ana gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera Ňčgav, mbe nd…®knd…®gi tuara mbuim, nde khar mba bigi mbararav, ana mbui t…®vi gari. Ana kha Efesus Ňčgu bak…®mera mba bigi ga mbui fhuvara. Ana kha mbui bigi, nta za kha Esia fhaiŇč vhara za mbui. Ana mba bigi ga mbuav khaŇč nza nzuai, ‚ÄėNza kha won farir mbar…®vi ntuu karigi, nta guigira bigi guari fhuvara.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Por nzuai buni, nta guigira nzan sh…®gar farfagirga buni ma. Mba buni vh…®ra mba gumgi gu mbigi nd…®knd…®gir muuŇčrim, mbe kha nd…®knd…®gar nzan mbar…®va bak…®me Artemisan phenan muunga, ana fhura ki ne ma. Nza fhum kha Esia fhain ki gumgi gu mbigi gum, za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe fharav kha mbiga bak…®me Artemis, mbe ana rotu mbui. Por ntige z…®gap nzuai buni, nta Artemis z…® bak…®men farfa za mbui. \f a \fr 19:27 \ft Mba mbar…®p, ana mbar…®va mbik ma. \f*
\p 
\v 28 Demitrius mba bunin mba gumgi ga suaŇčgim, mbe guigira ndav shigi. Mbe ndav shigap, kh…®r…®v kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza EfesusiŇč nzan mbiga bak…®me Artemis, ana guigira fharigi ne ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 29 \x - \xo 19:29 \xt FG 20.4; 27.2; Ro 16.23; 1 Ko 1.14; Kor 4.10; Fm 1.24\x*Mba gumgi kaai kakam, za mba Ňčgu bak…®me rugim, mba gumgi gu mbigi fhura tuavapuri. Mbe tuavapurav, wari t…®g…®ra khuafuiga vov, Gaius gu Aristarkus suirav, mani ndiga mba phogi ga vhuav buni nzuai Ňčanen vui. Mani Masedonia gumani ma, mani vh…®ra Por phorga rui gumani ma.
\v 30 Mba gumgi gu mbigi mba t…®va mbuim, Por nduara wo ndigip mbe vhen Ňčgir…® za mbuim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ana th…®vigi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 19:31 \xt 2 T 1.15\x*Por vh…®ra mba Esia fhaiŇč gari gumgir pani mbari, mbe ana khurkhuur vhuuiŇč ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana ndi kama ndi mbarigi. Mbe kama ndi mbav, kama havharar khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu mbe phogi ga vhuav buni nzuai Ňčanen Ňčg…® thari.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mben nd…®knd…®gi guigira ŇčanŇčangi. Mbe fhura kaav, fhura tamtam buni nzuai. Kha za wari fhugi gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rvera, mbe mba phoga vhui buna n…®…®eŇč kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 33 Mbe fhura kav garim, ZudaiŇč hegap, Areksander b…®rgim, ana vov mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®man th…®gi. Ana vov th…®gim, mba gumgi gu mbigi ana garav, kha nd…®knd…®gar ana mbui, ana mba simt…®ga bak…®me khavgi guma ma. Areksander mba gumgi gu mbigi n…®ma th…®gap, mbe buni Ňčgarka zav, farvera mbe khakhaigi, mbe th…®…®ri p…®ngirim, ana mbe suanga. \f b \fr 19:33 \ft Mbe kha fhain tuituigiap Grikin kama kaŇčgi fhuvara. \f*
\p 
\v 34 Ana mbe khakhaigi, mbe ana gangiap, ana heigi, ana Zuda guma ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe wari t…®g…®ra kh…®r…®v, kaav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza EfesusiŇč, nzan mbiga bak…®me Artemis, ana guigira fharigi.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuav kaavra kim, aua phunini vh…®zgi.
\p 
\v 35 Mbe maaŇč mbuav kim, aua phunini vh…®zgim, zumgum mba Efesus Ňčgu bak…®me gari fh…®ga suigi guma, mba gumgi gu mbigir Ňčgarigim, mbe fhura vhuagi. Mbe vhuagim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha EfesusiŇč gumgi gu mbigi, nde na mbarara. MaaŇčgi guma nde EfesusiŇč mba wari won mbiga bak…®me Artemis rotu mbui phena garav, vh…®ra mba mbe th…®vigi k…®m, ana buivar kege r…®gi. MaaŇčgi guma nen kakagi?
\v 36 Guma the nde daaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde wo th…®…®ri p…®ngiri. Nde ntigem hurar vhemkora big…®n thuen muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 37 Nde kha suira z…®gi gumani, mani nza rotu mbui phenan nza big…®n the k…®mgi fhuvara. Mani vh…®ra, nza rotu mbui mbiga bak…®me, mani vh…®ra ana nz…®…®i buna thueŇč suaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 38 Nde mbarara, Demitrius won Ňčaara gumgir kov, mbe kama thueŇč guma the k…®v, mbe rarg…®ri, buni nzuai tuk ki, vh…®ra Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari ki. Mbe z…®v, ana phorg…® suaŇčv mba kameŇč ndi th…®gar maanga.
\v 39 Nde vh…®ra maaŇč muuŇčgip harigi buni thari phorg…® k…®v, nde mba buni nzuai phogi ki tugara, nde mba buni suaŇčv nta ndi th…®g…®ra maaŇčri.
\v 40 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde mbararari. Nde ntige khar mbui bigeŇč, maaŇč muuŇčgip kha Ňčgui gari guman panan vharir Ňčaara guman pan kha kameŇč mbararagirga, ana guigira nza suaŇčv suaŇčgirga. Ana nza suaŇč suaŇčv khaŇč suaŇčgirga, nza big…®na mbat…®ga mueŇč khavi. Nza ntige khar mbui bigeŇč, ne guigira n…®…®eŇč ki fhuvara. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip z…®v nzan nzaŇčv khaŇč nza suanga, ‚ÄėNde thaŇč nzuav zav, khaŇč kav wari fhura tamtam kaai.‚Äô Mbe maaŇč suanga, nza mben Ňčgarkarga buna thueŇč ki fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 41 Mben Ňčgu gari fh…®ga suigi guma pan maaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčgiap, mbe sarigim, mbe taagia vui.
\c 20
\s1 Por Masedonian vov Grikar vugi.
\p 
\v 1 Mba gumgi gu mbigi tuavapurgia thugim, Por mbaram, mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir kamgim, mbe ana han zim, ana mbe fugap, mbe ndavi havhari bunin mbe suaŇčgiap, mben harir suigiap, mbe thav Masedonian fhain vui.
\v 2 Por vov Masedonia fhain vugap, ana maaŇč ruav, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe ndavi havharav, mbe phorga nzua rui. Ana maaŇč mbua vov, zumgum ana vov Grik fhain vugi.
\v 3 Por Grikar kim, k…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgim, ana mbaram, Siria fhain Ňčg…®r za mbui. Ana Ňčg…®r za mbuav mbararagim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúZudaiŇč ndu shogiri ndu r…®m…®ngane nzuai.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč muuŇčgia mbararagia thav, khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi ‚ÄúGu wom taagia Masedonian sh…®rav Ňčg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 4 \x - \xo 20:4 \xt FG 19.29; 21.29; Ef 6.21\x*Por taagia Masedonian vuim, Beria guma Sopater, Pirusan kam, ana ana phorga vui. Tesaronaika guma phunini, Aristarkus gu Sekundus, Derbe guma Gaius gum, Timoti, Esia guma phunini, Tikikus gu Trofimus, mbe vh…®ra Por phorga vui.
\v 5 Mbe fhara vov, Troasan kav, nzan rargi.
\v 6 Nza Firipaira kim, mba vhuui fhuv viktuma pi tugi bak…®vi vh…®zgim, nza vui. Nza Firipai tha vuav kim, feth…®gi rari vh…®zgim, nza meeŇčth…®gi ran, nza vov Troasan kav, nzan rargi gumgi, nza mben h…®gi. Nza Troasan mben h…®gap, harath…®gi rarir nza Troasan kegi. \f a \fr 20:6 \ft Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi vh…®rve, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Por taagia Firipain z…®gap, ana Rukar kov vugi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, kha kameŇč wom khaŇč h…®gi. Mba kameŇč khare. Nza ndu FG 16.10 gan…®ri. \f*
\s1 Por Troasan Utikusan kurigim, ana taagia khavgi.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 20:7 \xt FG 2.42; 2.46; 1 Ko 16.2; VB 1.10\x*Por Troasan kav nza Sanden Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi fugap, mbe phorga mb…®r za mbui. \f b \fr 20:7 \ft Mbe ZudaiŇč, mben t…®v, mbe khaŇč nzuai, mbe harigi raar kam, ana ra vera vov mpora ndim, Ňčkotuguraagen raar kam hi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza won t…®va z…®n vov, Sarare Ňčkotugar, mbe khaŇč nzuai, ana harigi Ňčaaren fharigi raa ma. Por mbe phorga mbegap, ana Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe phorga nzuai. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana gurmaŇčgip mbe thav Ňčg…®rga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin mbe nzuavra kim, maaŇč vov r…®gafurigi. \f*\f c \fr 20:7 \ft Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap nta kheri gumgi vh…®rve, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe Zisas v…®z…®n gum ana fhava s…®ga nd…®knd…®gi mba pi. \f*
\p 
\v 8 Nza kav, Por mbe phorga nzuai phen, ana vundap vhu guarara ki. Ana vhen raa vh…®rve ki.
\v 9 Nza mba vundavar kav, Por mbe phorga nzuai. Por mbe phorga nzuaim, tarar kama mbe, ana mba phenan b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč zi th…®mkamani ga perav ki. Ana perav kim, Por pim buni nzua vuav kim, Ňčkuu Utikus ga muuŇčgim, ana kuav ki. Ana kuav kav, kuiga Ňčangiap, ana mba vundav phuni kambara vhu guarara ki nen kegap, daaŇčgia n…®…®eŇč r…®gi. Ana daaŇčgia n…®…®eŇč r…®gim, mbe verav ana garim, ana za rimgi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 20:10 \xt 1 Kin 17.21\x*Mbe ana gan…® za verim, Por vh…®ra mbe phorga verav, ana gangiap, ana vov mba tara kama t…®thogap anan suirigi. Por ana suirav, khaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha guman kama gangip Ňčgava mbat…®gar muuŇč thari. Anan b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč khar ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Por maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbara taagia mbe mba ki vun ndagi vundavar ndav, viktuma ph…®rgiap, mba gumgi gu mbigir kov, mbe ana pi. Mbe mbegap, ana wom mbe phorga Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč nzuav tuga mpeeŇčra kegi. Ana mbe phorga nzuavra kim, m…®n thugim, ana mbe thav vui.
\v 12 Mba maan r…®gi tarar kam, ana rimgi fhuvara. Ana nzerara kim, mbe ana ko vui. Mbe ana ko vo, guigira ndikndigap, ndavi mb…®rigi.
\s1 Por Troas thav, Miretusan vui.
\p 
\v 13 Por maaŇč kim, nza fhara ana thav, kema ndigap, Asos Ňčgu bak…®men vegi. Nza vegap, Asos Ňčgu bak…®men kav, Porar rargi. Ana nduara nza sarigim, nza fhara vegi, ana th…®var z…®rgeŇč vuzvugiap, ana th…®var zi.
\v 14 Nza maaŇč kim, Por th…®var zav Asosan nzan h…®gim, nza ana kov vov, kema ndigap, vov Mitirini Ňčgu bak…®men vegi.
\v 15 Nza Mitirinin vegap, m…®timanera Mitirinin thav vov, Kios r…®g…®k…®rigen han mbarigi. Nza mba m…®timanera Kios r…®g…®k…®rige kambara vov, Samos Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorgap, mba m…®timanera nza vov Miretus Ňčgu bak…®men vegi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 20:16 \xt FG 18.21; 24.17; 1 Ko 16.8\x*Nza vov, maaŇč vegap, Por thav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu wo nd…®knd…®k kaŇčgi, gu Efesusa Ňčk…®…®arga. Gu khaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu Esia fhaiŇčra, gu fhura won tuga vh…®zgirga ne vuzvugi fhuvara. Gu vhemkora Ňčg…®r za mbui. Na vuzvuk ma, gu vuzvugirga, gu Zerusareman mba Pentikos tuga bak…®me gangirga.‚ÄĚ \f d \fr 20:16 \ft Ndu FG 2.1 gan…®ri. \f*
\s1 Por Efesusan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, ana mben harir suigi.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt FG 18.21\x*Nza vov Miretus Ňčgu bak…®men hegap, Por mbaram, Efesusan Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani ga nzuav kama ndi mbai. Ana mbe nzuav kama ndi mbarigim, mbe zav, ana gari. \f e \fr 20:17 \ft Miretus Ňčgu bak…®me, ana Efesus Ňčgu bak…®me thav samra ki. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgi 50 kiromitas. \f*
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 20:18 \xt FG 18.19; 19.10\x*Ana mbe nzuav kama ndi mbarigim mbe ana han zegim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nduarira gu fharav Esia fhain z…®gap, nde phorga kav, zazera muuŇčgi bigi, nde nta kaŇčgi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 20:19 \xt FG 20.3\x*Nde kaŇčgi, ZudaiŇč vh…®rve, mbe zazera na mbev…®r zav wari t…®gap kaa shogi. Mbe mba t…®va mbuav, mbe ndavi simt…®gi vh…®rver na nd…®…®v, mbe vh…®ra mparmpare vh…®rver na mbuim, gu tugi vh…®rvera gu nzigi. Mbe maaŇč na mbuim, gu za wo z…® mbevav Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaara mbui.
\v 20 Gu mbe kh…®ge rav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin nde nzuav nde kurkura thagi fhuvara. Gu mba gumgi gu mbigi phogi ga vui tugir, gu Fhe Bak…®me bunin vhuuin nde kh…®vav nde nzuai. Gu vh…®ra nde phenin vov, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin nde kh…®vav nde nzuai. Gu maaŇč nde muuŇčgim, nde ne kaŇčgi.
\v 21 Gu zazera khaŇč t…®ga havhargia ZudaiŇč gu GrikiŇč ga nzuai, mbe guigira wari wo ndavi domdorgip, Fhe Bak…®men han Ňčg…®p, nza wo Bak…®me Zisas khoth…®g…®rga.
\v 22 \x - \xo 20:22 \xt FG 19.21\x*Ore, nde ntige mbarara. Gu ntigem Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar nduara na rugim, gu ntigem Zerusareman naan za mbui. Gu Zerusareman ndarga, thag…®na bigeŇč nan h…®g…®rie? Gu kaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 23 \x - \xo 20:23 \xt FG 19.21; 21.4; 21.11; 1 Te 3.3\x*Gu khueŇčra kaŇčgi. Gu kha Ňčgui vh…®rve ga ruim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar khueŇčra na nzuai, phena t…®vaneŇč gum simt…®gi vh…®rve ndun rarga mbur ki.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 20:24 \xt FG 21.13; Ro 8.35; 2 Ko 4.1; 4.16; Ga 1.1; 2 T 4.7\x*‚ÄúAna mba suambarar na mbuim, gu won fhava nd…®knd…®gi fhu. Gu khaŇč nzuai fhu, na fhav, ana big…®na bak…®me. Gu mba nd…®knd…®ga mbuav won fhava ndi Ňčg…®rŇčg…®rgi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gu kha tuavar Ňčg…®rgeŇč vuzvugi. Gu mba tuavar Ňčg…®p, na Guma Bak…®me Zisas, gu ana han ndigi Ňčaar, gu zam ana vh…®zgirga. Mba Ňčaar khare, gu ruv, ana nza kora muuŇčgi buni vhuuiŇč, gu za nta bun suaŇčgirga.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúNde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, nde na mbarara. Gu fhum nde r…®gar kav, gu Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim mbe ana piin k…®rga, ne bun nde suaŇčgi. Gu ntige kaŇčgi, nde zumgum wom na khoma gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 26 \x - \xo 20:26 \xt FG 18.6; 2 Ko 7.2\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu ntige tuituigia nde suan za mbui. Nden r…®gar, nde the fh…®rgir…®g…®p vhavar Ňčg…®g…®rga, nen vhav na shigirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 27 Gu khaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu Fhe Bak…®men nd…®knd…®gi bun nde suangeŇč thagi fhuvara.
\v 28 \x - \xo 20:28 \xt 1 Ko 12.28; 1 T 4.16; Hi 9.14; 1 Pi 1.19; 5.2-4\x*Nde tuituigira wari gan…®v, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi gan…®ri. Ana mba gumgi gu mbigi, ana won kama v…®z…®nra mbe vhezgi. Anan Ňäina Ňäaar mba gumgi gu mbigi gan…® zav nde farasegi, nde ana sipsivi gan…®ri.
\v 29 \x - \xo 20:29 \xt Mt 7.15; Zo 10.12; 2 Pi 2.1\x*Gu kaŇčgi, gu nde thav Ňčg…®g…®rga, ruaŇčruaŇčgi feiŇč mbat…®gi fara muuŇčgi gumgi guarira nden r…®gar heg…®rga. Mbe nde r…®gar heg…®p, mbe ruaŇčruaŇčgi feiŇč mba sipsivir farfagi fara muuŇčgip, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gar farfagirga.
\v 30 \x - \xo 20:30 \xt 1 T 1.20; 1 Zo 2.19\x*Mbe maaŇč muunga, nden gumgi tharira, mbe heg…®p, tamtam Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin nde guiguig…®p, mbe Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi tuarar muuŇčv mbe Ňčg…®rim, mbe mbe z…®n Ňčgeg…®rga.
\v 31 \x - \xo 20:31 \xt Mk 13.37; FG 19.8-10; 1 Te 2.11\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde zazera tuituigira wari gan…®ri. Nde vh…®ra, gu muuŇčgi t…®vi, nde nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčan…® thari. Gu mpari mpuveni khegnt…®riven, gu rari gu mbarir nd…®knd…®gi vhuuin nden n…®…®ngen vhugi fhuvara. Gu za mba bigir nde heevra, nde suaŇčgi. Gu mba bigir nde kh…®vav nde nzuav, na r…®ma mb…®ni vh…®ra sia suegi.
\p 
\v 32 \x - \xo 20:32 \xt FG 26.18; Ef 1.18; Kor 1.12; Hi 13.9\x*‚ÄúGu ntigem nde ndim Fhe Bak…®me farve kh…®ngi. Gu vh…®ra khueŇč vuzvugi, nde vh…®ra ana fhura guigira nde kora muuŇčgi buni ga nd…®knd…®g…®ri. Anan kora muumbar, ana nde ndavi havhargirga. Anan kora muumbar, vh…®ra ana won mbuigi gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i bigir vhuuiŇč, ana ntan nden n…®…®nga.
\p 
\v 33 \x - \xo 20:33 \xt 1 Sml 12.3; 1 Ko 9.11-12; 2 Ko 7.2\x*‚ÄúGu guma the sirva gu gor anan shagi, gu nta gangiap, nta niihegi fhu.
\v 34 \x - \xo 20:34 \xt FG 18.3; 1 Ko 4.12; 1 Te 2.9\x*Nde nduarira na kaŇčgi, gu won farvera wo bigi ga mbuav, ntan panan ki. Gu ntan panan kav, gu vh…®ra ntan wo phorga ki gumgi gu mben kurkurigi.
\v 35 \x - \xo 20:35 \xt Mt 10.8; 2 Ko 11.9; 11.12; Ef 4.28; 1 Te 4.11; 2 Te 3.8\x*Gu za mba bigi ga mbuav ntan nde kh…®vigi. Nza mba t…®var muuŇčv khaŇč t…®g…®p Ňčgar…®rga. Nza maaŇč muuŇčv Ňčgar…®v, nza mba nduarira warir kurkurarga tukt…®gi fhuv gumgi, nza mben kurkurarga. Nza vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me Zisas suaŇčgi kameŇč, nza ne nd…®knd…®girga. Ana khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėGuma big…®nan harigi guma ga n…®…®Ňčgi ndikndik, ana guigira guma big…®na ndigap, wora mbuigi ndikndik, ana guigira ana kambarigi.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 \x - \xo 20:36 \xt FG 21.5\x*Por mba bunin za Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani phorga suaŇčgia thugap, mbaram mbe wo th…®pani ph…®rgiap fegap, ana Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\v 37 \x - \xo 20:37 \xt FG 20.25\x*Ana mbe phorgap Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgia thugim, mbe za ana nzuav nzi mbat…®ga mbuav, ana fh…®re rav ana khoman mparav, ana viavi.
\v 38 Mbe khueŇč nzuav guigira ana kora muuŇčgiap, nzi mbat…®ga mbui. Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, mbe wom ana khoma gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe maaŇč ana muuŇčgiap, ana kov keman vui.
\c 21
\s1 Por kema ndigap Zerusareman ndai.
\p 
\v 1 Nza maaŇč mba gumgir pani thav, kema regim, kem maaŇč thav sigi. Mba kem maaŇč thav sigap, za vo Kos r…®g…®k…®rigen vugi. Nza maaŇč thav wari wom siga vov, Rodes r…®g…®k…®rigen vegi. Nza niŇčgen vegap, maaŇč thav vov, Patara Ňčgu bak…®men vegi.
\v 2 Nza vov, Pataran vegap, kema mbe garim, ana sig…®p Fonisia fhain Ňčg…®r za mbuim, nza maam fo ana maaŇčgim, ana maaŇč nza kh…®ga sigi.
\v 3 Mba kem nza k…®ga siga vuim, nza Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rige garim, niŇčge nza Ňčk…®n haren th…®ga kim, nza niŇčge kambara vui. Nza vov, Siria fhain hegi. Nza Siria fhain hega vov, Tair Ňčgu bak…®men nimndigi ndi sur zav vov, Tair Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 21:4 \xt FG 20.23; 21.12\x*Nza maam Tair phorgav, nza vov, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari. Nza maam mbe phorga harath…®gi rarir kegi. Nza maaŇč mbe phorga kim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mbe rugim, mbe khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Zerusareman naaŇč thari.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Nza Tairan kim, kem maaŇč thav sir za mbuim, nza Tair Ňčgu bak…®me thav veri. Nza verim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe wari won muuiŇč gum tarir kov, nzan kov mba Ňčgu bak…®me thav k…®rar hegap, veri. Mbe nzan kov, verav mbas…®k taan vergim, nza maam th…®vi ph…®ra fegap, nza mbe phorga Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.
\v 6 \x - \xo 21:6 \xt FG 20.36\x*Nza maam Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, mbe nzan harir suigim, nza mben harir suigiap, nza maaŇč fo keman maaŇčgiap wari vuim, mbe taagia wari wo phenin vui.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma Agabus Sisarian Por phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 7 Nza maam Tair tha vov, Toremes Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorgap, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi harir suigi. Nza mbe harir suigap, raa bavira mbe phorga maaŇč kegi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 21:8 \xt FG 6.5; 8.5; 8.26; 8.40; Ef 4.11; 2 T 4.5\x*Nza maaŇč kegap, mba m…®timanera maaŇč thav, khavgiap, wari vui. Nza vov, Sisaria Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza Sisaria phorgav, wari vov, Firip phenan vegi. Firip, ana Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai guma mbe ma. Nza ana phorga ki. Firip vh…®ra Zisas mba farasarigi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgir kurkurigi, harath…®gi gumgir r…®gar ki guma mbe ma.
\v 9 \x - \xo 21:9 \xt Jol 2.28; FG 2.17\x*Firip, ana vh…®ra feth…®gi Ňčkarmbigi ki. Mbe mani ga r…®gi fhuvara. Mbe nz…®…®rira kav, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men kaathoorir gumgi nzuai fara muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 21:10 \xt FG 11.28\x*Nza rari mbari phorgap Sisarian kim, Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč guma mbe, ana z…® Agabus, ana Zudian kegap, Sisarian zergi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 21:11 \xt Zo 21.18; FG 20.23; 21.33\x*Ana zergap, zav nzan han z…®gap, Por ret ndigap, wo suani gum harani kegap, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėZerusareman ki ZudaiŇč, mbe kha t…®vara kha ret namkaman muuŇčgip, ana ndi, harigi Ňčguir gumgi farve kh…®ngirga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt Mt 16.22\x*Nza ne mbararagiap, nza mba Ňčgun ki gumgi gu mbigi phorgap, nza khaŇč t…®gap Zerusareman naangen Por th…®vi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 21:13 \xt FG 20.24\x*Nza Por th…®vim, Por nza Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nza nzuai, ‚ÄúNde thaŇč nzuav nziav, nan nd…®knd…®gar farfagi? Gu mbe nan suirav, na k…®rgane vuzvugira khar ki. Gu vh…®ra Zerusareman naaŇčv rimgip, Guma Bak…®me Zisas z…® ndi vun kuamkuargane vuzvugi.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Nza Por th…®vav ana nzuaim, Por Zerusareman naan zav khaŇč t…®ga havhargim, nza wom ana th…®v…®rgeŇč thagi. Nza thav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me vuzvuk ma. Ana mba bigeŇč vuzvugi ne h…®r za mbui, ne mbar h…®.‚ÄĚ
\ms1 Por Zudian phena t…®vaneŇč ga r…®gim, mbe ana nzuai buni mbararagi.
\s1 Por vov Zerusareman h…®gi.
\p 
\v 15 Nza Sisariara kim, rari mbari vh…®zgim, nza bigi bevahegap, Sisaria thav Zerusareman ndai.
\v 16 Nza Sisaria thav, Zerusareman ndaim, maaŇč Sisarian Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi mbari nza phorga ndai. Mbe nzan ko vov, Nason phenan vugi. Nason, ana Saiprus guma ma. Ana fhum guarara, ana Zisas z…®n vui guma ki. Mbe nzan ko vov, ana phena t…®gim, nza ana phenan ki.
\v 17 Nza nda vov, Zerusareman hegim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zav nzan ndikndigi.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 21:18 \xt FG 15.2; 15.13; Ga 1.19; 2.9\x*Nza Zerusarem ndav, m…®timanera Por nzan kov, Zems gan…® za vui. Nza Zems gan…® za vuim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani, mbe vh…®ra zav mba tugar nza phorga Zems phenan phoga vhuigi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 21:19 \xt FG 15.4; 15.12; Ro 15.18-19\x*Mbe nza phorga phoga vhuigim, Por mben ndikndigap, raar vhuun mbe n…®…®Ňčgiap, mbaram Fhe Bak…®me anan kurkurav ŇčkasŇčkar ana nd…®…®im, ana harigi Ňčgui phorga muuŇčgi bigi, ana za ntan mbe neŇčgi.
\s1 Por Zerusarem h…®gi.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 21:20 \xt FG 15.1; 15.5; 22.3; Ro 10.2; Ga 1.14\x*Mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi gari gumgir pani Por suaŇčgi buni mbararagiap, mbe Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuagi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuav, khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNzan fek, ndu kaŇčgi, mbark…®rga tausen ZudaiŇč, mbe za Zisas khoth…®gi. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe za Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, nta z…®n vui.
\v 21 \x - \xo 21:21 \xt FG 16.3; Ga 2.3\x*Mbe nta z…®n vuim, gumgi mbari, mbe ndu nzuav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėPor harigi Ňčguir ki ZudaiŇč, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, nde nta z…®n Ňčg…® thari.‚ÄĚ Ndu maaŇč mbe nzuav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde won tarir fooŇč thari. Nde vh…®ra Moses fhum muun za suaŇčgi t…®vi, nde wom nta z…®n Ňčg…® thari.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô
\v 22 Mbe maaŇč ndu nzuai ne, nza ne kaŇčgi. Mbe ntigem ndu Zerusareman ndagi ne mbararagip, ne suaŇčv ndu suaŇčrim, nza ram muuŇčrie?
\v 23 \x - \xo 21:23 \xt Nam 6.13-21\x*Mbe maaŇč ana suaŇčgiap, thav khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNza t…®va mueŇč kaŇčgi. Ndu ne z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nzan feth…®gi gumgi, mbe fhum kama havharar big…®n muen Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 21:24 \xt FG 18.18\x*Ndu mba feth…®gi gumgi, ndu mbe ndig…®p, nde Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarigi t…®var muuŇčgiri. Ndu vh…®ra mbe Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčv shaman muunga bigi, ndu nta vhezgirim, mbe won pani sh…®vkorgiri. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgirga, kha gumgi gu mbigi khaŇč suanga, mbe khar ndu nzuai buni, nta guigira buni fhuvara. Ndu Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n vui guma ma.\f a \fr 21:24 \ft Ndu FG 18.18 ki kameŇč gan…®ri. Ndu vh…®ra Namba 6.1-21 kameŇč gan…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 21:25 \xt FG 15.29\x*‚ÄúNza fhum mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Zisas khoth…®gi, nza gava khergiap, mbe ndi mbav, nza mba fhum suaŇčgi buni, nza ntan mbe suaŇčgi. Nza mba gavar khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėNde tuituigira wari gan…®ri. Nde guma the nduara won farver tuma kargip, ana n…®man t…®g…®rga s…®k, nde ana mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra v…®z…®nan mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra guma fh…®rar fagim, rimgiap, v…®z…®n korgia ndavar vergi s…®k, nde vh…®ra ana mb…® thari. Nde vh…®ra ruarir gumgi gu mbigi wari k…®m…® thari.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 26 \x - \xo 21:26 \xt Nam 6.13; FG 24.18; 1 Ko 9.20\x*Mbe maaŇč Por ga suaŇčgim, Por mba kama havharar Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap feth…®gi gumgi ndigi. Mba m…®timanera, Por mbe phorgap Fhe Bak…®me n…®ma Ňčgara zav mbe mba suaŇčgi t…®vi, mbe za nta muuŇčgi. Mbe mba t…®vi ga muuŇčgiap, Por vov, Fhe Bak…®men Phena b…®na vhen vergap, Fhe Bak…®me Phenan Ňčaara guma phorga nzuai. Ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgararga t…®vi, nza nta muuŇčgia thugi. Nza harath…®gi rari vh…®zgirim, nza z…®v, shaman muunga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me Phena vhen Por suirigi.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 21:27 \xt Ese 44.7; FG 6.13; 2 T 1.15\x*Por Zerusareman ndav kim, harath…®gi rari vh…®z…® za mbuim, ZudaiŇč mbari, mbe Esia fhain kega Zerusareman ndav, Por garim, ana Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen kim, mbe mbaram vov, mba gumgi gu mbigi ndavi ga sav, mbe ndavi khavim, mbe Por ga vhegi. Mbe Por ga vhegap, hegap, anan suirigi.
\v 28 Mbe ana suirav, kh…®r…®v kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde IsreriŇč gumgi, nde nzan kurari. Kha guma ana za kha Ňčguir ki gumgi ga nzuav, nza nt…®…®ri ndi n…®…®n mp…®…®v, vh…®ra Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, ana vh…®ra nta mbevav, ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Phena ndi n…®…®n p…®…®Ňčgi. Ana mba t…®vara muuŇčgi fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra mba Grikin kov zim, mbe vh…®ra zav Fhe Bak…®men phena b…®na vhen zerav, Fhe Bak…®me won mbuigi ŇčaneŇč ga muuŇčgim, ne Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzaŇčnzaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Mbe mba bunin Por ga nzuai.
\v 29 \x - \xo 21:29 \xt FG 20.4; 24.5-6; 2 T 4.20\x*Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba bunin Por ga nzuai, mbe fhum Efesus guma Trofimus garim, ana Por phorga Zerusareman kegim, mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, Por anan kov Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen vergi thi?
\p 
\v 30 Mba gumgi gu mbigi mba buni mbararagiap, Zerusareman ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgi. Mbe Ňčgava mbat…®ga muuŇčgiap, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za khuafua zav, za wari fugi. Mbe wari fugap, Por suirav, ana Ňčg…®rga Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen kegap k…®rar hi. Mbe ana Ňčg…®rga k…®rar hav, vhemkora mbe Fhe Bak…®men phena b…®na vhen veri th…®…®, mbe za nta puigi. \f b \fr 21:30 \ft Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®ni vh…®rve za ana behuigi. Mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi, mbe Ňčg…®p mba fhara guarara vhen veri b…®n, mbe mba b…®na vhera k…®rga, mbe mbu vhee guarara ki b…®na the vhen Ňčgir…®g…®ra tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe mba Por Ňčg…®rga Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen kega k…®rar h…®gi ne nzuai. Por ana mba fharigi b…®na vhen verga vov, mba fhari b…®na vhen ki b…®na vhen kegim, mbe ana Ňčg…®rga, mba k…®rar ki b…®na vhen zergi. Mbe ana Ňčg…®rga zergap, mba zumgum vov vhen veri b…®n, mbe ana th…®…®, mbe za nta puigi. Mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe za mba vhivgiap, k…®rar ki b…®na bak…®me mbe ana ki. Mba gumgi gu mbigi mbe Fhe Bak…®me phena phogi ga vhuav buni nzuai Ňčani, mbe ntan ki. Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi, mbe phen mba b…®na gaara mb…®ksh…®ma bisaŇč manen ki. Mbe phenan ndai sarve, mba Fhe Bak…®me phenan fharigi b…®na vhen mbe kav, phogi ga vhui Ňčanen kegap, nda vov mbe phena furigi. \f*
\s1 Roman ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi Por ndigi.
\p 
\v 31 Mbe th…®…® za nta puigap, mba gumgi, mbe Por shogirim, ana rimgir zav ana shogim, mba Roman ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan mba kameŇč mbararagi. Ana khueŇč mbararagi, mba Zerusareman ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ntara mbuav tamtam wari shogi.
\v 32 Ana maaŇč suaŇčgia h…®gap, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ndigap, mbe gari gumgir pani ndigap mbe khuafuigap, mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve ki Ňčanen veri. Mbe zerim, ZudaiŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pana garim, ana won ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vir kov zerim, mbe Por shog…® thav wari fhura ki.
\v 33 \x - \xo 21:33 \xt FG 20.23\x*Mbe fhura kim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan zav, Por han z…®gap, ana suirav, mbaram mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuaim, mbe shen phuninin ana kegi. Mbe ana kegim, ana kha nzambaran ZudaiŇč ga muuŇčgi. ‚ÄúKhe the khare? Ana ram mbui bigeŇč muuŇčgi?‚ÄĚ
\v 34 Mba gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve maaŇč kav kh…®r…®v kaav, tamtam buni nzuai. Mbe kh…®kh…®ma bak…®me mbuim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan tuituigiap mba buna n…®…®eŇč mbararagi fhuvara. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgia thav, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuaim, mbe Por ndigap wari wo phenan vui.
\v 35 Mbe vov, wari wo phena sarve th…®man hav garim, mba gumgi gu mbigi Por shogirim, ana rimgir zav khaŇč t…®ga havhargi. Mbe havhargim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi Por suirav, vunfegap, ana ndiga vui.
\v 36 \x - \xo 21:36 \xt Ru 23.18; Zo 19.15; FG 22.22\x*Mbe ana ndiga vuim, gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe z…®n vov, kh…®r…®v kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza ana shogirim, ana rimgirga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Zisas khoth…®gi ne n…®…®eŇč bun ZudaiŇč ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 37 Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi Por ndiga wari won phena vhen Ňčgir…® za mbuim, Por mbaram Grikin kaman khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu buna thuen ndu suaŇčrie?‚ÄĚ Por maaŇč ana nzuaim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan ana nzerigi, ‚ÄúAi, ndu Grikin kama kaŇčgire?
\v 38 \x - \xo 21:38 \xt FG 5.36-37\x*Ai, gu khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ndu kha Idz…®p guma, ndu fhum mba ntara bak…®me khavgiap, 4,000 gumgi ndigi, mbe ntari ga mbui kozin ntari ga mbui. Ndu mbe ndigap, zomzorap, nza RomiŇč, nde nzan ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi phorga shogim, nde vh…®zgi. Ndura mben kov mba gumgi ki fhuv Ňčanen vugi gumara khare thi?‚ÄĚ
\v 39 Ana ne nzuaim, Por khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Zuda guma ma. Gu Sirisia fhain Tarsus guma ma. Nan Ňčgu bak…®me, ana z…® ki Ňčgu ma. Ena, ndu guman vhuuŇč ma. Gu guigira ndun nzai, gu mbu gumgi gu mbigi phorg…®v suan za mbui.‚ÄĚ
\v 40 Por maaŇč nzuaim, ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pan, ana kh…®rigi. Ana Por kh…®rigim, Por mba phena sarvera th…®gap, won farvera mba gumgi gu mbigi khakhaigi, mbe won th…®…®ri p…®n…® zav, ana maaŇč mbe mbui. Ana maaŇč mbe mbuim, mbe za wari wo th…®…®ri p…®ngi. Mbe za vhuagim, Por mbaram Hibruin kama rugap, khaŇč mbe nzuai,
\c 22
\nb 
\v 1 ‚ÄúNde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, nan ndegi, nde mbarara. Gu ntigem guigira nde hiav, nde suan za mbui. Gu big…®na mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 Mbe mbararagim, Por Hibruin kaman mbe nzuaim, mbe za vhuav kav, ana mbararagi.
\p Mbe ana mbararagim, ana vov khaŇč mbe nzuai,
\v 3 \x - \xo 22:3 \xt FG 5.34-39; 9.11; 21.39; 26.5; Ro 10.2; 2 Ko 11.22; Ga 1.14; Fi 3.5\x*‚ÄúGu Zuda guma ma. Nan niamuuŇč Sirisia fhain Tarsus Ňčgu bak…®men na tegi. Gu Zerusarem Ňčgu bak…®men kav vhuuŇčgi. Gamarier na sure muuŇčgi guma ma. Ana guigira nzan nz…®gir t…®vir na sure muuŇčgim, gu guigira nta kaŇčgi. Gu nta kaŇčgiap, gu vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me vuzvugi t…®vi, gu guigira khaŇč t…®gap nta havhari guma ma. Nde ntige vh…®ra mba t…®vara mbui.
\v 4 \x - \xo 22:4 \xt FG 22.19; 26.9-11; Fi 3.6; 1 T 1.13\x*\x - \xo 22:4 \xt FG 8.3\x*Gu Zisas khoth…®gap ana nzuai t…®vi z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, gu mben farfav mbari shogim, mbe vh…®zim, mbari gu shenin mbe suira gu hari kav, mbe ndia vov b…®na sui.
\v 5 \x - \xo 22:5 \xt FG 9.2\x*Gu mba t…®va mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men rotu gari guman pan gum mba buaadegi gumgi, mbe na kaŇčgi, mbe na bun nde suanga. Mbe gavi khergiap, mben gumgi mbari, mbe Damaskusan ki. Mbe mba gavi khergiap, mbe ndi mbav na bun mbe nzuai. Gu Damaskusan naaŇčv mba Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui nt…®…®ri, gu mben suig…®v mbe ndiv Zerusareman zir…®rim, kha gumgi bak…®vi ne suaŇčv muumbara mbat…®gar mben muuŇčgirga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui ne bun mbe nzuai.
\r Farasegi Gumgi 9.3-19; 26.12-18
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 22:6 \xt FG 9.3; 26.12-13\x*Por mba bunin mbe nzuav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúGu mba gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav Damaskusan ndai. Gu nda vov, Damaskusan han mbaim, ra vov ph…®…®Ňč han mbai. Gu ndaim, vhava bak…® mbe tor vhekvhegi fara muuŇčgiap buivar kega zera zav guigira na sh…®rigi.
\v 7 Mba vhava Ňčaar na sh…®rigim, gu won hos thav k…®gira n…®…®aŇč ndarav, mbaram guma kamthooŇč mbe mbararagim, ana kha nzambaran na muuŇčgi, ‚ÄėSor, Sor, ndu thaŇč nzuav nan farfagi?‚Äô
\v 8 Ana maaŇč nzuaim, gu khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me, ndu the?‚Äô Gu maaŇč nzuaim, ana khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėGu Nasaret guma Zisas, ndu nan farfagi.‚Äô
\v 9 Mba na phorga ndai gumgi, mbe mba vhava gari. Mbe mba na nzuai guma, mbe ana kamthooŇč mbararagi fhu.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúAna maaŇč na nzuaim, gu thav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me, gu ntigem ram muuŇčrie?‚Äô Guma Bak…®me khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu khavgip Damaskus Ňčgu bak…®men vhen Ňčgir…®ri. Guma the maam, gu muun zav ndun farasarigi Ňčaari, ana za nta bun ndu suanga.‚Äô
\v 11 Mba buivar kega zerav na sh…®rigi vhavar Ňčaar, ana guigira havhargi. Ana na r…®mani ga muuŇčgim, gu ram muuŇčgip gan…®rie? MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, na phorga vui gumgi, mbe nan harar suirav, nan kov Damaskus Ňčgun vhen vergi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 22:12 \xt FG 9.17; 10.22; 1 T 3.7\x*‚ÄúMbe nan kov Damaskusan vergim, guma mbe maaŇč ki. Mba guma z…®, Ananaias. Ana guigira Fhe Bak…®men piin kav, Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi guigira nta z…®n vui guma ma. Mba Damaskusan ki ZudaiŇč, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėAna guman vhuuŇč ma.‚Äô
\v 13 Ana zav, na han th…®gap, khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNan fek, Sor, ndun r…®mani taagip nzerav gan…®ri.‚Äô Ana maaŇč na nzuai tugera, nan r…®mani taagia nzerigim, gu ana gari.
\v 14 \x - \xo 22:14 \xt FG 9.15; 1 Ko 9.1; 11.23; Ga 1.12\x*Gu ana garim, ana khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNzan nz…®gir Fhe Bak…®me, ana ndun farasarigi. Ndu anan vuzvugi kaŇčgirga, ndu vh…®ra ana Ňäaara Guman Ňäaar, ndu ana gan…®v, ndu vh…®ra ana won kamthoon suanga buni, ndu nta mbarararga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 22:15 \xt FG 23.11; 26.16\x*Ndu mba garav mbararagi buni gum bigi, ndu za nta bun za kha gumgi gu mbigi ga suanga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16 \xt FG 2.21; 9.11; 9.18; Ro 10.13; Hi 10.22\x*Ndu mba Ňčaarar muunga, ndu ntige thag…®nen rarga ki? Ndu khavgip khaŇč suaŇč, ‚ÄúZisas nan korar muuŇč.‚ÄĚ Ndu maaŇč suaŇčv, ana z…®n panan ruagirim, ana ndu fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta ruagirim, nta vh…®zgirga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me Por ga sarigim, ana vov harigi Ňčguir Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 17-18 \x - \xo 22:17-18 \xt FG 9.29-30\x*Por maaŇč nzua vov, khaŇč mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. ‚ÄúGu zumgum taagia zav Zerusareman ndav, gu vov Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen vergap, Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav kav, gu r…®ma kui fhara muuŇčgiap Guma Bak…®me gangi. Gu ana garim, ana khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu vhemkora Zerusarem thav khavgi Ňčg…®ri. Ndu kha Ňčgu bak…®mera nan buni vhuuiŇč bun suanga, kha gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ndu khoth…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô
\v 19 \x - \xo 22:19 \xt FG 8.3; 22.4; 26.9-11\x*Ana maaŇč na nzuaim, gu nduara khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGuma Bak…®me, mbe na kaŇčgi. Gura fhum Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi pheni ga ruav, ndu khoth…®gap ndu z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, gu mbe suigav, mbe ndia zav b…®na suav, hor mbat…®gar mbe mbuim, mbe na kaŇčgi.
\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt FG 7.58; 8.1\x*Gu vh…®ra, mbe ndun buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai guma Stiven, gu vh…®ra th…®ga mbe garim, mbe na n…®mara ana shogim, ana rimgim, gura khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúMbe mba t…®var ana muuŇčgi, ne nzerara‚ÄĚ. Gu nen mbe nzuav, gu nduara mba ana shogi ana rimgi gumgir shagir kirav kegi.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 22:21 \xt FG 9.15; 13.2; 13.46; Ga 1.15-16; 1 T 2.7\x*Gu maaŇč nzuaim, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu Ňčg…®, gu ndu sararim, ndu harigi Ňčguir samra Ňčg…®g…®rga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Rom guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 22:22 \xt FG 21.36\x*Por mba buni nzua vov, mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuaim, mba ZudaiŇč ne mbararagiap, mbe wom Por buni mbararargeŇč thagi. Mbe thav, kama bak…®mera kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúAna shogirim, ana rimik! Mba khesharigi guma, ana kha nuianan k…® thari. Ana vh…®ra Ňčamk…®rga fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 Mbe ne nzuav tamtam kaava nz…®…®v, wari wo ruga hav shari fhavi shari, mbe nta zorav nta sim, nta k…®zr…®ga vov tamtam mbur rim, mbe vh…®ra vher…®na dogap, ana fuav vu sui. Mbe mba t…®va mbui ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mbe Por suaŇčgi buneŇč vuzvugi fhu.
\v 24 Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari, ana mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuaim, mbe Por ndigap, wari won phena vhen vergi. Mbe ana ndiga wari won phena vhen vergim, mbe gari guman panan vhari phiv…®gan Por khar…® zav mbe nzuai. Ana khueŇč kaŇčgi zav, kha gumgi gu mbigi thag…®na big…®na n…®…®eŇč ga nzuav kh…®r…®v Porar kaav, ana tuarahuri.
\v 25 \x - \xo 22:25 \xt FG 16.37\x*Mbe maaŇč Poran muuŇčv ana harani gu suani k…®r za mbui. Por garim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pan ana hara th…®gi. Por mbara kha nzambaren ana muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúEe, nzan t…®v ram nzuai? Ana khaŇč nzuaire, nza kha khesharigi t…®var Rom guman muunga, ne nzerigi, o fhu? Nde vh…®ra kha t…®var na muun za mbui. Nde na nzuav suaŇčgiap, fhura phiv…®gan na khar…® za mbui fhuvara. Nde mba t…®var muun za mbui, ne nzerigi, o?‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 22:25 \ft Ndu FG 16.37 gan…®ri. Mbe RomiŇč, mben t…®va mueŇč khaŇč nzuai, mben t…®v guigira havhargia khaŇč nzuai, mbe fhura sh…®sh…®g…®p phiv…®gar Rom guma the khargirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. \f*
\p 
\v 26 Por mba nzambaren mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pana muuŇčgim, ana mbaram vov, nen mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari ga nzuav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu ntige ram muuŇčrie? Mbu guma, ana Rom guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Ana ne suaŇčgim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari zav khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu na suaŇč. Ndu Rom guma, ee?‚ÄĚ Ana ne nzuaim, Por khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúAhaŇč.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Por maaŇč nzuaim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu won Ňčk…®…®a vh…®rve guarira wo nzuav vhezgiap, gu ntigem Rom guma ki.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Por khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu maaŇč muuŇčgi fhuvara. Gu nan ndia Rom guma ma. Gu vh…®ra Rom guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 29 \x - \xo 22:29 \xt FG 16.38\x*Por maaŇč suaŇčgim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ana nzav, phiv…®gar ana khar…® za mbuav, mbe ne mbararagiap, mbe vhemkora sh…®va vergap ana thagi. Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari vh…®ra Por kaŇčgi, ana Rom guma ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana vh…®ra rivgi. Ana khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana nzuaim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi shenin Por kegi.
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin Zudain buaadegi gumgi ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 30 Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari rivgiap, ana vh…®ra tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgi za mbui, Por thag…®na big…®na mbat…®ga goreŇčra muuŇčgim, kha ZudaiŇč ana nzuav nzuai. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba m…®timanera ana Por fh…®rgim, ana b…®na thav k…®rar h…®gi. Ana mbaram Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani gum za mba Zudain buaadegi gumgir panin kamgim, mbe zav wari fugi. Mbe zav wari fugim, ana mbaram Porar kov mbe han zerav, ana nzuaim, ana vov, mbe n…®man th…®gi.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 23:1 \xt FG 24.16; 1 Ko 4.4; 2 Ko 1.12; 2 T 1.3\x*Por mbe n…®man th…®gap, mbaram purara mba buaadegi gumgir pani garav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nan fegi, gu Fhe Bak…®me r…®mani n…®ma ruav, gu won ndava vhee kaŇčgi. Gu ana n…®man mbui t…®vi, nta nzerara zav gu ntige khar th…®gi. Gu wo kaŇčgi, gu big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi fhu.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 \x - \xo 23:2 \xt 1 Kin 22.24; Jer 20.2; Zo 18.22-23\x*Por maaŇč nzuaim, mba Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan Ananaias, ana khaŇč mba Por han thivgi gumgi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde ana th…®ri phavik.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt Wkp 19.35; Lo 25.1-2; Mt 23.27-28; Zo 7.51\x*Ana maaŇč nzuaim, Por khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me ndura shogirga! Ndu khaŇč muuŇčgi, ndu b…®na mbat…®k ma. Mbe pena hurar ana h…®vgi, ndu mba fara muuŇčgi. Mbe pena hurar ana h…®vgirim, gumgi mba ana kh…®nan ki big…®na mbat…®ga gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ndu kha Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi ga nzuav na nzuav nzuav, za khar perav ki. Gu ndu nzuai, ndu nduara Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi ph…®rgiap mbe nzuaim, mbe na shogi.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 23:3 \ft Wok Pris 19.15 khaŇč nzuai, mba buni mbararagi gumgi, mbe t…®var vhuuŇčra z…®n Ňčg…®p, mbe buni mbararari. Por mba t…®va nt…®r…®gap, khaŇč mba Fhe Bak…®me phena Ňčgari guman pana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu nduara mba t…®va ph…®rgi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 4 Por ne ana nzuaim, gumgi mbari Por han thivgia kav ne mbararagiap, kha nzambaren Por ga muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúNdu Fhe Bak…®men rotu gari guman pan, ndu buna mbat…®gen ana nzuaire?‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5 \xt Kis 22.28\x*Mbe mba nzambaren Por ga muuŇčgim, Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, gu mba guma Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pan ki ne kaŇčgi fhuvara. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap pham muuŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėNde won guman pan, nde buni mbat…®gir ana suaŇč thari.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6 \xt Mt 22.23; Mk 12.18; Ru 20.27; FG 4.2; 24.15; 24.21; 26.5; Fi 3.5\x*Por khaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana kaŇčgi, mba buaadegi gumgi mbari, mbe SadusiŇč gumgi ma. Mbe mbari, mbe FherasiŇč ma. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap mba buaadegi gumgir k…®…®av khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, gu Fherasi guma ma, gu Fherasin kam ma. Gu khueŇč khoth…®gi, guma rimgip, zumgum taagi khavgirga. Mbe ntigem mba big…®na n…®…®eŇčra nzuav na nzuav nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Por mba kameŇč suaŇčgim, mba SadusiŇč gu FherasiŇč ne nzuav wari dai kama bak…®me mbe r…®gar h…®gim, mba phok r…®g…®ra wari sh…®rigi.
\v 8 Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe SadusiŇč khaŇč nzuai nt…®…®ri ma, ‚ÄúGuma rimgi taagia khavi fhu.‚ÄĚ Mbe vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me enseri ki fhu, vh…®ra ntuu ki fhu.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, mbe FherasiŇč, mbe mba bigi khoth…®gi, mba bigi ki.
\v 9 \x - \xo 23:9 \xt FG 5.39; 22.7; 22.17-18; 25.25\x*Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ne nzuav kh…®r…®v kaav nzuai. Mba ZudaiŇč t…®vi kaŇčgi gumgi mbari, mbe vh…®ra Fherasi gumgi ma. Mbe th…®vgia khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza kha guma garim, ana big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi fhuvara. Ana Ňčina the ana suaŇčgim, ana nzuai o, Fhe Bak…®me enser the ana suaŇčgim, ana nzuai thi?‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Mbe mba t…®va mbuim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari mbe garim, mba FherasiŇč gu SadusiŇč wari dai, ntarar kam guigira vov k…®vgim, ana rivgiap, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ‚ÄúKheiŇč muuŇčv k…®v Por suig…®v, ana Ňčg…®v warir n…®…®Ňčrim, ana karireg…®p, rimgirga.‚ÄĚ Ana mba nd…®knd…®ga muuŇčgia thav, khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Ňčgir…®p ZudaiŇč farve t…®n Por ndig…®p, nde wo phena vhen Ňčgirg…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 23:11 \xt FG 18.9; 19.21; 25.11; 27.23-24; 28.16-23\x*Mbe Por ndiga wari wo phenan vugim, mba raar kegap, mba maan kegap, m…®n thugim, mba raar kegap, maan Fhe Bak…®me Por han th…®gap khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu th…®g…® havhargiri, ndu r…®v…® thari. Ndu khaŇč t…®gap Zerusareman na buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčgi. Ndu mba t…®vara ndu Roman na buni vhuuiŇč bun suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 ZudaiŇč Por shogirim, ana r…®m…®n zav kama shogi.
\p 
\v 12 Mba maan m…®n thugim, ZudaiŇč mbari wari fugap, Por shogirim, ana r…®m…®nga kama shogi. Mbe kama havhara nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza guigira nzuai, kha vun ki Fhe Bak…®me nza kaŇčgi, nza guigira Por shogirim, ana rimgirga, nza ntigem gura mban mbeg…®rga fhu. Nza Por shogirim, ana rimgirga, nza za mban mb…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 13 Mbe kameŇč suaŇčgi ZudaiŇč, mben vh…®rve 40 kambarigi.
\v 14 Mba gumgi, mbe vov, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani gum mba Zudain gumgir pani han vov, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNza kama havharar khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNza gura mban mbeg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nza khara muuŇčgip k…®v, Por shogirim, ana rimgirim, nza mban mb…®rga.‚Äô
\v 15 \x - \xo 23:15 \xt FG 25.3\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde mba buaadegi gumgir panin kov, nde kama ndim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari ndi mbararim, ana Porar kov, nde han zir…®ri. Nde ana guig…®p khaŇč ana suaŇčri, ‚ÄėNza Por tuituig…®p suaŇčgi buni mbari nd…®…®riveŇč kaŇčgi zav, anan nzan za mbui.‚Äô Nza ana rarg…® k…®rga. Ana z…®v nden h…®r saŇč muunga, nza za ana shogirim, ana rimgirga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Mbe maaŇč nzuaim, Por mbiga h…®r…®…®n kam, ana kav, mbe ana muun za nzuai kameŇč, ana ne mbararagi. Ana ne mbararagiap, mbaram vov, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ki phenan vugap, ne bun Por ga suaŇčgi.
\v 17 Por ne mbararagiap, mbaram mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pana mben kamgim, ana ana han zim, ana khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu kha guman kaman kuv, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari han Ňčg…®ri. Ana buna muen ana suan za mbui.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Por nen ana suaŇčgim, ana mba guman kaman kov, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari han vov khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúMba phena t…®vanen ki guma, Por, nan kamgia khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu kha guman kaman kuv, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari han Ňčg…®ri. Ana ana suanga buna mueŇč ki.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Ana maaŇč ana suaŇčgim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari mbaram mba guman kama harar suirav, ana kov mani gaar vugi. Mani gaar vugap nuanira kav, ana mba guman kaman nzav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu thag…®na bunen na suan za mbui?‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Ana maaŇč ana nzuaim, mba guman kama mbaram khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúMbe ZudaiŇč kama shogiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėMbe ndun nzararim, ndu gurmaŇčgip Porar kov mba buaadegi gumgir panin han Ňčgir…®ri.‚Äô Mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNza ana guig…®p khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúNza tuituigip Por kaŇčgi saŇčv ana nzanga.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô
\v 21 Mbe maaŇč ndu suanga, ndu mbe buni mbarara thari. Mbe gumgi mbari, mbe vh…®rve 40 kambarigi. Mbe kama havharar khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNza mban mbeg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara, nza Por shogirim, ana rimgirga, nza za mban mb…®rga.‚Äô Mbe ne suaŇčgiap nen ndu rarga mbur ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 Mba guman kam nen mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari ga suaŇčgim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pana vhari kama havharar khaŇč mba guman kama nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Ňčg…®p, khaŇč harigi guma the suaŇč thari, gu mba bigeŇč bun ana suaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mbe Por ga sarigim, ana Ňčgui gari guman panan vhari Feriks han vui.
\p 
\v 23 Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pana manin kamgim, mani ana han zim, ana khaŇč mani ga nzuai, ‚ÄúŇäko Ňčg…®p, 200 ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ndig…®p, mbaram 70 ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi thari phorg…® ndigiri, mbe hozi ndigiri. Ňäko vh…®ra harigi 200 ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi thari phorg…® ndigiri, mbe fugi suigiri. Ňäko mbe bevaheg…®p, nde 9 kirok maan Sisarian Ňčgir…®ri.
\v 24 Nde vh…®ra Por hozi bevaheg…®p, ana kuv, nde ruru vhuuŇčra muuŇčv, Ňčgir…®p Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari Feriks han Ňčgirg…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\v 25 Mbe Ňčgir…® za mbuim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari gava kherav khaŇč nzuai,
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄúGu Krodius Risias, gu kha gava khergiap, Ňčgui gari guman panan vhari Feriks ndi mbai. Raara vhuuŇč.
\v 27 \x - \xo 23:27 \xt FG 21.30-33; 22.25-27; 24.7\x*Mbe ZudaiŇč kha guman suirav, ana shogiri ana r…®m…®n za mbui. Gu mbararagi, mbe khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėKha guma, ana Rom guma ma.‚Äô Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap won ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vir kov vov, nza mbe t…®n ana ndigi.
\v 28 \x - \xo 23:28 \xt FG 22.30\x*Gu mbe ana sav, ana nzuai buna n…®…®eŇč kaŇčgi zav, ana kov, mben buaadegi gumgir pani han vugap, mben nzarigi.
\v 29 \x - \xo 23:29 \xt FG 18.14-15; 25.19; 26.31\x*Gu mben nzarigim, mbe khaŇč nzuai, mbe won t…®vira nzuav ana nzuai. Mbe guigira ana r…®m…®nga big…®na guara thueŇč gangia nzuav kake, nza ana shogi, ana r…®…®e o, nza ana ndi b…®na sue.
\v 30 \x - \xo 23:30 \xt FG 23.20; 24.5-8\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ntige mbararagim, mbe mba guma shogirim, ana r…®m…® zav nimra kama shogi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap vhemkora ana sarigim, ana ndu han mbar veri. Ana ndu han mbar verim, gu mba ana sav ana nzuav nzuai gumgi, gu mbe suaŇčgi. Mbe Ňčgir…®p ndu n…®man mba ana sav ana nzuav nzuai buni, mbe ntan ana suaŇčrim, ndu mbe ana nzuav nzuai buni kaŇčgirga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman panan vhari maaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga suaŇčgim, mbe ana kameŇč z…®n vov, mba maaŇčra Porar kov Antipatris Ňčgu bak…®men veri.
\v 32 Mbe vergap, mba m…®timanera mba hozi ga piigiap vergi ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi, mbe Porar kov Sisaria Ňčgu bak…®men vergi. Mbe Porar ko verim, mba harigi ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi, mbe taagiap Zerusareman wari wo phenan ndai.
\v 33 Mba hozi ga piigiap ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi, mbe Porar ko vera Sisarian h…®gap, mbaram mba gava ndiga vov, mba Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari ga nd…®…®v, vh…®ra Porar ko vov, ana n…®man thivgi.
\v 34 Por mba Ňčgui gari guman panan vhari n…®ma th…®gim, ana mbaram mba gava gangiap, kha nzambaran Por ga muuŇčgi. ‚ÄúNdu maaŇčgi fhaiŇč guma?‚ÄĚ Por ana Ňčgarkarav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Sirisia guma ma.‚ÄĚ
\v 35 Por maaŇč nzuaim, Ňčgui gari guman panan vhari khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKha bunin ndu sav ndu nzuai gumgi, mbe z…®v khaŇč heg…®rga, gu ndu buni mbarararga.‚ÄĚ Ana ne suaŇčgiap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde Por ndim Ňčgui gari guman pana Herot muuŇčgi phena kh…®ngiri.‚ÄĚ
\c 24
\s1 ZudaiŇč gumgir pani Por ga nzuav nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Por Sisariara kim, meeŇčth…®gi rari vh…®zgim, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari guman pana Ananaias, mba Zudain gumgir pani gum, Romin t…®vi kaŇčgi guma Terturusan kov, mbe Sisarian zergi. Mbe zergap, Por ga nzuav suanga buneŇč bun Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari ga nzuai.
\v 2 Mbe nen Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari ga suaŇčgim, ana mbaram Porar kamgim, ana za th…®gi. Ana za th…®gim, Terturus mbaram bunin ana sav ana nzuav nzuai. Ana khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGumana rum Feriks, ndu guigira nzan kurigim, nza mpirmpir…®ga vhuuŇčra muuŇčgia kim, ntara bak…® the nza fhain h…®gi fhu. Ndu vh…®ra won nd…®knd…®gar vhuuŇč nza nt…®…®rir kurav, mba fhum mbat…®gi bigi, ndu nta muuŇčgim, nta ntige nzerigi.
\v 3 Guman rum Feriks, nza za wo fhain mba bigi gangiap, nzan ndavi guigira nzerigim, nza guigira ne nzuav ndun ndikndigi.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúGu vh…®ra buni vh…®rver ndu suaŇč ndu suirav tuga mpeen k…®rga fhuvara. Gu khueŇč nzuav ndun nzai, ndu nzan korar muuŇčgip, nzan buna t…®veŇčra mbarararga.
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5 \xt FG 6.13; 16.20; 17.6; 21.28; 1 Pi 2.12; 2.15\x*Nza kha guma garim, ana simt…®gi vh…®rve khavi. Ana za kha nuianan ki ZudaiŇč, ana za mbe phorga ntari khavi guma ma. Ana maaŇč mbuav, ana vh…®ra mba nza thav wari sh…®rav ki nt…®…®ri, mbe kha z…®n mbe r…®gi, NasaretiŇč. Ana mben guman pan ma.
\v 6-8 \x - \xo 24:6-8 \xt FG 21.28-30\x*Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Phena muuŇčgirim, ana Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzaŇčnzaŇč zav mbui. Ana maaŇč mbuim, nza ana suirigi. Ndu ntigem, ndu nduara anan nzarim, ana mba muuŇčgi bigi, ana nduara nta bun ndu suaŇčgirim, ndu kaŇčgirga, nza ana nzuav nzuai buni, nta guigira.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 24:6-8 \ft Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč kaŇčgiap, nta kheri gumgi mbari, mbe khaŇč nzuai, harigi kama mueŇč phorgap kha vezar ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza won t…®vira nzuav, ana nzuav nzuai. Nza ana nzuav nzuaim, Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari Risias won ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vir kov, zav nza tamtam nza daaga suav, nzan farve t…®n ana ndigi. Risias ana ndigap khaŇč nzuai, kha guma ga suaŇčv suangeŇč vuzvugi gumgi, mbe z…®n ndu phorg…®v ana suaŇčv suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 9 Terturus ne nzuaim, mbe ZudaiŇč vh…®ra anan kurav, nen Por ga sav, ana nzuai. Mbe za khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba buni, nta za guigira buni guari ma.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun Feriks ga nzuai.
\p 
\v 10 Terturus mba buni suaŇčgim, mba Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari mba buni mbararagiap, mbaram won farve n…®…®Ňčkui, ana Por suangeŇč nzuav, ana maaŇč wo farve ga mbui. Ana maaŇč wo farve ga muuŇčgim, Por ana farve gangiap, mbaram kama hegap, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu kaŇčgi, ndu mpari vh…®rvera ndu kha gumgi gu mbigi buni ndi t…®gar mbai guman pan ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nan ndava vhee guigira ndu buni ŇčgarkargeŇč vuzvugi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 24:11 \xt FG 21.17; 21.26; 24.17\x*Ndu tamtam mben nzanga, ndu khueŇč kaŇčgirga, gu ph…®k bavira raa phunini vov vh…®zgi, gu mba tugivigen, gu rotur muun zav Zerusareman ndagi.
\v 12 Gu vugim, ZudaiŇč na garim, gu Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen, gu Zuda guma the phorga nzuav, ana dav, ana vhegi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra na garim, gu gumgi gu mbigi thari, gu Fhe Bak…®me buni mbararagi phena vhen phok the khavgi fhu. Gu vh…®ra kha Ňčgu bak…®me vhen gumgi gu mbigi thari fugap, phok the khavgi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara!
\v 13 Mbe ntigem na nzuav nzuai buni, nta guigira buni fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra mbar na sav na nzuai buni, mbe gu muuŇčgi tuav guara thueŇč kh…®varga, mbe nzuai buni nta guigira buni ma.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14 \xt FG 24.5; 26.22; 28.23; 2 T 1.3\x*‚ÄúGuigira buneŇč khare. Mba Zisas khoth…®gav ana z…®n vui tuav, mbe kha suambarar ana mbui, ‚Äėharigi nt…®…®ri ma.‚Äô Gu tuav z…®n vov, gu nza won nz…®gir Fhe Bak…®me, gu ara rotu mbui. Gu mba Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi, gu za nta khoth…®gap, gu vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi fhum khergi buni, gu vh…®ra za nta khoth…®g…®vra ki.
\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Dan 12.2; Zo 5.28-29; FG 23.6; 26.6-7; 28.20\x*Gu nta khoth…®gap, gu Fhe Bak…®me taagip mba vh…®zgi gumgi gu mbigi khav…®rgane, gu nen rarga ki. Ana t…®vir vhuuiŇč muuŇčgi gumgi gu mbigi, mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgi gumgi gu mbigi, ana za taagi mbe khavgirga. Mbe vh…®ra ne nzuav Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gap, ana rarga wari ki.
\v 16 \x - \xo 24:16 \xt FG 23.1\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap won ndava havhargiap ki. Gu big…®na mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇč thav, gu zazera nzerara Fhe Bak…®me n…®man kav, gu vh…®ra kha gumgi gu mbigi n…®man ki.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17 \xt FG 11.29-30; 20.16; Ro 15.25-26; 2 Ko 8.4; Ga 2.10\x*\x - \xo 24:17 \xt FG 21.17-28\x*‚ÄúGu mpari mbarir harigi Ňčguir kegap, zumgum gu taagia wo nt…®…®ri han z…®gi. Gu Ňčk…®…®a gu bigi mbari ndiga zav bigi sosuagi gumgi mbarir kurkurav, gu vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me nzuav shama mbui bigi mbari ndiga z…®gi.
\v 18 Gu mba bigi ndigip, Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen Ňčgir…®v, gu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgara zav mbui t…®v, gu fharav ne muuŇčgiap, gu zumgum mba bigi ndiga vov Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen verav, ana nzuav shama muuŇčgi. Gu mba Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen kim, mbe na gari, gu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarav, gu ki. Gu mba tugen gumgi vh…®rve na phorga kegi fhu, vh…®ra mba tugen gumgi thari kh…®kh…®m bak…® the muuŇčgi fhu. \f b \fr 24:18 \ft Ves 6 khaŇč nzuai, Por Fhe Bak…®me phena muuŇčgirim, ana Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nzaŇčnzaŇč za mbui. Por mbe maaŇč ana nzuai, ne Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgarav, gu ana phena guara vhen vergi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 24:19 \xt FG 23.30; 25.16; 2 T 1.15\x*‚ÄúMba tugen Esia fhain kega ndagi ZudaiŇč, mbe fhura zav na suirigi. Mba nan suirigi gumgi, mbe kamen nan k…®v, mbe nduarira ntige z…®v, ndu n…®ma thivgip, na suaŇčv suaŇčri.
\v 20 Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip zeg…®rga fhu, gu fhum mben buaadegi gumgi phorga nzuai, mbe na buni mbararagi. Gu pham buna thueŇč suaŇčgirim, mbe nen ndu suanga. Mbe nen ndu suaŇčv, gu mba muuŇčgi big…®na mbat…®geŇč, mbe nen ndu suaŇčri.
\v 21 \x - \xo 24:21 \xt FG 23.6; 28.20\x*Gu buna bueŇčra suaŇčgim, mbe nen ndikndigi fhu. Gu mben r…®gar th…®gap, kaav khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėGu khueŇč khoth…®gi, guma rimgip, taagia khav…®rga. Mbe ntige nera nzuav na ndigap, nde wo buni nzuai Ňčanen z…®gap, na nzuav nzuai.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 24:22 \xt FG 23.26\x*Por mba buni nzuaim, Feriks nta mbararagi. Feriks, ana vh…®ra gumgi gu mbigi Zisas khoth…®gav ana z…®n vui tuav, ana vh…®ra ana kaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Por buni suaŇčgia thugim, Feriks mbaram khaŇč ZudaiŇč ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde rarg…®ri.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúMba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pana vhari Risias garari. Ana zirg…®rim, gu za nde buneŇč ndi th…®gar maanga.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 \x - \xo 24:23 \xt FG 27.3; 28.16; 28.30\x*Ana mbe suaŇčgiap khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari guman pana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu Por ndi b…®na kh…®ngiri, ndu big…®na thuen ana muuŇč thari. Ndu vh…®ra ana k…®vntogi bigir ana n…®…®n saŇč muuŇčrim, nde mbe th…®v…® thari.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Feriks Por ndi b…®na kh…®ngim, ana b…®nan kim, mpari mpuveni vh…®zgi.
\p 
\v 24 Rari mbari vh…®zgim, Feriks won muuŇč Drusiran kov, mani zi. Drusira, ana Zudar mbik ma. Mani zav, Feriks Porar kamgim, ana zim, ana anan buni mbari mbararagi. Por Zisas Krais khoth…®g…®rga buni mbarir ana phorga nzuai.
\v 25 Por ana phorga nzuav, t…®vir vhuuin muunga bunin ana nzuav, guma vh…®ra tuituigip won k…®r…® t…®vi gu bigi gan…®nganen ana phorga nzuav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me zumgum nza muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv nza suangane phorga ana nzuai. Ana nen Feriks ga nzuaim, Feriks ne mbararagiap, rivgi. Ana rivgiap, khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu ntige Ňčg…®ri! Gu zumgum tuk k…®rga, gu taagip ndu suaŇčv kama ndi maanga.‚ÄĚ
\v 26 Feriks maaŇč Por ga nzuav, ana vh…®ra kha nd…®knd…®gar Por ga mbuav, ana rarga ki. Por ana raaŇč sh…®v, Ňčk…®…®a tharir ana n…®…®Ňčgirim, ana fhura ana fh…®rgirim, ana b…®na thav, Ňčg…®g…®rga. Feriks mba nd…®knd…®gar Por ga mbuav, ana tugi vh…®rvera zav Porar kaaim, ana zav ana phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 24:27 \xt FG 25.9; 25.14\x*Ana maaŇč mbuav kim, mpari mpoveni vh…®zgim, Porsius Festus Feriks Ňčana ndigap, Zudia fhaiŇč gari guman pana vhari ki. Mba tugen, Feriks ZudaiŇč ana ndikndig…®r zav, ana Por th…®vigim, ana b…®nara ki.
\c 25
\s1 Sisar Por buni mbarararga.
\p 
\v 1 Mba tugen Feriks vh…®zgim, Festus ana Ňčana ndigap, Zudia fhaiŇč gari guman pana vhari ki. Ana Feriks Ňčana ndigap, raa phunini khegene vh…®zgim, ana Sisaria Ňčgu bak…®me thav Zerusareman ndai.
\v 2 \x - \xo 25:2 \xt FG 23.12; 23.15; 24.1; 25.15\x*Festus Zerusareman ndagim, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani gum Zudain gumgir pani, mbe zav, ana han zegap, buni mbarir Por ga sav ana nzuav Festus phorga nzuai. Mbe khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap khaŇč Festus ga nzuai,
\v 3 ‚ÄúNdu guigira nzan kurav, mba guma ga sararim, ana Zerusareman naaŇčri.‚ÄĚ Mbe mba kamen ana nzuai ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Mbe kama shogiap gumgi mbari ga suaŇčgi, mbe tuavar zomzorgi k…®v, Por z…®v naaŇčrim, mbe tuavar ana shogirim, ana rimgirga.
\v 4 Mbe maaŇč Festus ga nzuaim, Festus mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúPor Sisarian phena t…®vanen ki. Gu tuga t…®vanera khaŇč keg…®p, gu nduara Sisarian Ňčgir…®rga.
\v 5 Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip Ňčgir…®rim, nden gumgir pani na phorg…®p Ňčgir…®rga. Mbe Ňčgir…®p, mba guma ana big…®n mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgirim, mbe maaŇč ana suaŇčv suanga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Festus maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbe phorga ki s…®garath…®gi o ph…®kth…®gi rari vh…®zgim, ana zumgum Sisarian vergi. Ana vergap, m…®timanera ana vov, buni mbararagi phena perav mbe nzuaim, mbe Porar kov ana han zi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 25:7 \xt FG 24.5-6; 24.13\x*Mbe Porar kov ana han z…®gim, mba Zerusareman kegap zergi ZudaiŇč, mbe zav, ana han thivgi. Mbe ana han thivgiap buni vh…®rvera Por ga sav ana nzuai. Mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ana mbark…®rga mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira muuŇčgi. Mbe maaŇč ana nzuav, ana muuŇčgi t…®va mbat…®k thueŇč, mbe ne fara sarav tuituigia Festus kh…®vav, khaŇč ana nzuai fhu, nza nzuai buni nta guigira buni guari ma. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 8 \x - \xo 25:8 \xt FG 24.12; 28.17\x*Mbe mba bunin Por ga sav ana suaŇčgia thugim, Por mbaram mbe buni Ňčgarkarav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu t…®va mbat…®k thueŇč muuŇčgi fhu. Gu ZudaiŇč t…®va thueŇč ph…®rgi fhu. Gu vh…®ra t…®va mbat…®ga thuen Fhe Bak…®me Phena muuŇčgi fhu. Gu vh…®ra t…®va mbat…®ga thuen Sisar muuŇčgi fhu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 25:9 \xt FG 24.27; 25.20\x*Por maaŇč nzuaim, Festus ZudaiŇč ana ndikndig…® zav, ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap h…®gap, kha nzambaren Por ga muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúNdu Zerusareman naaŇčv wo buni suangeŇč vuzvugi thi? Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgirga, gu vh…®ra naaŇčv Zerusareman ndu buni mbarararga.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Festus mba nzambarer Por ga muuŇčgim, Por thav khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGu ntige kha th…®gi phen, ana Sisar wo buni mbararagi phen ma. Mbe kha phenara na buni mbarararga. Ndu kaŇčgi, gu big…®na mbat…®ga thuen ZudaiŇč ga muuŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 11 \x - \xo 25:11 \xt FG 23.11; 23.29; 25.25; 26.31-32; 28.19\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip r…®m…®nga big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgip, gu ne suaŇčv rimgirga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbe khar na sav na nzuav nzuai buni, nta guigira buni guari fhuvara, guma the fhura na ndim, mbe farve kh…®ngirga fhu. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, gu nduara Sisar han Ňčg…®rga, ana na buni mbarararga.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 25:11 \ft Romin t…®v khaŇč nzuai, Rom guma the, mbe ana suaŇčv suanga, ana mbe phorg…®v wo suaŇčv suanga, mbe tuituigiap ana buni mbararagi fhu. Ana mbe phorg…® suaŇčrim, mbe ana kh…®rarga, Sisar ana buni mbararga. Sisar, ana Roman Ňčguive, ana za nta gari guman pan ma. \f*
\p 
\v 12 Por maaŇč suaŇčgim, Festus mbaram vov, nd…®knd…®gar wo nd…®…®i gumgi, ana mbe phorga suaŇčgia thugap, zumgum taagia zav khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu khueŇč vuzvugi, ndu Sisar han Ňčg…®ri, ana ndu buni mbarararga. Ndu ne vuzvugip, ndu Sisar han Ňčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Festus Por ga nzuav Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 13 Festus mba suambarar Por ga muuŇčgim, zumgum rari mbari vh…®zgim, Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa won mbiga h…®r…®…®Ňč Bernaisi, mani Festus gan…®v, ana ndikndig…®p, ana harar suig…® zav Sisarian zergi. \f b \fr 25:13 \ft Ňägui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, ana ndia Herot, ana fhum Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan kav, ana Zon fega Zems shogim ana rimgi. Ndu Farasarigi Gumgi 12 gan…®ri. \f*
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 25:14 \xt FG 24.27\x*Mani zergap, rari vh…®rvera Sisarian k…®r za mbui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Festus mbaram Por suaŇčgi kamen mba Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pana nzuai. Ana khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma mbe, Feriks fhum Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari kav, ana ana ndi b…®na kh…®ngi. Mba guma mbara muuŇčgiap b…®nan khar ki.
\v 15 Gu nda vov Zerusareman kim, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani gum mba Zudain gumgir pani, mbe buni mbarir ana sav, ana nzuav na suaŇčgi. Mbe khueŇč vuzvugiap khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėGu khaŇč suanga, ana big…®na mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi. Gu khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga suanga, ‚ÄúAna r…®m…®nga.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô
\v 16 Mbe mba suambarar na mbuim, gu mbe Ňčgarkarav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėNza RomiŇč, nzan t…®v khaŇč muuŇčgia ki. Nza fhura r…®m…®n saŇčv guma, the suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Guma big…®na mbat…®geŇč muuŇčgi, ana fharav, mba ana nzuav nzuai guma ana ana phorg…®p, mani wo buni suaŇčrim, guman pan mani buni mbararagirga.‚Äô
\p 
\v 17 ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu taagiap Sisarian zerim, mba gumgi na phorga zergi. Mbe zergim, gu mbe nzuaim, mbe rarga kegi fhuvara. Mbe zergap, m…®timanera gu vov buni mbararagi phena perav nzuaim, mbe mba guman kov, na han z…®gi.
\v 18 Mbe ana kov na han z…®gim, mba ana nzuav nzuai gumgi, mbe za zav, ana han thivgi. Gu khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ‚ÄėMbe ana muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta bun suanga thi?‚Äô Fhuvara.
\v 19 \x - \xo 25:19 \xt FG 18.15; 23.29\x*Mbe hegap, wari won rotu mbui t…®vi ga nzuav ana phorga nzuav ana dav, mba rimgi guma, ana z…® Zisas, mbe mba bigi ga nzuav ana dai. Mbe mba rimgi guma Zisas ga nzuaim, Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėZisas rimgiap, taagia khavgi.‚Äô
\v 20 \x - \xo 25:20 \xt FG 25.9\x*Gu ana suaŇčgi buna n…®…®eŇč kaŇčgi za mbuav, gu tuituigia ana nzan za mbuav, na nd…®knd…®k tuituigiap sagi fhuvara. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana nzangeŇč thagi. Gu ana nzangeŇč thav, gu mbaram kha nzambaren ana muuŇčgi, ‚ÄėMaaŇčgi, ndu Zerusareman naangeŇč vuzvugip, ndu Zerusareman naaŇčrim, gu vh…®ra naaŇčv Zerusareman nde buni mbarararga?‚Äô
\v 21 Gu maaŇč nzuaim, Por thav, khaŇč na nzuai, ana khueŇč vuzvugi, ana phena t…®vaneŇčra k…®rim, zumgum Sisar nduara ana buni mbarararga. Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, gu ne rargap ana ndi phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngim, ana mbur ki. Ana mbara muuŇčgip k…®rim, gu tuav the gangip, ana sararim, ana Ňčg…®p, Sisar gan…®nga.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 Festus mba bigir Agripa neŇčgegim, Agripa mba bigi mbararagiap khaŇč Festus ga nzuai, ‚ÄúGu nduara mba guma buni mbararargeŇč vuzvugi.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč nzuai, Festus khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇčgim, ndu gurmaŇčgip ana buni mbarararga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 25:23 \xt Mt 10.18; Mk 13.9\x*Mbe maaŇč wari ga suaŇčgiap, mba m…®timanera Agripa gu Bernaisi, wani wo shagi vhuuiŇčra wani s…®…®Ňčgiap, wani zi. Mani zav, mbe phogi ga vhov buni nzuai phena vhen verim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®…®t…®vir pani gum mba Ňčgu bak…®men ki gumgir pani, mbe mani phorga zav mba phena vhen vergi. Mbe zav vergim, Festus nzuaim, mbe Por ndiga zi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 25:24 \xt FG 25.2-3; 25.7; 22.22\x*Mbe Por ndiga mben han z…®gim, Festus khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu kha Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, nde kha nza phorga ki gumgir vh…®rve, nde kha guma gan…®. Mba Zudain ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za ana nzuav nzuav kama havharar khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėNdu za ana shog…®rim, ana rimgi.‚Äô Gu Zerusarem kim, mbe mba suambarara na mbuav kim, gu zav khaŇč zergim, mbe mbara na nzuai. Mbe khara na nzuai, ‚ÄėNde mba guma shogirim, ana rimgiri. Nza ana k…®rgeŇč vuzvugi fhuvara.‚Äô
\v 25 Mbe maaŇč na nzuai, gu kha guma gari, ana r…®m…®nga big…®n thueŇč muuŇčgirga, ana ne suaŇčv r…®m…®nga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana thagi. Ana vh…®ra khueŇč vuzvugi, Sisar nduara ana buni mbarararga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap khueŇč suaŇčgiap khar ki, gu ana sararim, ana Sisar han Ňčg…®rga.
\v 26 Gu ana sarari, ana Ňčg…®r za mbuav, gu vh…®ra kaŇčgi fhu, gu ram muuŇčgi khesharigi kameŇč khergip, nza wari wo guma bak…®me ndi mbararim, ana gangip kaŇčgirie, mbe kha bigeŇč ga nzuav kha guma ga nzuav nzuai? Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap kha guma ndigap, ndu Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, gu ana ndigap, ndu han zav, vh…®ra kha gumgi vh…®rve han z…®gi. Nza za ana nzuai buni mbararagip, nde nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč tharir nan kurarim, gu Sisar suaŇčv kher…®rga gap, gu mba kameŇč khergip ana ndi maanga.
\v 27 Gu kaŇčgi khueŇč nzerigi fhuvara, gu maaŇč muuŇčgip phena t…®vanen ki guma the ndi harigi guman pana the ndi maaŇčv, gu mba guma mba bigeŇč muuŇčgiap ne khuav b…®neŇč r…®gi. Gu vh…®ra ne khergiap, ne phorga mba guma ndi mbai fhu, ne nzerigi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\c 26
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuin Agripa phorga nzuai.
\p 
\v 1 Festus mba bunin mbe suaŇčgim, Agripa mbaram khaŇč Por ga nzuai, ‚ÄúGu ndu kh…®rigi, ndu nduara wo suaŇčv suaŇčri.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč suaŇčgim, Por mbaram har ndav wo nzuav nzuav, khaŇč nzuai,
\v 2 ‚ÄúŇägui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, gu kha ZudaiŇč na sav na suaŇčgi buni, gu nta Ňčgarkai buni suan za mbui. Gu ntige khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, gu wo nd…®knd…®gi bun ndu suanga, ne nzerara.
\v 3 Ndu guigira nza ZudaiŇč, ndu za nzan t…®vi kaŇčgi. Ndu vh…®ra nza wari dav wari ga mbui t…®vi kaŇčgi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap khueŇč vuzvugi, ndu fhura mbar perav k…®v, na buni mbarari.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 26:4 \xt FG 22.3; 23.6; 24.15; 24.21; Fi 3.5\x*‚ÄúKha ZudaiŇč, mbe za na kaŇčgi. Mbe khaŇč muuŇčgia na kaŇčgi, gu taranera gu wo Ňčgu n…®…®Ňčgera mben hara kav vhuuŇčgiap guma ruma muuŇčgi. Gu zumgum nda vov, Zerusareman kim, Zerusareman ki gumgi, mbe na kaŇčgi.
\v 5 Mbe za na kaŇčgi, mbe vuzvugip, nduarira nan t…®vir ndu neŇčg…®rga. Mbe na kaŇčgi, gu guman kamara kav, gu Fherasi guma ki.\f a \fr 26:5 \ft Por taranera kav, ana Sirisia fhain Tarsus Ňčgu bak…®men kegi. Ndu Farasegi Gumgi 22.3 gan…®ri. \f* Gu Fherasi guma kav, gu mben t…®vi z…®n vui. Mbe FherasiŇč, mben t…®vi vh…®rve, ndu nta z…®n Ňčg…®rga, nta guigira simgi. ZudaiŇč mbari, mbe kha FherasiŇč z…®n vui t…®vi havhari mbari, mbe mba t…®vi ki fhuvara.
\v 6 \x - \xo 26:6 \xt Lo 18.5; Sng 132.11; Ais 7.14; Dan 9.24; FG 23.6; 28.20\x*Gu ntige khar th…®gim, mbe na nzuav nzuai. Mbe ntigem na nzuav nzuai, ne n…®…®eŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Gu khueŇč khoth…®gap Fhe Bak…®men rarga ki. Ana mba fhum muun zav nzan nz…®gi ga suaŇčgi ne, ana nen muunga, gu ne rarga ki.
\v 7 Mba nzan 12 th…®gi nz…®gi, mbe ra gu maan Fhe Bak…®me rotu mbuav, mbe guigira ana khoth…®gap, ana mba muun za mbui bigen rarga ki, ne h…®rga. Ňägui vh…®rve gari guman pan, gu vh…®ra mba bigeŇč khoth…®gap nen rarga ki. Mba bigen n…®…®eŇčra khare, mbe ZudaiŇč nera nzuav bunin na sav na nzuav nzuai.
\v 8 Nde gumgi mbari, nde thaŇč nzuav khuen Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi fhu, ana rimgi gumgi gu mbigi, ana taagi mbe khavgirga tukt…®gi?
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 26:9 \xt 1 T 1.13\x*\x - \xo 26:9 \xt FG 8.3; 22.4-5\x*‚ÄúGu fhum, gu nduara kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, gu bigi vh…®rvera muuŇčv Nasaret guma Zisas z…® mbevarga.
\v 10 \x - \xo 26:10 \xt FG 9.14; 9.21; Ga 1.13\x*Gu Zerusareman mba bigi ga muuŇčgi. Gu Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani han z…® bak…®me ndigap, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rver farfav, mbe ndi b…®na suegi. Gu maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgir pani mbe shog…®rim, mbe vh…®z…® zav nzuaim, gu vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėMbe vh…®z…®rga.‚Äô
\v 11 Gu vh…®ra tugi vh…®rvera vov, Fhe Bak…®men buni mbararagi phenin vherir verar gumgi gu mbigir suigav, farfa mbat…®gar mbe muuŇčgi. Gu khaŇč t…®g…®p mben muuŇčrim, mbe k…®r Guma Bak…®me s…®v, buni mbat…®gir ana suanga. Gu guigira mbe nzuav ndav shigap, gu mbe nzuav garav, saman ki Ňčgui bak…®vir vov, mbe ndi gari. Gu Ňčg…®p, mbe gangirga, gu mben suigip, z…®v, farfa mbat…®gar mben muunga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n panan ruagi ne neŇčgi.
\r Farasegi Gumgi 9.3-19; 22.6-16
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 26:12 \xt FG 9.3; 22.6\x*Por mba buni nzua vov khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGu maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me rotu gari gumgir pani, mbe z…® bak…®men na n…®…®Ňčgiap, na sarigim, gu vui. Mbe na sarigim, gu Damaskusan ndai.
\v 13 Ňägui vh…®rve gari guman pan, ndu mbarara. Gu ndav kim, ra ndav vov, ph…®…®Ňč ndim, gu garim, vhava bak…® mbe tor vhekvhegi fara muuŇčgiap buivar kega zeri. Mba vhava Ňčaar, ana guigira havhargiap ran Ňčaara kambarigi. Ana zerav na sh…®gap, vh…®ra na phorga ndai gumgi, ana vh…®ra mbe sh…®rigi.
\v 14 Ana nza sh…®rigim, nza za n…®…®eŇč regi. Nza n…®…®eŇč regav, gu guma mbe kama mbararagim, ana HibruiŇč kaman nan nzav khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėSor, Sor, ndu thaŇč nzuav nan farfagi? Ndu b…®rgi bigi safuav, zaar wora nd…®…®i.‚Äô
\v 15 Mba guma maaŇč na nzuaim, gu khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄėGuma rum, ndu the?‚Äô Gu maaŇč nzuaim, Guma Bak…®me khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėGu Zisas ma! Ndu nan farfagi!
\v 16 \x - \xo 26:16 \xt FG 22.15\x*Ndu khavgi th…®g…®. Gu ntige ndun h…®gap, ndu farasarigi. Ndu ntigem nan Ňčaara suirav, ana muunga. Ndu nan Ňčaarar muuŇčv, ndu ntige gangi bigeŇč, ndu ne bun suaŇčv, ndu vh…®ra gu zumgum ndu kh…®v…®rga bigi, ndu vh…®ra nta bun suanga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 26:17 \xt FG 22.21\x*Gu ndu gan…®nga, ndun Ňčgu gumgi gum harigi fhaiŇč Ňčgui gumgi, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gir ndun muunga. Gu fhura mbe gan…®rim, mbe ndu shogirim, ndu rimgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Gu ndu sararim, ndu mben han Ňčg…®rga.
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Ais 35.5; 42.7; 42.16; Zo 8.12; FG 20.32; 2 Ko 6.14; Ef 2.2; Kor 1.13\x*Ndu mben han Ňčg…®p mben r…®mgi taaŇčrim, mbe mba g…®ng…®na thav, Ňčaarar z…®rga. Mbe vh…®ra Satanan ŇčkasŇčka thav, Fhe Bak…®me han z…®rga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip, mbe fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, gu nta vh…®zgirga. Gu mben t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgirim, mbe z…® bak…®me ndirga, mba na khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, gu mbe farasegi, mbe nan gumgi gu mbigi ma. Mbe mbe phorg…® k…®rga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ndigap, harigi Ňčguir vugi nen Agripa nzuai.
\p 
\v 19 Por mba bunin Agripa nzua vov khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúŇägui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, gu Hevenan ki big…®na gangiap, gu ana buni kaadogi fhuvara.
\v 20 \x - \xo 26:20 \xt Mt 3.8; FG 9.20; 9.28-29; 11.26; 13.14\x*Gu mba big…®na gangiap, fhara guarara gu Damaskusan ki gumgi gu mbigi, gu mbe phorga suaŇčgi. Gu zumgum zav Zerusareman ki gumgi gu mbigi phorga suaŇčgiap, mba Zudia fhain gu za mbe phorga nzua vov, harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi, gu vh…®ra mbe suaŇčgi. Gu mbe phorga nzuav, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėNde wari won ndavi domdor…®v, Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®v, nden t…®vi, mbe nta gan…®rim, nde ndavi domdorgi gumgi mbui t…®vir muuŇčri.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 26:21 \xt FG 21.30-31\x*Gu mba buni bun nzuaim, ZudaiŇč mba big…®na n…®…®eŇčra nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phena b…®na vhen nan suirav, na shogirim, gu r…®m…®n za mbui.
\v 22 \x - \xo 26:22 \xt Ru 24.27; 24.44; Zo 5.46; Ro 3.21\x*Fhe Bak…®me nduara nan kurkurigim, gu nzerara ka zav, ntige zav khar th…®gi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu ntige khaŇč th…®gap, gu Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun gumgi kh…®ni ga nzuav, gu vh…®ra z…® ki gumgir panan ga nzuai. Gu harigi khesharigi buni nzuai fhuvara. Gu mba nzuai buni, gu ntara nzuai. Gu Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi fhum suaŇčgi buni gum Moses suaŇčgi buni, gu mba bunira bun nzuai.
\v 23 \x - \xo 26:23 \xt Ais 42.6; 49.6; Ru 24.26; 24.44-47; 1 Ko 15.20; Kor 1.18\x*Mbe khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄėFhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi ndir zav farasarigi guma, ana fharav zaa ndigip, rimgip, ana vh…®ra fharav taagi mbogar keg…®p khavgirga guma ma. Ana khavgip, ana Fhe Bak…®me taagip IsreriŇč gum mba harigi Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigi ndirga buni bun mbe suanga. Ana mba buni bun mbe suanga, mba buni vhava Ňčaara farar muuŇčgip tuavar mbe kh…®v…®rga.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúAgripa guigira khueŇč khoth…®g…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Por wo nzuav gorav, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuaim, Festus kh…®r…®v kaav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúPor, ndu ŇčanŇčangi! Ndu shure vh…®rve ga muuŇčgiap, ndu nd…®knd…®ga bak…®me ndigim, ndun nd…®knd…®ga bak…®me ndu muuŇčgim, ndu ŇčanŇčangi!‚ÄĚ
\v 25 Ana ne nzuaim, Por khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuman rum, Festus, gu ŇčanŇčangi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gu guigira nzuai, gu nd…®knd…®k kav, gu khar nzuai.
\v 26 \x - \xo 26:26 \xt Zo 18.20\x*Ňägui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, gu khar nzuai buni, ana za nta kaŇčgi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu za mba bigi bun ana nzuav, gu r…®vi fhuvara. Gu vh…®ra kaŇčgi, gu kha nzuai bigi, nta ana r…®mani gum khuarani ga zorgi fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra nta kaŇčgi, kha bigi, nta zorga h…®gi fhuvara.
\v 27 Ňägui vh…®rve gari guman pan Agripa, ndu kha Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi suaŇčgi buni, ndu nta khoth…®gi o, fhu? Gu kaŇčgi, ndu nta khoth…®gi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Por maaŇč nzuaim, Agripa khaŇč nzambaren Por ga muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúNdu ram muuŇčgiap mba nd…®knd…®ga mbui? Gu kha tuga t…®vaneŇčra, gu Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n Ňčg…®g…®rie?‚ÄĚ
\v 29 Ana ne nzuaim, Por ana Ňčgarkarav, khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu tuga mpeeŇčmpeeŇč o tuga t…®vaneŇč ga nd…®knd…®g…® ne suaŇčv sim…® thari. Gu khaŇč muuŇčgi t…®gap Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ntige ndu nduara fhuvara, ndu phorga kav gu khar nzuai buni mbararagi gumgi, nde za wari t…®g…®ra ntige na farar muuŇčgirga. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi fhuvara, mbe khar na mbui t…®var nden muuŇčv, shenin nde hari gu suira k…®v, nde ndi b…®na surgane, gu ne thagi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Por mba buni suaŇčgim, mba Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan gum, mba Ňčgui gari guman pana vhari, Bernaisi, mbe phorgap piigiap ki gumgi, mbe za wari t…®g…®ra khavgi.
\v 31 \x - \xo 26:31 \xt FG 23.9; 23.29; 25.25\x*Mbe za khavgiap, mba kav buni nzuai ŇčaneŇč thav, wari vui. Mbe mba ŇčaneŇč thav vov, nduarira wari phorga nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúKha guma, ana big…®na mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgia kake, ana ne khuav r…®…®e o, ana ne khuav phena t…®vanen kae.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 \x - \xo 26:32 \xt FG 25.11\x*Mbe ne suaŇčgia thav, Agripa khaŇč Festus ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu kha guma fh…®rgirim, ana Ňčg…®rga tukt…®gi, ana nduara khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄėGu Sisar han Ňčg…®rim, ana na buni mbararargeŇč vuzvugi.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\c 27
\ms1 Por Roman vui.
\s1 Mbe Por ndim Roman vui kema kh…®ngi. \fig [map]|alt="Pol i go long biktaun Rom" src="paul4.tif" size="span" copy="The British and Foreign Bible Society" ref="Farasegi Gumgi 27"\fig*
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 27:1 \xt FG 25.12; 25.25\x*Mbe kama shogiap, nza sarigim, nza kema ndigap, Itari fhain vui. Nza vuim, mbe Por gum ana phorga phena t…®vanen ki gumgi mbari, mbe mbe ndi kema suegap, mbe ndi mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pana mbe farve kh…®ngi. Mba g…®mat…®v, ana 100 g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pan ma. Ana z…® Zurius, ana Sisaran ntari ga mbui g…®mat…®va mbe ma. \f a \fr 27:1 \ft Por Zerusareman ndagi tugen Ruk vh…®ra ana phorgap ndagi. Ndu FG 16.10 ki kameŇč gan…®ri. Ndu vh…®ra, FG 21.17 gan…®ri. Por Zudia thav, Roman verim, Ruk vh…®ra wom taagiap ana phorgap vergi. \f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 27:2 \xt FG 19.29\x*Nza mba fomaŇčgia ndai kem, ana kha Ňčgu bak…®men kem ma, Adramitium. Mba kem, ana kha Esia fhain ki Ňčguir sari, ana nta phog…®v naan za mbui. Nza mba kema ndigap, maaŇč thav ndai. Nza ndaim, Tesaronaika guma Aristarkus, ana Masedonia fhaiŇč guma ma, ana vh…®ra nza phorga ndai.
\v 3 \x - \xo 27:3 \xt FG 24.23\x*Nza ndaim ra vh…®zgim, nza harigi ra h…®gim, nza vov, Saidon Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorgap, Zurius t…®var vhuun Por ga mbuav, ana kh…®rigim, ana vov, won k…®vntogi garav mben han mba gu bigi ndi.
\v 4 Nza Saidon phorga kegap, maaŇč Saidon thav, siga wari vuim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč k…®vgia nza ndiga vuim, kem thav, nza kh…®gap Saiprus r…®g…®k…®rige z…®n k…®rar h…®gap ndai.
\v 5 Nza nda vov, Sirisia gu Pamfiria fhain mbas…®ga bak…®me shoga nda vov, zumgum nza vov, Risia Ňčgu bak…®me fhain Maira Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi.
\p 
\v 6 Nza vov maaŇč phorgap, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®var pan, ana Areksandria Ňčgu bak…®men kema gari, ana phorga kegap, Itarin naan zav mbui. Ana Itarin naan zav mbuim, ana mbaram nza nzuaim, nza mba zegi kema thav vov, fov, mba keman maaŇčgi.
\v 7 Nza fov, mba keman maaŇčgiap ndai. Nza ndaim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč guigira k…®vgiap nza daim, mba kem mbarara ndaim, rari mbari vh…®zgi. Mba keman Ňčgari gumgi khaŇč t…®gap Ňčgarav, nza nda vov, Nidus Ňčgu bak…®me han mbaim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč maaŇč nza th…®vigim, nza naangen mbovara thav, wari vov, Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen z…®n k…®rar mueŇč nderen Sarmone n…®mane gaara t…®ga ndai.
\v 8 Mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe khaŇč t…®gap, Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, nza Krit mbas…®k taaŇčra t…®gap wari ndai. Nza nda vov, zumgum mbe kha z…®n r…®gi Ňčanen hegi, Mb…®n Kaman VhuuaeŇč. Mba Mb…®n Kaman VhuuaeŇč Rasea Ňčgu bak…®men han ki.
\p 
\v 9 Rari vh…®rvera vh…®zgim, ZudaiŇč Fhe Bak…®me mbe muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgi ne nzuav, mbe ZudaiŇč ne nd…®knd…®gap, mbe thamthagi tuga bak…®me vh…®ra vh…®zgim, mbas…®k phuri guigira mbat…®gi, maaŇč muuŇčgiap Por khaŇč mbe nzuai,\f b \fr 27:9 \ft Kha tuga bak…®me, ana Fhe Bak…®me mba gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vh…®zgi tuk ma. Ndu Wok Pris sapta 23.26-32 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves. Mba tugivigen b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…®me Mediterenian mbas…®ga bak…®men khavi tugivige ma. Mba tugivigen, Ňčkee rui fhu. \f*
\v 10 \x - \xo 27:10 \xt FG 27.22\x*‚ÄúNde kha gumgi, nde na mbarara. Gu kaŇčgi, nza ntige khaŇč thav Ňčg…®rga, nza guigira tuga mbat…®ga ndigirga. Nza tuga mbat…®ga ndiv, bigi vh…®rve fusueg…®rga. Nza kha ndiga vui bigi, nta nduarira mbar r…®rim, kem vh…®ra nduara mbat…®girga tukt…®gi fhuvara, nza vh…®ra mbat…®girga.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Por maaŇč nzuaim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pan, ana Por nzuai kameŇč mbararagi fhuvara. Ana mba kema sh…®man suigi guma gum mba kema namkam, ana mani nd…®knd…®ga z…®n vui.
\v 12 Mbe mba phorgi mb…®n kameŇč, ne b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč zorga ki mb…®n kameŇč fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba keman ki gumgi vh…®rve, mbe wari t…®ga nzuav, mbe mba mb…®n kameŇč thav, wari Ňčg…®r za mbui. Mbe khueŇč vuzvugi, nza maaŇč muuŇčgip tukt…®g…®rga, nza Ňčg…®p, Finiks mb…®n kameŇč phorg…®p, nza nen k…®v, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč gan…®nga. Finiks mb…®n kameŇč, ana Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen muen saut fhain ra veri fhain mbarav ki.
\s1 B…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč gum mbas…®k phuri khavgi.
\p 
\v 13 Mbe mb…®n kama vhuueŇč kim, mba saut fhain b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč khavgi, mba fhain b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč k…®vgi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ‚ÄúNza nzerara Ňčg…®p, mba nzuai mb…®n kamen Ňčg…®g…®rga.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgiap, aŇčka Ňčg…®rga kema kh…®ngiap, wari Krit mbas…®k taaŇčra t…®gap, wari vui.
\v 14 Mbe vuim, tuga t…®vaneŇčra b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…® guarara khavgi. Mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč, mbe kha z…®n ana r…®gi, Not fhaiŇč b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ma. Mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč Krit r…®g…®k…®rigen mueŇč nderen kega zi.
\v 15 Ana zav, kh…®r…®v, kha kema sav, ana mbui. Mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe kema tog…®p, wari taagip Ňčg…®r za mbui, mbe tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgia thav, fhura mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč garim, ana mba kem sav, ana ndiga vui.
\v 16 B…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč mba kema ndiga vuim, nza vov, saut fhain r…®g…®k…®ra bisaŇč maneŇč, mbe kha z…®n ne ga r…®gi, Kauda, nza ne han vui. Nza ne han vov, ne vhen vuim, ne mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč tuav puigi. Nza mbaram, mba kema bisaneŇč nza Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbuav, ne Ňčg…®rga kema bak…®me han zi. Nza ana Ňčg…®rga, kema bak…®me gaar z…®gim, mba keman Ňčgari gumgi mba kema bisaneŇč Ňčg…®rga kema bak…®me ndarav, mpiiŇč ndigap ana kav, ana z…®ri.
\v 17 Mbe ana kav, ana z…®rgiap, mbar hegap, harigi mpiiŇč ndigap, mbu kema bak…®me piiaŇč rugap, mueŇč h…®gap, mbaram mba kema bak…®me kav, ana z…®ri. Mbe khueŇč nzuav mbe maaŇč muuŇčgirga, mba kem sh…®rav mbas…®k Ňčgirg…®rga fhu. Mbe vh…®ra khuen rivgi, mbe Ňčg…®v k…®v, Afrika fhaiŇč k…®t…®gar mbas…®ga r…®gar kh…®…®nan ndarga, mbe maaŇč muuŇčgia vh…®ra mba keman sher, mbe ana fh…®rgi. Mbe mba kema sher fh…®rgim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč nduara mba kema ndiga vui.
\v 18 Mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč gum mbas…®k phuri guigira k…®vgia zav, nza sim, mba m…®timanera mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe hegap, mba keman ki bigi mbari, mbe nta fo mbas…®ga sui.
\v 19 Mba b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč gum mbas…®k phuri mbara muuŇčgiap kim, ra phuni vh…®zgim, khegenen mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mben nd…®knd…®gi guigira mbe mbat…®gi, mbe thav wari wo farira mba keman sher gu bigi, mbe nta fuasui. \f c \fr 27:19 \ft Mbe kha fhain tuituigiap Grikin kama kaŇčgi fhuvara. \f*
\p 
\v 20 Mbe nta fuasuav, rari vh…®rve vh…®zgim, nza za khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza rari vh…®rver, nza ran Ňčaar gum Ňčkaan Ňčaari gangi fhuvara. Kha b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…®me vh…®ra nza safui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza wom khaŇč suanga fhu, ‚ÄėNza nzerara keg…®rga.‚Äô Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza nd…®knd…®gi, nza za mbat…®girga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Mbe rari vh…®rver, mbe the mba thaneŇč mbegi fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Por zumgum khavgiap, mbe r…®gar th…®gap, khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde kha gumgi, nde maaŇč muuŇčgiap gu nzuai kameŇč z…®n vov, nza Krit r…®g…®k…®rigera kakake, kha kem mbat…®geŇč nt…®…®Ňč, nza vh…®ra bigi thari fuasuege nt…®…®Ňč.
\v 22 \x - \xo 27:22 \xt FG 27.10; 27.31\x*Gu ntigem khaŇč muuŇčgia t…®ga nde nzuai, nde gori taagip thuuri ga reg…®ri. Nza guma thevi vh…®zgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara, kem nduara mbat…®girga.
\v 23 \x - \xo 27:23 \xt Dan 6.16; FG 23.11; Ro 1.9\x*Gu Fhe Bak…®me Ňčaara mbui guma ma. Gu vh…®ra ana guma ma. Gu gurum Ňčkoran Fhe Bak…®me enser mbe garim, ana nan h…®gap, na han th…®gi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 27:24 \xt FG 23.11\x*Ana na han th…®gap, khaŇč na nzuai, ‚ÄėPor, ndu r…®v…® thari. Ndu Ňčg…®p, Sisar n…®man th…®g…®ri. Ndu mbarara. Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuuŇčra ndu mbui. Ndu phorga mba keman ki gumgi, mbe vh…®zgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚Äô
\v 25 \x - \xo 27:25 \xt Ro 4.20-21; 2 T 1.12\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me enser maaŇč na suaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgia, gumgi, nde gori taagip thuuri ga reg…®ri. Gu Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi, ana mba na suaŇčgi bigi, nta ana mba na suaŇčgi bunira z…®n Ňčg…®g…®p, h…®g…®rga.
\v 26 \x - \xo 27:26 \xt FG 28.1\x*Kha kem, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ana ndigi Ňčg…®p, r…®g…®k…®ra thige phorg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Nza maaŇč Mediterenian mbas…®ga bak…®me, nza fhura b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč nza ndigap, ana shoga vui. Mba maaŇč, ana nzan 14 maaŇč ma. Nza mba maan fhura anan vui. Nza fhura anan vuav kav, mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe gari maaŇč r…®gar vov ph…®…®Ňč ndim, mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ‚ÄúNza gaa han mbai thi?‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Mbe mba nd…®knd…®ga muuŇčgiap, mbaram mb…®n mpari panpana ndi kh…®ngim, ana vergi. Mbe khueŇč kaŇčgi zav, mb…® kogira ki o, nza gaar han mbai. Mbe mba panpan ndi kh…®ngiap, garim, ana 40 mita th…®gi. Mbe gangia thav wari kim, kem maneŇč s…®ga mpeeŇčgera vugim, mbe wom mba panpana ndi kh…®ngi. Mbe ana ndi kh…®ngiap ana garim, ana 30 mita th…®gi.
\p 
\v 29 Ana 30 mita th…®gim, mbe khuen rivgi, kha kem Ňčg…®v k…®v, Ňčk…®…®r ndav, za sharer…®g…®rga. Mbe ne rivgiap, mba feth…®gi aŇčkari, mbe za nta ndi, kema z…®n k…®ra mbugu suegi. Mbe nta ndi suegap, ra vhemkora sh…®rargeŇč nzuav kaav, khaŇč nzuai.
\v 30 Mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe mba kema thav Ňčgeg…®rga tuavi ndi gari. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mpiin mba kema bisanen fegap, ana ndi mbarigim, ana taagia mb…®n verim, mbe puskarav, mbu kema n…®man ki aŇčkari ndi sur zav mbui. \f d \fr 27:30 \ft Ruk kha gava khera ana kha mpari mpuvenin Poran h…®gi bigi bun nza suaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe gumgi mbari khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, mbe RomiŇč Por fh…®rgim, ana vov, harigi Ňčguir vov, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai. Mbe gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe Por shogim ana rimgi. \f*
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 27:31 \xt FG 27.22\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Por khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pana nzuav, vh…®ra khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumgi kha keman k…® tharga, nde vh…®zgirga.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 Por maaŇč nzuaim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi hegap, mba kema bisanen fegap, ana ndi mbaim, ana veri mpiiŇč, mbe nta shogap, nta gorgim, mba kem mbas…®ge r…®gim, mbas…®k phuri za ana ndiga vui.
\p 
\v 33 Mba kema bisaneŇč mbas…®k phuri ana ndiga vugim, ra naan za mbuim, Por mbaram kaman mba keman ki gumgi ga nd…®…®i. Ana mbe mban mb…®rgeŇč nzuav, ana mba kamen mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNde tuga mpeeŇčra nden gori nde mbuim, nde mba mbegap ki fhuvara. Nde mba thav fhura kim, ph…®k bavira feth…®gi rari vh…®zgi.
\v 34 \x - \xo 27:34 \xt 1 Kin 1.52; Mt 10.30; Ru 12.7\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap khaŇč t…®gap nde nzuai, nde mban mb…®ri. Mba ŇčkasŇčkar nden n…®…®nga. Nde mbarara! Nde thaneŇč mbat…®girga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde za nzerara k…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 35 \x - \xo 27:35 \xt Mt 15.36; Zo 6.11; 1 T 4.3-5\x*Por maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, mbaram viktuma ndigap, mbe n…®mara Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigap ana phorga nzuai. Ana Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, ana ph…®rgiap, ana pi.
\v 36 Por maaŇč mbuim, mba gumgi ana gangiap, mbe gori taagia thueŇč regim, mbe vh…®ra mba pi.
\v 37 Nza mba keman ki gumgi, nzan vh…®rve 276 th…®gi.
\v 38 Mba keman ki gumgi za k…®vgia mbega thav, mbe wit k…®ni, mbe za nta fov mbas…®ga suegi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgirga, kem simgirga fhu.
\s1 Kem mbat…®gi.
\p 
\v 39 Ra ndav sh…®rigim, mba keman Ňčgari gumgi, mbe nza mba gaar zegi ŇčaneŇč gari. Mbe ne garav, ne kaŇčgi fhu, nza maaŇčgi fhain zegi. Mbe ne nzuav gara vov, mb…®n kama mueŇč gari. Mbe ne garim, ne guigira kh…®…®na vhuuŇč ki. Mbe ana gangiap khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ‚ÄúNza tukt…®g…®rga, nza khueŇč vuzvugi, nza kha kema ndigi Ňčg…®p mbu mbas…®k taaŇč vhuuŇč phorg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 40 Mbe ne suaŇčgiap, mba keman aŇčkari, mbe za ntan mpiiŇč gorgim, nta za mbas…®gar vergi. Mbe nta gorgi, nta vergim, mbe vh…®ra toga kema ndi tuavar mbai ndava bak…®ni, mbe vh…®ra ni fh…®rgiap, niin suirigi. Mbe niin suirav mbaram mba kema n…®man ki sher bak…®me, mbe ana fh…®rgi. Mbe ana fh…®rgiap ana ndagim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč mbe kh…®ga mba kema t…®gim, ana mba mb…®n kama gaar vui.
\p 
\v 41 \x - \xo 27:41 \xt 2 Ko 11.25\x*Mbe vuim, kem mbas…®ga r…®gagera kh…®…®nar ndav, ana perigi. Mba kema n…®m guigira vov, mba kh…®…®na perav, guigira th…®ga havhargi. Ana th…®gim, mbas…®k phuri zav, kh…®r…®v mba kema z…®nk…®ra shoga kim, ana za sh…®rager…®gi.
\v 42 Mba kem sh…®rager…®gim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi, mbe mba b…®nan ki gumgi shogirim, mbe vh…®z…® za nzuai. Mbe khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi, ‚ÄúNza muuŇčv k…®rim, mbe fov mbas…®gar maaŇčgip, di Ňčg…® phogip wari reg…® rivgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 43 Mbe maaŇč suaŇčgiap, mbe shog…®r za mbuim, mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pan, ana Por ga nd…®knd…®giap, thav khaŇč mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mba b…®nan ki gumgi shog…®rim, mbe vh…®z…® thari.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč mbe suaŇčgia thav, khaŇč mba keman ki gumgi ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde di kaŇčgi gumgi, nde fharav fov maaŇčgip, di Ňčg…®p, th…®va phogiri.
\v 44 \x - \xo 27:44 \xt FG 27.22-25\x*Nde di kakagi gumgi, nde mba khira t…®vi gum keman f…®gi, nde nta tuigirim, mbas…®k phuri nde ndigi Ňčg…®p, th…®va phogiri.‚ÄĚ Mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi gari g…®mat…®va pan maaŇč nza suaŇčgim, nza za mba t…®vara muuŇčgiap, nza za th…®va phogiap, nza the mbat…®gi fhu.
\c 28
\s1 Por Marta r…®g…®k…®rigen ki.
\p 
\v 1 Nza za nzerara vov, th…®va phogiap, nza zumgum, mba phogi r…®g…®k…®rige nza niŇčge kaŇčgi. Nza vov, Marta r…®g…®k…®rige phogi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 28:2 \xt Ro 1.14; 1 Ko 14.11; 2 Ko 11.27; Kor 3.11\x*Nza mba r…®g…®k…®rigen kim, mba r…®g…®k…®rigen ki gumgi, mbe t…®var vhuuŇč guarara nza mbui. Nza maaŇč kim, mbok nzi, bigi raŇčgim, mbe vhavi ga r…®gap nza nzuaim, nza vov, mbe phorga vhavi gurguri.
\v 3 Nza mbe phorgap vhavi gurgurav, Por nzira mbari ndiga zav, nta ndi vhava suim, kuruk mba nziran kegap, vhav ana shim, ana h…®gap, za Por farve ga bigap, zirgiap, ana ntorgi.
\v 4 Mba kuruk zirgiap, Por ga ntorgim, mba r…®g…®k…®rigen ki gumgi gu mbigi ana gangiap, mbe nduarira khaŇč wari ga nzuai, ‚ÄúNde mbu guma gan…®, ana gumgi shogim, mbe vh…®zi guma thi? Ana mbas…®ga r…®gar r…®m…®ngeŇč thagi. Anan tor ntigem anan t…®vi mbat…®gi Ňčgarkai, ana ntige vh…®zgirga.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \x - \xo 28:5 \xt Mk 16.18; Ru 10.19\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mba suambarar Por ga mbuim, Por mba kuruga hiŇčgi, ana vhava r…®gap, shigi. Big…®n thueŇč Porar h…®gi fhu.
\v 6 \x - \xo 28:6 \xt FG 14.11\x*Por maaŇč mba kuruga muuŇčgim, mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe khueŇč nzuav Por garav ki. Ana barga thi? Ana vhemkora r…®v rimgirga thi? Mbe ne rarga tuga mpeeŇčra Por garav kim, big…®n thueŇč ana h…®gi fhu. Mbe thav kha nd…®knd…®ga mbuav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúKhe mbar…®va bak…® mbe ma.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Mbe mba nd…®knd…®gar Por ga mbuim, mbe mba ki Ňčgun han ki nuianeŇč, ne mba r…®g…®k…®rige gari guman panan nuianeŇč ma. Mba guman pana z…® khare, Pubrius. Mba guman pan nza ndiga wo phenan vugap, ra phuni khegenen ana t…®var vhuuŇčra nza muuŇčgi.
\v 8 \x - \xo 28:8 \xt FG 19.11; 1 Ko 12.9; 12.28; Ze 5.14-15\x*Nza vugap, Pubrius phenan kim, ana ndia r…®…®v, kaar ki. Ana r…®…®v, fhav gurgurgiap, v…®z…®na buna vhi. Por mbaram vov ana garav, ana nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. Por Fhe Bak…®me phorga suaŇčgiap, won farven ana kh…®ngim, ana taagia nzerigi.
\v 9 Por maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, mba r…®g…®k…®rigen ki r…®…®i gumgi, mbe za Por han zim, ana vh…®ra mbe mbuim, mben r…®mr…®…® vh…®zim, mbe taagia nzezerigi.
\v 10 Nza maaŇč kim, mbe guigira t…®var vhuuŇčra nza mbui. Nza maaŇč mbe phorga kav kav, mbe thav wari Ňčg…®r za mbuim, mbe nza mba sosuagi bigi, mbe za nza ndim, ntan ndiga vov kema suegi.
\s1 Por vov Roman h…®gi.
\p 
\v 11 Nza Martan kim, k…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgi. Mba k…®ni phuni khegene vh…®zgim, nza zumgum fo kema mben maaŇčgi. Mba kem zav, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč k…®vgim, ana b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč rarga, mba r…®g…®k…®rigen kegi. Mba kem, ana Areksandriain kem ma. Mba kema n…®man, mben mbar…®va Susan kamanin tumani th…®gap ki. Nza mba kema ndigap maaŇč thav sigi.
\v 12 Nza siga vov, Sirakus Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorga ra phuni khegenen maaŇč kegi.
\v 13 Nza maam Sirakusan kegap, ana thav siga vov, Regium Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi. Nza maaŇč phorga kegap, m…®timanera nza gari, saut fhaiŇč b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč khavgim, nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap maaŇč Regium thav sigi. Nza maaŇč Regium thav siga vuim, ra phunini vh…®zgim, nza khegenen, nza vov, Puteori Ňčgu bak…®me phorgi.
\v 14 Nza maaŇč phorgap, mba Ňčgu bak…®men, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi mbarir hegi. Nza mben hegim, mbe wari phorg…® k…®r zav nza nzuaim, nza mbe phorga kim, harath…®gi rari vh…®zgi. Nza maaŇč mbe phorga kim, mba harath…®gi rari vh…®zgim, nza khavgiap, Roman Ňčgu bak…®me ndai.
\v 15 Nza ndaim, Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Rom Ňčgu bak…®men kegap, nza ndai ne mbararagiap mbe tuavar nzan pua zeri. Mbe tuavar nzan pua zerim, nza ndav Apius Phok th…®mara, nza mben purav, nza nda vov, mbe kha z…®n r…®gi pheni, Gumgi Za Kui Phena Phuni Khegene, nza mba Ňčanera mbarir purigi. Por mbe gangiap, ana Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigap, ana ndav anan havhargi.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 28:16 \xt FG 24.23\x*Mbe nzan purav nza wari t…®ga ndav, Rom Ňčgu bak…®men hegi. Nza Roman hegim, Rom gari guman pan Por kh…®rav, khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúNdu phena then k…®rim, ntari ga mbui g…®mat…®va the ndu phorg…® k…®v, ndu gan…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Por Roman Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuai.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 28:17 \xt FG 21.33; 24.12-13; 25.8\x*Por ra phuni khegenen Roman kegap, ana mbaram Zudain gumgir panin kamgi. Ana mben kamgim, mbe zav wari fhugim, ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNan fegi gum Ňčgugi, gu nza wari mbevi big…®n thueŇč muuŇčgi fhu. Gu vh…®ra nza won nz…®gi t…®va thueŇč dai fhu. Mbe fhura nan suirav, Zerusareman na ndi b…®na kh…®ngia kegap, mbe ntige na ndi RomiŇč farve kh…®ngi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 28:18 \xt FG 22.24; 25.8; 26.31\x*Romin gumgir pani na buni mbararagi, gu r…®m…®nga big…®n thueŇč muuŇčgi fhu, mbe na shogirim, gu rimgirga fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgia fhura na fh…®rgirim, gu Ňčg…®r za mbui.
\v 19 \x - \xo 28:19 \xt FG 25.11\x*Mbe maaŇč na nzuaim, ZudaiŇč hegap, mbe buni kaadogi. Mbe mbe buni kaadogim, gu mbe suanga tuap the ki fhu. Gu thav khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄėGu vuzvugi, Sisar na buni mbarararga.‚Äô Gu fhura big…®n the suaŇčv won nt…®…®ri ga suaŇčv suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 20 \x - \xo 28:20 \xt FG 24.15; 26.6-7; 26.29; Ef 3.1-2; 2 T 2.9; Fm 1.10; 1.13\x*Gu mba bunira nzuav nden kamgim, nde zegi. Gu nde gan…®p, mba bunin nde suanga. Gu khueŇč khoth…®gi, nza IsreriŇč, nza za rarga ki guma, mbe ara nzuav kha shenan na kegi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Por ne nzuaim, mbe khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúZudaiŇč thari gava khergiap, nza ndi mbav, ndu bun nza suaŇčgi fhu. Mbe vh…®ra guma the zav khaŇč h…®gap, ndu suaŇčgi buna mbat…®ga thueŇč bun nza suaŇčgi fhu, vh…®ra guma the khaŇč zerap, buna mbat…®ga thuen ndu suaŇčgi fhuvara.
\v 22 \x - \xo 28:22 \xt FG 24.5; 24.14; 1 Pi 2.12; 4.14\x*Nza maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ntige ndu mbararargeŇč vuzvugi. Ndu nduara won nd…®knd…®gi bun nza suaŇč. Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, za kha Ňčguiven ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zam, nza ZudaiŇč nzan r…®gar h…®gi t…®var kama z…®n vui nt…®…®ri, mbe buni mbat…®gir mbe nzuai.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Mbe maaŇč Por ga suaŇčgiap, hegap, tuga mbe sarigi. Mba tugar, gumgi vh…®rve zav Por ki phenan zegi. Mbe zegim, Por manera th…®gap Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga bigi n…®…®n sh…®gap, mba bunin gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav kim, ra vov vh…®zgi. Ana mbe nzua vov, Moses suaŇčgi t…®vi mbari, ana nta bun mbe nzuav vov, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi khergi buni, ana nta phorga khaŇč t…®gap havhargiap mbe nzuai. Ana mbe nzuav mbe nd…®knd…®gi khavi, mbe Zisas khoth…®g…®rga.
\v 24 Por mba buni suaŇčgim, gumgi mbari, mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Por nzerara nzuai. Mbe mbari, ana buni khoth…®gi fhu.
\v 25 \x - \xo 28:25 \xt Ais 6.9-10; Mt 13.14\x*Mbe mba buni ga nzuav, warira phorga nzuav wari dai. Mbe mba bunin wari dav, rur za mbuim, Por mpuun kha kamen mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira won kamthooŇč guma Aisaia ga rugim, ana nzan nz…®gi ga suaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar khaŇč Aisaia ga nzuai,
\v 26 \x - \xo 28:26 \xt Jer 5.21; Ese 12.2; Ro 11.8\x*\x - \xo 28:26 \xt Ais 6.9-10\x*‚ÄėNdu mba gumgi gu mbigi han Ňčg…®p, khaŇč mbe suaŇčri, ‚ÄúNde zazera kha buni mbarararga, nde mba buni nd…®…®riveŇč kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nde vh…®ra zazera gang…®nga, nde bigin the kaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ
\v 27 Mba gumgi gu mbigi mben pani havhargim, mbe bigi mbararargeŇč vuzvugi fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra wari wo khuari p…®ngiap, mbe vh…®ra won r…®mgi p…®ngi. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgirga fhu, mbe wo rimgir mba bigi gan…®v, wari wo khuarir mba bigi mbararav, nta nd…®…®riveŇč kaŇčgirga. Mbe ndavi domdor…®v, nan han z…®rim, gu mben muuŇčrim, mbe nzerarga.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28-29 \x - \xo 28:28-29 \xt Sng 67.2; Ru 3.6; FG 13.46-47; 18.6; 22.21; Ro 11.11\x*Por mba bunin mbe nzua vov khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúMaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde kaŇčgiri, Fhe Bak…®me taagip nza ndir zav muuŇčgi Ňčaarar vhuuŇč, Fhe Bak…®me mba Ňčaara ndigap, harigi Ňčgui ndi vugi. Mbe mba buni mbarararga.‚ÄĚ \f a \fr 28:28-29 \ft Bigi kaŇčgi gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, harigi buna mueŇč vh…®ra kha vezar ki. Mba kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúPor mba buneŇč suaŇčgim, ZudaiŇč ana thav vuim, ntara bak…®me mba gumgi r…®gar h…®gim, mbe warira phorga vhegi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 28:30 \xt FG 28.16\x*Por maam phena mben kav, mba bunin mbe nzuav kim, mpari mpuveni vh…®zgi. Ana mba phenan kav, zazera Ňčk…®…®ar mba phena namkama nd…®…®i. Ana kim, gumgi ana han phenan zim, ana guigira ndikndigi.\f b \fr 28:30 \ft Ruk mba mpari mpuveni vh…®zgim, ana Porar h…®gi bigi, ana nta bun nza suaŇčgi fhuvara. Mbe gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe RomiŇč, mbe phena t…®vanen Por fh…®rgim, ana k…®rar h…®gap vov, harigi fhaiŇč Ňčguir vugap, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun mbe nzuai. Mbe gumgi mbari kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe RomiŇč Por shogim, ana rimgi. \f*
\v 31 \x - \xo 28:31 \xt FG 4.31; 28.23; Ef 6.19\x*Ana kav, Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga bunin mbe nzuav, vh…®ra Zisas Krais buni vhuuin mbe nzuav mbe kh…®vi. Por Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suangen r…®vi fhu, vh…®ra guma the Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suangen ana th…®vi fhu.
